\id JHN
\h Yuḥanna 
\toc1 Yuḥanna 
\toc2 Yuḥanna 
\toc3 Yḥ. 
\mt1 Yuḥanna  
\c 1
\s1 Awař n Arebbi d Tafawt d Tudart  
\m
\v 1 Deg umezwaru tuɣa iǧa Wawař, Awař tuɣa-t ɣar AREBBI u AREBBI tuɣa-t d Awař. \x ◘ \xo 1:1 \xt Awřn. 8:22; Yḥ. 1:1, 2. \x*  
\v 2 Wanita d wenni iǧan ɣar AREBBI deg umezwaru. \x ◘ \xo 1:2 \xt Yḥ. 17:5. \x*  
\v 3 Zzayes Netta iǧa kuřci u břa Netta war teǧi uřa d ict n tmesřact zi \add marra\add* min iǧan. \x ◘ \xo 1:3 \xt Amz. 1:3; Izhd. 33:6; Afa. 3:9; Kul. 1:16; Ɛbr. 1:2. \x*  
\v 4 Dayes i teǧa Tudart u Tudart teǧa Tafawt n iwdan. \x ◘ \xo 1:4 \xt Yḥ. 5:26; 1 Yḥ. 5:11; 8:12; 9:5; 12:46. \x*  
\v 5 Tafawt tareqq di taǧest, taǧest war tt tᵉṭṭif. \x ◘ \xo 1:5 \xt Yḥ. 3:19. \x*   
\b  
\m
\v 6 Tuɣa \add din\add* ijj n bnadem issekk i-t-i-dd AREBBI, qqaren as Yuḥanna. \x ◘ \xo 1:6 \xt Mal. 3:1; Mt. 3:1; Mk. 1:2, 4; Lk. 3:3; 7:27; Yḥ. 1:33. \x*  
\v 7 Netta yusa-dd am ccahed ḥima ad iched i Tfawt, ḥima ad zzayes amnen marra.  
\v 8 Netta war iǧi ca d Tafawt, maca \add tuɣa-t\add* ḥima ad iched i Tfawt.   
\b  
\m
\v 9 Maɣar \add Tafawt\add* nni, tuɣa d Tafawt n tidett i itticen tafawt i kuř bnadem i dd-ittasen ɣar ddunect. \x ◘ \xo 1:9 \xt Yḥ. 8:12; 9:5; 12:46. \x*  
\v 10 Netta tuɣa-t di ddunect u zzayes tᵉttwagg ddunect, \add maca\add* ddunect war t tessin ca. \x ◘ \xo 1:10 \xt Ɛbr. 1:2; 11:3. \x*  
\v 11 Yusa-dd ɣar wi iǧan nnes, \add maca\add* wi iǧan nnes war t qbiřen.  
\v 12 Maca marra inni t iqebřen, iwca asen ṣṣulṭa, ḥima ad dewřen d tarwa n AREBBI, i yinni ittamnen deg Yisem nnes, \x ◘ \xo 1:12 \xt Ica. 56:5; Rum. 8:15; Gal. 3:26; 2 Bṭ. 1:4; 1 Yḥ. 3:1. \x*  
\v 13 inni war dd-ixřiqen uřa zeg idammen, uřa zi min ixs ddat \add n bnadem\add*, uřa zi min ixs weryaz, maca zi AREBBI dd-ittwaxeřqen.   
\b  
\m
\v 14 Awař idweř d ddat, izdeɣ jar aneɣ, neccin neẓra aɛuǧi nnes, aɛuǧi n Uyenni \add n Mmis\add* zi ɣar Babas i iccuren s arḍa d tidett. \x ◘ \xo 1:14 \xt Ica. 7:14; Mt. 1:16; 17:2; Lk. 1:31; 2:7; Kul. 1:19; 2:9; 2 Bṭ. 1:17; 1 Yḥ. 4:2, 3; 2 Yḥ. 1:7. \x*  
\v 15 Iched xas Yuḥanna, iřaɣa, inna: “D Wa min xef nniɣ, aqa Netta ad dd-yas awarni ayi, waxxa Netta idweř zzati, minzi Netta tuɣa-t qbeř inu.” \x ◘ \xo 1:15 \xt Mt. 3:11; Mk. 1:7; Lk. 3:16; Yḥ. 1:26,30. \x*   
\m
\v 16 Zi řekmařet nnes niwi-dd marra, arḍa x arḍa. \x ◘ \xo 1:16 \xt Kul. 2:10. \x*  
\v 17 Ccariɛa temmewc x ufus n Musa, maca arḍa d tidett usin-dd zi Yasuɛ Lmasiḥ. \x ◘ \xo 1:17 \xt Uf. 20:1. \x*  
\v 18 Uřa d ijj war iẓri AREBBI. Ayenni n AREBBI i iǧan deg weḥsin n Babas, d Netta i \add zzayes\add* issxebbaren. \x ◘ \xo 1:18 \xt Uf. 33:20; Aɛwd. 4:12; Mt. 11:27; Yḥ. 6:46; 1 Tim. 6:16; 1 Yḥ. 4:12. \x*   
\b  
\m  
\s1 Cchadet tamezwarut n Yuḥanna Amseɣḍaṣ  
\m
\v 19 Ta d cchadet n Yuḥanna řami dd-ssekken Wudayen ikehhanen d Ilawiyyen zi Urcalim ḥima ad t sseqsan: “Min teɛnid cek?” \x ◘ \xo 1:19 \xt [Mt. 3:1-12; Mk. 1:2-8; Lk. 3:15-17] — Yḥ. 5:33. \x*  
\v 20 Tuɣa iched, war issnuffar ca, iched: “Necc war ǧiɣ ca d Lmasiḥ.” \x ◘ \xo 1:20 \xt Yḥ. 3:28; Řex. 13:25. \x*  
\v 21 Sseqsan t: “I min teɛnid cek xenni? Ma d cek d \add anabi\add* Iliya?” Inna: “Lla, war ǧiɣ d necc!” “Ma d cek d anabi?” Yarra-dd: “Lla!”  
\v 22 \add Xas uca\add* nnan as: “Min teɛnid cek? Ittxeṣṣa aneɣ ad narr i yinni d aneɣ dd-issekken. Min teqqared x yixef nnec?”  
\v 23 Inna: “Necc d tmijja i ittřaɣan di řexřa: ‘Seggmem abrid n SIDI nican!’, am mammec inna unabi Icaɛya.” \x ◘ \xo 1:23 \xt Ica. 40:3; Mt. 3:3; Mk. 1:3; Lk. 3:4. \x*   
\m
\v 24 Inni dd-ittwassekken, tuɣa aten zeg Ifarisiyyen.  
\v 25 Nitni sseqsan t, nnan as: “Mařa war teǧid ca d Lmasiḥ uřa d Iliya uřa d anabi, i xenni mayemmi tᵉsseɣḍaṣed?” \x ◘ \xo 1:25 \xt Aɛwd. 18:18. \x*  
\v 26 Yuḥanna yarra-dd, inna asen: “Necc sseɣḍaṣeɣ deg waman, maca aqa din di řwesṭ nwem wenni war tessinem ca. \x ◘ \xo 1:26 \xt Mt. 3:11; Mk. 1:7; Lk. 3:16; Řex. 1:5; 11:16; 19:4. \x*  
\v 27 Netta d wenni i dd ɣa yasen awarni ayi, Netta iǧa qbeř inu, necc war sdiheǧeɣ ad as fesyeɣ ifiřan n sandaliyat nnes.”   
\m
\v 28 Man aya imsar di Baytɛanya x ujemmaḍ n L’Urdun, mani tuɣa Yuḥanna isseɣḍaṣ.   
\b  
\m
\v 29 Tiwecca nnes iẓra Yuḥanna Yasuɛ iggur-dd ɣares, inna: \bd “Xzarem, aqa-t d Izmar n AREBBI i ittekksen ddnub x ddunect!\bd* \x ◘ \xo 1:29 \xt Amz. 22:7, 8; Ica. 53:5, 7; Yḥ. 1:36. \x*  
\v 30 D Wa min xef nniɣ: ‘Ad dd-yas awarni ayi ijj n Weryaz nni iǧan zzati, minzi Netta tuɣa-t qbeř inu.’  
\v 31 Necc war t ssineɣ ca, maca ḥima ad ittwassargeb ɣar Israil, x uyenni usiɣ-dd ḥima ad ssɣeḍṣeɣ deg waman.”   
\m
\v 32 Yuḥanna iched, inna: “Ẓriɣ Arruḥ ihwa-dd am yict n tedbirt zeg ujenna, tarsa xas. \x ◘ \xo 1:32 \xt Mt. 3:16; Mk. 1:10; Lk. 3:22. \x*  
\v 33 Necc war t ssineɣ ca, maca wenni d ayi dd-issekken ḥima ad ssɣeḍṣeɣ deg waman, Netta inna ayi: ‘Wenni teẓrid ihwa-dd xas Arruḥ uca yarsa xas, d Wa d wenni isseɣḍaṣen di Arruḥ Iqeddsen.’  
\v 34 U Necc ẓriɣ, cehdeɣ belli Wanita d Mmis n AREBBI.”   
\b  
\m  
\s1 Imeḥḍaren imezwura n Yasuɛ  
\m
\v 35 Tiwecca nnes tuɣa Yuḥanna ibedd ak-d tnayen n imeḥḍaren nnes.  
\v 36 Am tuɣa ixezzar ɣar Yasuɛ i \add din\add* igguren, inna: “Xzarem, \add d Wa d\add* Izmar n AREBBI!” \x ◘ \xo 1:36 \xt Ica. 53:7; Yḥ. 1:29; Řex. 8:32\x*  
\v 37 Tnayen n imeḥḍaren nnes sřin as am tt iqqar uca ḍfaren Yasuɛ.  
\v 38 Inneqřeb-dd Yasuɛ, iẓra i-ten ḍeffaren t-i-dd, isseqsa ten: “Min xef tarezzum?” Nitni nnan as: “\add A\add* Amseřmad nneɣ, mani tzeddɣed?”  
\v 39 Inna asen: “Araḥem-dd, ad tẓarem!” Ruḥen akides, ẓrin mani izdeɣ, qqimen akides ass nni. Tasaɛɛet tuɣa-tt ɛřaḥař d ɛecra, \add ixs ad yini ɛřaḥař tasaɛɛet wiss arebɛa n tmeddit\add*.   
\m
\v 40 Andrawus, umas n Cimɛun, tuɣa-t d ijjen zeg yinni isřin aya zi Yuḥanna uca ḍeffaren Yasuɛ.  
\v 41 D wa i iẓrin amezwaru umas Cimɛun, inna as: “Aqa nufa Lmasiḥ!”  
\v 42 Issiweḍ i-t-i-dd ɣar Yasuɛ. Ixzar dayes Yasuɛ, inna: “Cek d Cimɛun, mmis n Yuna, ad ac řaɣan: ‘Kifa’, \add ixs ad yini ‘aẓru’\add* ”\f ◼ \fr 1:42 \ft \+fk Kifa\ft  - isem wanita d isem nnes s Tramit, u ‘Buṭrus’ d isem nnes s Tyunanit, minzi iwdan di temmurt di řweqt nni, tuɣa ssiwřen s Tramit, maca Tyunanit d iřes n Iyunaniyyen inni tuɣa ṣṣelṭen di temmurt ɣar ijj n řweqt qbeř dd-yusin Irumaniyyen.\f*  \x ◘ \xo 1:42 \xt Mt. 16:18. \x*   
\m
\v 43 Tiwecca nnes tuɣa ixs Yasuɛ ad iraḥ ɣar Ljalil. Immeřqa ak-d Filippus, inna as: “Ḍfar ayi-dd!”  
\v 44 Filippus s yixef nnes tuɣa zi Bayt-Ṣayda zi tandint n Andrawus d Cimɛun. \x ◘ \xo 1:44 \xt Yḥ. 12:21. \x*  
\v 45 Filippus yufa Natanayil, inna as: “Nufa wenni xef yura Musa di Ccariɛa uřa d Inabiyyen, aqa-t d Yasuɛ, mmis n Yusuf zi Nnaṣira.” \x ◘ \xo 1:45 \xt Amz. 3:15; 22:18; 26:4; 49:10; Aɛwd. 18:18; 2 Ṣm. 7:12; Ica. 4:2; 7:14; 9:5; 40:10, 11; 53:1-12; Irm. 23:5; 33:14; Ḥiz. 34:23; Dan. 9:24; Zak. 6:12; 9:9. \x*  
\v 46 Natanayil inna as: “Ma ad taɣ izemmar ad dd-teffeɣ zi Nnaṣira ca n tcuni?” Filippus inna as: “Araḥ-dd, texzared!”  
\v 47 Yasuɛ iẓra Natanayil iggur-dd ɣares, inna xas: “Xzar, wa d ijj n mmis d tidett n Israil nni war dayes bu řɣecc!”  
\v 48 Natanayil inna as: “Manis d ayi tessned?” Yasuɛ inna as: “Ẓriɣ cek swadday i wartu qbeř ma ad ac dd-iřaɣa Filippus.”  
\v 49 Natanayil yarra-dd xas: “\add A\add* Amseřmad inu, Cek d Mmis n AREBBI, Cek d Ajeǧid n Israil.”  
\v 50 Yasuɛ inna as: “Ma tumned s minzi d ac nniɣ: ‘Aqa ẓriɣ cek swadday i wartu’? Ad tẓared min iǧan ktar zi man aya.”  
\v 51 Inna as: “S tidett, s tidett, Necc ad awem iniɣ, zi ssa d tsawent ad tẓarem ajenna innurzem u lmalakat n AREBBI ttařyent hekkwant ɣar Mmis n bnadem!” \x ◘ \xo 1:51 \xt Amz. 28:12. \x*   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 2
\s1 Lmuɛjiza tamezwarut di Qana  
\m
\v 1 Deg wass wiss třata temsar ict n tmeɣra di Qana, ict n tendint di Ljalil. Tuɣa din yemmas n Yasuɛ.  
\v 2 Uřa d Yasuɛ d imeḥḍaren nnes ttwaɛarḍen-dd ɣar tmeɣra.  
\v 3 Řami iqḍa binu, tenna as yemmas i Yasuɛ: “War ɣarsen bu binu!”  
\v 4 Yasuɛ inna as: “Min din jar ayi akidem, \add a\add* tamɣart? Tasaɛɛet inu war dd-tiwiḍ ɛad!”  
\v 5 Yemmas tenna i imsexxaren: “Min d awem i ɣa yini, ggem t.”   
\m
\v 6 Tuɣa din setta n iqeddwaḥ n weẓru daysen aman, mmarsen dinni am mammec nnumen tteggen Wudayen řuḍu, kuř ijjen \add zzaysen\add* ɣares řqedd n tnayen ař třata n ‘iribaɛen’. \f ◼ \fr 2:6 \ft \+fk iribaɛen\ft  - niɣ ‘imitriten’ di tutlayt n Tyunanit. Ijj n zzaysen dayes ɛřaḥař tmanyin ař mya u-ɛicrin litru.\f*  
\v 7 Yasuɛ inna asen: “Ccurem iqeddwaḥ s waman!” Uca ccuren ten s waman ař aqemmum.  
\v 8 \add Xas uca\add* inna asen: “Řexxu ssfarrɣem \add cwayt\add* zzaysen, wcem t i bab n wurar.” Uca ssiwḍen t.  
\v 9 Umi bab n wurar iqeǧeb aman i idewřen d binu - \add maca\add* netta war issin manis dd-ikka, maca imsexxaren nni d as dd-yuymen aman, ssnen - iřaɣa-dd bab n tmeɣra x wesři.  
\v 10 Inna as: “Kuř bnadem ittqeddam binu aṣebḥan d amezwaru. Mařa inewjiwen swin aṭṭas, ad asen iwc binu war iḥřin, maca cek txemmřed binu iṣebḥen ař i řexxu.”   
\m
\v 11 D ta d řeɛřamet tamezwarut i igga Yasuɛ, di Qana di Ljalil. Isseḍhar-dd aɛuǧi nnes uca umnen zzayes imeḥḍaren nnes.  
\v 12 Awarni man aya ihwa-dd ɣar Kafarnaḥum, Netta d yemmas, d aytmas, d imeḥḍaren nnes, uca qqimen din ca n wussan.   
\b  
\m  
\s1 Yasuɛ di Zzawect Tameqqrant  
\m
\v 13 Řami dd-yiweḍ \add Řɛid n Tɣarṣt n\add* Useɛdu, Řɛid n Wudayen, igeɛɛed Yasuɛ ɣar Urcalim. \x ◘ \xo 2:13 \xt [Mt. 21:12-13; Mk. 11:15-17; Lk. 19:45-46]\x*  
\v 14 Yufa di Zzawect Tameqqrant inni din izznuzan iyenduzen d wuǧi d idbiren, uřa d iṣarrafen n tenɛacin i din iqqimen. \x ◘ \xo 2:14 \xt Mt. 21:12; Mk. 11:15; Lk. 19:45. \x*  
\v 15 Igga ijj n urekkuḍ zeg iseɣwan i Yixef nnes, uca yuẓẓeř xasen marra zi Zzawect Tameqqrant, uřa d uǧi d iyenduzen d iṣarrafen, uca izeǧeɛ iṣuldiyyen nsen di temmurt, inneqřeb ṭṭwabeř nsen.  
\v 16 Inna i yinni izznuzan idbiren: “Kksem man aya ssa! War ttarrim ca Taddart n Baba d taddart n ssuq!”  
\v 17 \add Xenni\add* ɛeqřen imeḥḍaren nnes belli tura: “Cḍaret i Taddart nnec icca ayi.” \x ◘ \xo 2:17 \xt Izhd. 69:10. \x*   
\m
\v 18 \add Maca\add* Udayen arrin-dd, nnan as: “Man řeɛřamet i d aneɣ ɣa temřed, belli \add aqa ɣarek řḥeqq ḥima\add* ad tegged man aya?” \x ◘ \xo 2:18 \xt Mt. 12:38; 16:1; Mk. 8:11; Lk. 11:29; Yḥ. 6:30. \x*  
\v 19 Yasuɛ yarra-dd, inna asen: “Hedmem Zzawect Tameqqrant tanita uca di třata n wussan ad tt ssbeddeɣ.” \x ◘ \xo 2:19 \xt Mt. 26:61; 27:40; Mk. 14:58; 15:29. \x*  
\v 20 Nnan as Wudayen: “Zzawect Tameqqrant tanita tebna di setta u-rebɛin n iseggʷusa, ma Cek texsed ad tt-i-dd-tessbedded di třata n wussan?”  
\v 21 Maca Netta tuɣa issawař x Zzawect Tameqqrant n Arrimet nnes.   
\m
\v 22 Awarni řami dd-ikkar Yasuɛ zi taddart n imettinen, ɛeqřen imeḥḍaren nnes min d asen inna, uca umnen di Tira \add Iqeddsen\add* u deg wawař i inna Yasuɛ. \x ◘ \xo 2:22 \xt Lk. 24:8. \x*   
\m
\v 23 Umi Yasuɛ tuɣa di Urcalim, di Řɛid n \add Tɣarṣt n\add* Useɛdu, umnen waṭṭas dayes řami ẓrin řeɛřamat i igga.  
\v 24 Maca Yasuɛ war isscen ca Ixef nnes ɣarsen, minzi Netta issen marra iwdan,  
\v 25 war iḥdij ca ad as iched ḥed x bnadem, minzi Netta s Yixef nnes issen min iǧan di bnadem. \x ◘ \xo 2:25 \xt 1 Ṣm. 16:7; 1 Im. 28:9; Izhd. 7:10; 103:14; Irm. 11:20; 17:10; 20:12; Yḥ. 6:64. \x*   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 3
\s1 Yasuɛ d Nikudimus  
\m
\v 1 Tuɣa din ijj n bnadem zeg Ifarisiyyen qqaren as Nikudimus, netta d ijj n umeqqran n Wudayen.  
\v 2 Yusa-dd ɣar Yasuɛ s ǧiřet, inna as: “\add A\add* Amseřmad inu, neccin nessen belli Cek d Amseɣɣar i dd-yusin zi ɣar AREBBI, minzi war izemmar uřa d ijj ad igg řeɛřamat-a i teggid Cek, mɣir mařa akides AREBBI.” \x ◘ \xo 3:2 \xt Yḥ. 7:50; 9:16, 33; 19:39; Řex. 10:38. \x*  
\v 3 Yarra-dd Yasuɛ, inna as: “S tidett, s tidett, Necc ad ac iniɣ, uřa d ijj war izemmar ad iẓar Tageldit n AREBBI mɣir mařa ittwaxřeq-dd zi jdid.”  
\v 4 Nikudimus inna as: “Mammec izemmar ijj n uwessar ad dd-ittwaxřeq \add ́́ɛad\add*? War izemmar ad yadef ɛawed deg uɛeddis n yemmas, maḥend ad dd-ittwaxřeq i twařa wiss tnayen?”  
\v 5 Yasuɛ yarra-dd, inna as: “S tidett, s tidett, Necc ad ac iniɣ: Mařa ca n yijjen war dd-ixřiq ca zeg waman u zeg Arruḥ, war izemmar ad yadef ɣar Tgeldit n AREBBI. \x ◘ \xo 3:5 \xt Tit. 3:5. \x*  
\v 6 Min dd-ittwaxeřqen zi ddat, netta d ddat, u min dd-ittwaxeřqen zi Arruḥ, netta d Arruḥ. \x ◘ \xo 3:6 \xt Rum. 8:5. \x*  
\v 7 War tbehtem ca mařa nniɣ ac, ittxeṣṣa kenniw ad dd-tᵉttwaxeřqem zi jdid.  
\v 8 Asemmiḍ ittsuḍ manis ixs, tᵉttesřid i usuḍi nnes, war tessined ca manis dd-ittas uřa mani ittraḥ. Ammu i iǧa ɛawed marra wenni dd-ittwaxeřqen zi Arruḥ.”   
\m
\v 9 Nikudimus yarra-dd, inna as: “Mammec i ɣa yegg ad yiři man aya?”  
\v 10 Yasuɛ yarra-dd, inna as: “Ma Cek d amseɣɣar n Israil u war tessined ca man aya?  
\v 11 S tidett, s tidett, Necc ad ac iniɣ: Neccin nessawař x min nessen, neched x min neẓra, waxxa amenni kenniw war teqbiřem ca cchadet Nneɣ. \x ◘ \xo 3:11 \xt Yḥ. 3:32; 7:16; 8:28; 12:49; 14:24. \x*  
\v 12 Mařa ssiwřeɣ awem x min iǧan x temmurt, kenniw war timnem, mammec ɣa teggem ad tamnem mařa ssiwřeɣ awem x min iǧan deg ujenna?  
\v 13 Uřa d ijj war yuři ɣar ujenna mɣir wenni dd-ihwan zeg ujenna, aqa-t d Mmis n bnadem, d Wenni iǧan deg ujenna. \x ◘ \xo 3:13 \xt Dan. 7:13; Yḥ. 6:62; Afa. 4:9. \x*   
\m
\v 14 Am mammec issgeɛɛed Musa afiɣar di řefyafi, ammu ittxeṣṣa ad ittwassgeɛɛed Mmis n bnadem \add ɛawed\add*, \x ◘ \xo 3:14 \xt Řxř. 21:4-9; 2 Ij. 18:4; Yḥ. 8:28; 12:32. \x*  
\v 15 ḥima marra wenni zzayes i ɣa yamnen, war itthellik ca, maca ad ɣares tiři Tudart ittduman. \x ◘ \xo 3:15 \xt Yḥ. 3:15. \x*  
\v 16 Ammu i yexs AREBBI ddunect ař mani iwca ayenni n Mmis, ḥima kuř ijjen wenni zzayes i ɣa yamnen, war ihellik ca, maca ad ɣares tiři Tudart ittduman. \x ◘ \xo 3:16 \xt Yḥ. 3:36; Lk. 19:10; Rum. 5:8; 8:31; 1 Yḥ. 4:9; 5:10. \x*  
\v 17 Minzi AREBBI war dd-issekk ca Mmis ɣar ddunect, ḥima ad iḥaseb ddunect, maca issekk i-t-i-dd ḥima ad zzayes teddar ddunect. \x ◘ \xo 3:17 \xt Lk. 9:56; Yḥ. 9:39; 12:47; 1 Yḥ. 4:14. \x*  
\v 18 Wenni zzayes i ɣa yamnen, war ittwaḥasab ca. Wenni war ittimnen ca, aqa ittwaḥaseb zi řexxu, minzi netta war yumin ca deg Yisem n uyenni n Mmis n AREBBI. \x ◘ \xo 3:18 \xt Yḥ. 5:24; 6:40,47; 20:31. \x*  
\v 19 D wa d řeḥkam, aqa Tafawt tusa-dd ɣar ddunect, \add maca\add* iwdan xsen taǧest x Tfawt, minzi timegga nsen tuɣa atent d tiɛeffanin. \x ◘ \xo 3:19 \xt Yḥ. 1:5. \x*  
\v 20 Marra wenni itteggen tuɛeffna, icarreh Tafawt, war dd-ittis ca ɣar Tfawt, ḥima war ttwawebbxent ca timegga nnes.  
\v 21 Maca wenni itteggen tidett ad dd-yas ɣar Tfawt, ḥima ad banent timegga nnes, aqa ttwaggent di AREBBI.” \x ◘ \xo 3:21 \xt Afa. 5:8, 13. \x*   
\b  
\m  
\s1 Cchadet wiss tnayen n Yuḥanna Amseɣḍaṣ  
\m
\v 22 Awarni man aya yusa-dd Yasuɛ d imeḥḍaren nnes ɣar temmurt n Yahudiyya, isseɛdu din ca n řweqt akidsen uca tuɣa isseɣḍaṣ. \x ◘ \xo 3:22 \xt Yḥ. 4:1. \x*  
\v 23 Uřa d Yuḥanna tuɣa isseɣḍaṣ di Ɛaynun i dd-yusin ṭṭarf i Salim, minzi dinni aman aṭṭas. Usin-dd \add iwdan\add* dinni uca ttwassɣeḍṣen, \x ◘ \xo 3:23 \xt Mt. 3:6; Mk. 1:5; Lk. 3:7. \x*  
\v 24 minzi Yuḥanna tuɣa ɛad war immenḍar ca di řeḥbes. \x ◘ \xo 3:24 \xt Mt. 14:3. \x*   
\m
\v 25 Imsar ijj n umḥarweḍ jar ijjen zeg imeḥḍaren n Yuḥanna d ijj n Wuday x mammec ɣa yiři řuḍu.  
\v 26 Nitni usin-dd ɣar Yuḥanna, nnan as: “\add A\add* Amseřmad nneɣ, xzar, wenni akidek iǧan x ujemmaḍ n L’Urdun, wenni min xef tcehded, aqa uřa d Netta isseɣḍaṣ u marra ttasen-dd ɣares.” \x ◘ \xo 3:26 \xt Mt. 3:11; Mk. 1:7; Lk. 3:16; Yḥ. 1:15, 26, 34. \x*  
\v 27 Yarra-dd Yuḥanna, inna asen: “Bnadem war izemmar ad iqbeř uřa d ict n tmesřact mařa war d as temmewc zeg ujenna.  
\v 28 Kenniw simant nwem tcehhdem belli necc nniɣ: ‘Necc war ǧiɣ ca d Lmasiḥ!’, maca aqa necc ttwassekkeɣ-dd zzates. \x ◘ \xo 3:28 \xt Mal. 3:1; Mt. 11:10; Mk. 1:2; Lk. 1:17; 7:27; Yḥ. 1:20, 21, 23. \x*  
\v 29 Wenni ɣar teǧa tesřit, netta d asři. Ameddukkeř n wesři wenni ittbeddan \add zzates\add*, ittesřa ɣares, ifarreḥ s řefraḥet tameqqrant s tmijja n wesři. S uyenni, xzar, aqa tᵉttwakemmeř řefraḥet inu tanita.  
\v 30 Ittxeṣṣa ad igma Netta u necc ad neqṣeɣ.  
\v 31 Maɣar wenni dd-yusin zi sennej, Netta sennej i marra. Wenni iǧan zi temmurt, zi temmurt issawař. Wenni dd-yusin zeg ujenna, Netta sennej i marra, \x ◘ \xo 3:31 \xt Yḥ. 8:23. \x*  
\v 32 u Netta icehhed zi min iẓra d zi min isřa, \add maca\add* cchadet nnes war tt iqebbiř uřa d ijjen. \x ◘ \xo 3:32 \xt Yḥ. 5:30; 8:26; 12:49; 14:10; 1 Yḥ. 5:10. \x*  
\v 33 Wenni iqebbřen cchadet nnes d wenni issarsen ṭṭabeɛ nnes n ucemmiɛ belli aqa AREBBI d tidett. \x ◘ \xo 3:33 \xt Ayub Rum. 3:4. \x*  
\v 34 Minzi wenni dd-issekk AREBBI, issawař s wawařen n AREBBI, minzi AREBBI war ittic ca Arruḥ s řmizan. \x ◘ \xo 3:34 \xt Afa. 4:7. \x*  
\v 35 Babas ittexs Mmis uca igga as kuřci deg ifassen nnes. \x ◘ \xo 3:35 \xt Mt. 11:27; 28:18; Lk. 10:22; Yḥ. 5:22; 17:2; Ɛbr. 2:8. \x*  
\v 36 Wenni ittamnen di Mmis ɣares Tudart ittduman, maca wenni war iṭṭiɛ ca Mmis, war iẓarr Tudart, \add maɣar\add* aɣḍab n AREBBI ad xas iqqim.” \x ◘ \xo 3:36 \xt Yḥ. 3:36; 6:47; 1 Yḥ. 5:10. \x*   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 4
\s1 Yasuɛ ak-d temɣart zi Samariya  
\m
\v 1 \add Umi\add* issen Yasuɛ, aqa Ifarisiyyen sřin belli Netta ittegg u issɣeṭṭaṣ imeḥḍaren ktar zi Yuḥanna \x ◘ \xo 4:1 \xt Yḥ. 3:26. \x*  
\v 2 - waxxa Yasuɛ simant nnes war isseɣḍiṣ ca, maca imeḥḍaren nnes -  
\v 3 iffeɣ-dd zi Yahudiyya, iruḥ ɛawed ɣar Ljalil.  
\v 4 Maca tuɣa ittxeṣṣa ad icuq di Samarya.  
\v 5 Netta yusa-dd ɣar ict n tendint n Isamariyyen, qqaren as Suxar, tenni ɣar ṭṭarf n iyyar i iwca Yaɛqub i mmis Yusuf. \x ◘ \xo 4:5 \xt Amz. 33:19; 48:22; Yac. 24:32. \x*  
\v 6 Tuɣa din anu n Yaɛqub. Yuḥeř Yasuɛ zeg ibriden uca iruḥ iqqim amenni ɣar wanu, tuɣa tasaɛɛet d setta, \add ixs ad yini azyen n wass\add*. \f ◼ \fr 4:6 \ft \+fk tuɣa tasaɛɛet d setta\ft  - man aya ixs ad yini: tuɣa azyen n wass (ḍḍuhr).\f*   
\m
\v 7 Tusa-dd ict n temɣart zi Samarya ḥima ad tagem aman. Yasuɛ inna as: “Ewc ayi aman, ad sweɣ!”,  
\v 8 minzi imeḥḍaren nnes tuɣa ruḥen ɣar tendint maḥend ad sɣen macca i yixef nsen.  
\v 9 Tamɣart n Samarya tenna as: “Mammec teggid tᵉttared zzayi ad teswed, aqa Cek d Uday u necc d tamɣart zi Samarya?” Minzi Udayen war nnumen ttemṣurufen ak-d imezdaɣ n Samarya. \x ◘ \xo 4:9 \xt Lk. 9:52, 53; Yḥ. 8:48. \x*  
\v 10 Yasuɛ yarra-dd, inna as: “Maɛlik tessned timewca n AREBBI d wenni d am iqqaren: ‘Ewc ayi ad sweɣ!’, iři cem tᵉttar tt zzayes, uca Netta ad yiři iwc am Aman Iddaren.”  
\v 11 Tenna as temɣart: “\add A\add* Sidi, war ɣarek i zi ɣa tagmed uca anu yuǧeɣ, manis i d ɣa tawyed Aman Iddaren? \x ◘ \xo 4:11 \xt Irm. 2:13. \x*  
\v 12 Ma Cek d ameqqran zi jedditneɣ Yaɛqub wenni d aneɣ iwcin anu wanita, iswa zzayes, netta d tarwa nnes d řebhayem nnes?”  
\v 13 Yasuɛ yarra-dd, inna as: “Marra wenni i ɣa iswen zeg waman-a, ad ifud ɛawed,  
\v 14 maca wenni i ɣa iswen zeg waman i d as ɣa wceɣ Necc, netta war ittfadi ɛemmarṣ. Minzi aman i d as ɣa wceɣ Necc, ad dayes dewřen d řɛunṣar n waman i dd itteffɣen ɣar Tudart ittduman.” \x ◘ \xo 4:14 \xt Yḥ. 3:16; 6:27, 35, 54; 7:38. \x*  
\v 15 Tamɣart tenna as: “\add A\add* Sidi, ewc ayi aman-a ḥima war ttfideɣ, war dd-ttiseɣ ɛad da, ḥima ad agmeɣ.”   
\m
\v 16 Inna as Yasuɛ: “Ruḥ, řaɣa-dd i weryaz nnem uca dweř-dd danita.”  
\v 17 Nettat tenna as: “War ɣari bu weryaz!” Yasuɛ inna as: “Tessiwřed nican umi tennid: ‘War ɣari bu weryaz!’,  
\v 18 minzi tuɣa ɣarem xemsa n yeryazen d wenni ɣarem řexxu, war iǧi bu d aryaz nnem. Man aya i tennid d tidett.”   
\m
\v 19 Tamɣart tenna as: “\add A\add* Sidi, ttwařiɣ belli Cek d anabi. \x ◘ \xo 4:19 \xt Lk. 7:16; 24:19; Yḥ. 6:14. \x*  
\v 20 Řejdud nneɣ sejden deg wedrar-a, maca kenniw teqqarem belli di Urcalim mani iǧa wemcan i di icuwwar ad nesjed.” \x ◘ \xo 4:20 \xt Aɛwd. 12:5, 11; 1 Ij. 9:3; 2 Im. 7:12. \x*  
\v 21 Yasuɛ inna as: “Ttiqq ayi, \add a\add* tameṭṭut, aqa tasaɛɛet ad dd-tas i di war tɛebbdem Baba uřa deg wedrar-a uřa di Urcalim.  
\v 22 Kenniw tɛebbdem min war tessinem, \add maca\add* neccin nɛebbed min nessen, minzi Tudart zeg Wudayen. \x ◘ \xo 4:22 \xt Amz. 12:3; 18:18; 22:18; 26:4; 2 Ij. 17:29; Ɛbr. 7:14. \x*  
\v 23 Maca ad dd-taweḍ tsaɛɛet, nettat aqa-tt řexxu, belli inni iɛebbden nican, ad ɛebden Baba di Arruḥ u di tidett, minzi Baba yarezzu inni t i ɣa iɛebden ammu.  
\v 24 AREBBI d Arruḥ u inni t iɛebbden, ittxeṣṣa asen ad ɛebden s Arruḥ d tidett.” \x ◘ \xo 4:24 \xt 2 Kur. 3:17. \x*   
\m
\v 25 Tamɣart tenna as: “Necc ssneɣ belli ad dd-yas Lmasiḥ. Xmi dd ɣa yas Netta, ad aneɣ isseřmed kuřci.”  
\v 26 Yasuɛ inna as: “Aqa d NECC, wenni kim issawařen.” \x ◘ \xo 4:26 \xt Yḥ. 9:37. \x*   
\m
\v 27 Am tuɣa issawař, usin-dd imeḥḍaren nnes, ttɛejben řami t ufin issawař ak-d ict n temɣart. Waxxa amenni uřa d ijj war ini: “Min tarezzud?” niɣ: “Mayemmi akides tessawařed?”  
\v 28 \add Xas uca\add* tejja temɣart aqedduḥ nnes s waman, tuyur ɣar tendint, tenna i iwdan:  
\v 29 “Araḥem-dd, ad tẓarem Aryaz i d ayi inna marra min ggiɣ. Ma \add ad taɣ\add* Netta d Lmasiḥ?”  
\v 30 Iwdan ffɣen-dd zi tendint, usin-dd ɣares.   
\m
\v 31 Jar u jar ttaren \add zzayes\add* imeḥḍaren nnes, nnan: “\add A\add* Amseřmad nneɣ, ecc!”  
\v 32 Maca Netta inna asen: “Necc aqa ɣari ijj n macca ḥima ad zzayes ittwacc, war tt tessinem ca kenniw.”  
\v 33 Imeḥḍaren mmseqsan jar asen: “Ma yiwyi as-dd ḥed ca n macca?”  
\v 34 Yasuɛ inna asen: “Macca inu aqa ad ggeɣ min ixs wenni d ayi dd-issekken u ad kemmřeɣ řxedmet nnes.  
\v 35 Ma war teqqarem: ‘Iqqim ɛad arebɛa n iyuren uca ad dd-tas ṣṣabet’?’ Xzarem, Necc ad awem iniɣ, sgeɛɛdem tiṭṭawin nwem, xzarem deg iyyaren, aqa warɣen, wejden i ṣṣabet. \x ◘ \xo 4:35 \xt Mt. 9:37; Lk. 10:2. \x*  
\v 36 Wenni imejjaren ad iksi řmunet nnes, iyru řɣiǧet i Tudart ittduman, ḥima ad farḥen jmiɛ wenni izarrɛen d wenni imejjaren.  
\v 37 Minzi di man aya aqa awař-a d tidett: ‘Ijjen ad izarɛ u wenneɣni ad imjar.’  
\v 38 Necc ssekkeɣ-dd kenniw ḥima ad temjarem min umi war texdimem kenniw. Inneɣni tuɣa xeddmen, kenniw tudfem ɣar řxedmet nsen.”   
\m
\v 39 Aṭṭas n Isamariyyen zi tendint nni umnen zzayes x wawař n temɣart i tuɣa icehhden: “Netta inna ayi marra min ggiɣ.”  
\v 40 Řami ɣares dd-usin Isamariyyen nni, sseqsan t ḥima akidsen iqqim, uca iqqim akidsen tnayen n wussan dinni.  
\v 41 Uca aṭṭas umnen zzayes zi ssibbet n wawař nnes,  
\v 42 nnan i temɣart nni: “Neccin war nettimen ca ɛad zi min d aneɣ tennid, minzi neccin nesřa i-t s yixef nneɣ, nessen belli Wa s tidett d Lmasiḥ, wenni itticen Tudart i ddunect.”   
\b  
\m  
\s1 Asgenfi n mmis n umsexxar n ujeǧid  
\m
\v 43 Awarni tnayen n wussan iffeɣ-dd Yasuɛ ssenni, iruḥ ɣar Ljalil. \x ◘ \xo 4:43 \xt [Mt. 8:5-13; Lk. 7:1-10]\x*  
\v 44 Minzi Yasuɛ simant nnes aqa iched belli anabi war ɣares bu ccan di temmurt nnes. \x ◘ \xo 4:44 \xt Mt. 13:57; Mk. 6:4; Lk. 4:24. \x*  
\v 45 Umi dd-yusa ɣar Ljalil, areḥḥben t-i-dd Ijaliliyyen, minzi nitni ẓrin marra min igga di Řɛid di Urcalim, minzi uřa d nitni usin-dd ɣar Řɛid.   
\m
\v 46 Yusa-dd Yasuɛ ɛawed ɣar \add tendint n\add* Qana di Ljalil mani yarra aman d binu. Tuɣa din ijj n umsexxar n ujeǧid di Kafarnaḥum ɣares mmis ihřec. \x ◘ \xo 4:46 \xt Yḥ. 2:1, 11. \x*  
\v 47 Řami isřa belli Yasuɛ yusa-dd zi Yahudiyya ɣar Ljalil, iruḥ ɣares, isseqsa t ḥima ad dd-ihwa maḥend ad issgenfa mmis, wenni tuɣa igguren ad immet.  
\v 48 Yasuɛ inna as: “Kenniw war ttimnem ca mařa war teẓrim řeɛřamat d lmuɛjizat.” \x ◘ \xo 4:48 \xt 1 Kur. 1:22. \x*  
\v 49 Inna as uxeddam n ujeǧid: “\add A\add* Sidi, hwa-dd qbeř i ɣa immet uḥenjir inu.”  
\v 50 Yasuɛ inna as: “Ruḥ aqa mmic iddar!” Aryaz nni ittiqq deg wawař i d as inna Yasuɛ uca iruḥ.   
\m
\v 51 Řami dd-ihwa, mmeřqan akides imsexxaren nnes, xebbaren t, nnan as: “Aqa mmic iddar”.  
\v 52 Isseqsa ten x tsaɛɛet min di iggenfa. Nnan as: “Iḍennaḍ ɣar tsaɛɛet wiss sebɛa, \add ixs ad yini ɣar tsaɛɛet tamezwarut n uziř,\add* tejja xas tmessi.”  
\v 53 Xenni issen babas belli aqa imsar ɣar tsaɛɛet i d as inna Yasuɛ: “Aqa mmic iddar!” Yumen netta d marra aytbab n taddart nnes.   
\m
\v 54 Ta tuɣa ɛawed d řeɛřamet wiss tnayen i igga Yasuɛ zeg wami dd-iffeɣ zi Yahudiyya ɣar Ljalil.   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 5
\s1 Asgenfi n ijj n umehřuc di Bayt-Xisda  
\m
\v 1 Awarni man aya yiweḍ-dd Řɛid n Wudayen uca igeɛɛed Yasuɛ ɣar Urcalim. \x ◘ \xo 5:1 \xt Lawi 23:2; Aɛwd. 16:1. \x*  
\v 2 \add Ɣar Tewwart n Wuǧi\add* di Urcalim tuɣa din ict n tyeřmamt n useɣḍeṣ umi qqaren s Tɛibranit ‘Bayt-Xisda’, tuɣa ɣares xemsa n iseqqifen ak-d ikulwaren d ipilaren.  
\v 3 Daysen tuɣa iqqim ijj n řɣaci d ameqqran n imehřac d idarɣařen d iqejdaḥen d ineɛḍaben, ttrajan anhezzi n waman.  
\v 4 Minzi zi řweqt ɣar řweqt ihekkwa-dd ijj n lmalak ɣar tyeřmamt-a n useɣḍeṣ, issenhezza aman, u wenni i dd ɣa ihwan d amezwaru awarni anhezzi n waman, ad ittwassgenfa, mammec ma iǧa řehřac nnes.   
\m
\v 5 Tuɣa din ijj n bnadem dayes řehřac i yijj n řmijař n tmenya u-třatin n iseggʷusa.  
\v 6 Iẓra Yasuɛ aryaz-a isenned dinni, issen belli tuɣa \add iḥřec ammu\add* aṭṭas zeg wami. Inna as: “Ma texsed ad teggenfid?”  
\v 7 Yarra-dd xas umehřuc, inna: “Wah, \add a\add* Sidi, maca war ɣari ijjen wenni d ayi ɣa yiwyen ɣar tuyeřmamt n useɣḍeṣ xmi ɣa ttwassenhezzen waman. Xmi ttraḥeɣ necc, ihekkwa-dd wenneɣni zzati.”  
\v 8 Yasuɛ inna as: “Kkar, teksid tassut nnec, tuyured!” \x ◘ \xo 5:8 \xt Mt. 9:6; Mk. 2:11; Lk. 5:24. \x*  
\v 9 Deɣya iggenfa bnadem nni uca iksi tassut nnes, yuyur. Man aya tuɣa deg wass n ssebt. \x ◘ \xo 5:9 \xt Yḥ. 9:14. \x*   
\m
\v 10 Nnan Wudayen i wenni tuɣa ittwassgenfan: “Wa d ssebt, war ɣarek bu ttesriḥ maḥend ad teksid tassut nnec!” \x ◘ \xo 5:10 \xt Uf. 20:10; Aɛwd. 5:13; Irm. 17:21; Mt. 12:2; Mk. 2:24; Lk. 6:2. \x*  
\v 11 Yarra-dd, inna asen: “Wenni d ayi issgenfan, inna: ‘Ksi tassut nnec, traḥed!’”  
\v 12 \add Xenni\add* sseqsan t: “Min iɛna Bnadem-a i d ac innan: ‘Ksi tassut nnec, traḥed’?”  
\v 13 Wenni ittwassgenfan war issin min iɛna Yasuɛ, minzi innejra minzi aqa din aṭṭas n řɣaci deg wemcan nni.   
\m
\v 14 Awarni man aya yufa i-t Yasuɛ di Zzawect Tameqqrant, inna as: “Xzar, aqa teggenfid, war ttegg bu ddnub ɛad, ḥima war d ac ittemsar min iǧan d aɛeffan zi min iǧan qbeř.” \x ◘ \xo 5:14 \xt Mt. 12:45; Yḥ. 8:11. \x*   
\m
\v 15 Aryaz iruḥ, ixebbar Udayen belli d Yasuɛ i-t issgenfan.   
\m
\v 16 S uyenni darrcen Wudayen x Yasuɛ, arezzun ad t nɣen, minzi igga man aya di ssebt.  
\v 17 Maca Yasuɛ yarra-dd, inna asen: “Aqa Baba ixeddem ař yiḍa u \add xenni\add* Necc ɛawed aqa xeddmeɣ.” \x ◘ \xo 5:17 \xt Yḥ. 14:10. \x*  
\v 18 Di ssibbet-a arezzun Wudayen ɛad ktar ḥima ad t nɣen, war iǧi waha minzi ixařef ssebt, maca uřa minzi Netta inna aqa AREBBI d Babas, issqudda Ixef nnes ak-d AREBBI. \x ◘ \xo 5:18 \xt Yḥ. 7:19. \x*  
\v 19 Yarra-dd Yasuɛ, inna asen: “S tidett, s tidett, Necc ad awem iniɣ, Mmis war izemmar ad igg uřa d ict n tmesřact s Yixef nnes, mɣir mařa iẓra Babas ittegg i-tt. Min ma ittegg Babas uřa d Mmis ittegg amenni. \x ◘ \xo 5:19 \xt Ica. 54:5; Yḥ. 3:30; 8:38; 9:4; 10:30; 14:9; 17:5. \x*  
\v 20 Babas ittexs Mmis, isscen as marra min ittegg, uca ad as isscen řexdayem timeqqranin x tina, ḥima ad tdehcem. \x ◘ \xo 5:20 \xt Yḥ. 1:2; 3:35; 7:16; 8:28; 14:24. \x*  
\v 21 Am mammec d issnekkar Babas imettinen uca ittic tudart, amenni uřa d Mmis ittic tudart i wenni ixs.  
\v 22 Babas war ittḥasab uřa d ijj, maca iwca lḥisab marra i Mmis \x ◘ \xo 5:22 \xt Mt. 11:27; Yḥ. 3:35. \x*  
\v 23 ḥima ad weqqaren marra Mmis am ttweqqaren Babas. Wenni war ittweqqaren Mmis war ittweqqar ca uřa d Baba wenni i-t-i-dd-issekken. \x ◘ \xo 5:23 \xt Yḥ. 2:23. \x*   
\m
\v 24 S tidett, s tidett, Necc ad awem iniɣ: Wenni ittesřan i wawař inu uca yumen deg wenni d ayi dd-issekken, ɣares Tudart ittduman, war dd-ittis ca ɣar lḥisab, maca netta aqa immuṭṭi zi řmewt ɣar Tudart. \x ◘ \xo 5:24 \xt Lk. 23:43; Yḥ. 3:18; 6:40, 47; 8:51. \x*  
\v 25 S tidett, s tidett, Necc ad awem iniɣ: Ad dd-tas tsaɛɛet, aqa-tt řexxu, i di imettinen ad sřen tmijja n Mmis n AREBBI u inni i \add tt\add* ɣa isřen, ad ddaren. \x ◘ \xo 5:25 \xt Afa. 2:1, 5; 1 Tim. 5:6. \x*  
\v 26 Maɣar am mammec Babas ɣares Tudart di ṭṭbiɛet n Yixef nnes, ammu i iwca uřa i Mmis ḥima ad ɣares tiři Tudart di ṭṭbiɛet n Yixef nnes,  
\v 27 uca iwca as ṣṣulṭa ḥima ad iḥaseb, minzi Netta d Mmis n bnadem.  
\v 28 War ttɛejibem ca s man aya, aqa ad dd-tas tsaɛɛet i di marra inni iǧan deg imeḍřan ad sřen tmijja nnes, \x ◘ \xo 5:28 \xt 1 Ts. 4:16. \x*  
\v 29 uca ad dd-ffɣen \add zeg imeḍřan\add*: inni iggin taṣebḥant ad kkaren ad raḥen ɣar tnukra i tudart, u inni iggin tuɛeffna ad kkaren, ad raḥen ɣar tnukra i lḥisab. \x ◘ \xo 5:29 \xt Dan. 12:2; Mt. 25:34,46. \x*   
\m
\v 30 Necc war zemmareɣ ad ggeɣ ca zeg Ixef inu, maca am mammec ttesřiɣ, ad ḥasbeɣ u lḥisab inu d řḥeqq, minzi Necc war arezzuɣ min xseɣ, maca min ixs Wenni d ayi dd-issekken. \x ◘ \xo 5:30 \xt Yḥ. 6:38. \x*  
\v 31 Meɛlik cehhdeɣ i ixef inu, iři aqa cchadet inu war teǧi ca nican. \x ◘ \xo 5:31 \xt Yḥ. 8:14. \x*  
\v 32 Aqa din Ijjen nneɣni wi xafi icehhden, u Necc ssneɣ belli cchadet i xafi icehhed, aqa d tidett i teǧa. \x ◘ \xo 5:32 \xt Ica. 42:1; Mt. 3:17; 17:5. \x*  
\v 33 Kenniw tessekkem-dd \add ca n ireqqasen\add* ɣar Yuḥanna uca netta iched i tidett. \x ◘ \xo 5:33 \xt Yḥ. 1:15, 19, 27. \x*  
\v 34 Maca Necc war qebbřeɣ ca cchadet n bnadem, maca Necc qqareɣ \add marra\add* man aya ḥima ad teddarem.  
\v 35 Tuɣa Netta d řefnar yareqqen, ittlillicen, u kenniw texsem ad tfarḥem s tfawt nnes ɣar ict n tsaɛɛet.  
\v 36 Maca Necc ɣari ict n cchadet d tameqqrant x tenni n Yuḥanna, minzi řexdayem i d ayi iwca Baba, ḥima ad tent kemmřeɣ, řexdayem nni i tteggeɣ cehhdent simant nsent aqa d Baba d Netta i d ayi dd-issekken. \x ◘ \xo 5:36 \xt Yḥ. 10:25; 1 Yḥ. 5:9. \x*  
\v 37 Baba, wenni d ayi-dd issekken, d Netta i xafi icehhden. Kenniw ɛemmarṣ war tesřim tmijja nnes uca war teẓrim ca udem nnes, \x ◘ \xo 5:37 \xt Uf. 33:20; Aɛwd. 4:12; Mt. 3:17; 17:5; Mk. 1:11; 9:7; Lk. 3:22; 9:35; Yḥ. 1:33; 6:27; 8:18; 1 Tim. 6:16; 2 Bṭ. 1:17; 1 Yḥ. 4:12. \x*  
\v 38 uca awař nnes war daywem ittɣimi ca řebda, minzi kenniw war tᵉttimnen ca deg wenni i-t-i-dd-issekken.  
\v 39 Arzum di Tira \add Iqeddsen\add*, minzi ittɣiř awem aqa daysent Tudart ittduman, u aqa atent d inni i xafi icehhden. \x ◘ \xo 5:39 \xt Aɛwd. 18:18; Ica. 34:16; Lk. 16:29; 24:27; Yḥ. 1:46; Řex. 17:11. \x*  
\v 40 \add Waxxa amenni\add* kenniw war tᵉttexsem ad ɣari dd-tasem ḥima ad ɣarwem tiři Tudart ittduman.   
\m
\v 41 War qebbřeɣ ca aɛuǧi n iwdan,  
\v 42 maca ssneɣ kenniw, aqa kenniw war ɣarwem bu tayri n AREBBI deg ixef nwem.  
\v 43 Necc usiɣ-dd s Yisem n Baba, kenniw war d ayi tqebbřem ca. Mařa yusa-dd ca n yijjen s yisem nnes, ad t tqebřem.  
\v 44 Mammec tzemmarem ad tamnem, mařa kenniw tᵉttexsem aɛuǧi n wayawya, maca war tarezzum ca x uɛuǧi n uyenni n AREBBI d Ijjen? \x ◘ \xo 5:44 \xt Yḥ. 12:43. \x*  
\v 45 Ma ittɣiř awem ad zzaywem cetciɣ ɣar Baba? Wenni zzaywem i ɣa icetcan d Musa x wenni tessrusam asitem nwem.  
\v 46 Minzi meɛlik tumnem zi Musa, iři tumnem dayi ɛawed, minzi netta yura xafi. \x ◘ \xo 5:46 \xt Amz. 3:15; 22:18; 26:4; 28:14; Aɛwd. 18:18. \x*  
\v 47 Mařa kenniw war tuminem ca deg Idlisen nnes, mammec ɣa teggem ad tamnem deg wawařen inu?”   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 6
\s1 Lmuɛjiza n usecci n xemsa ařaf  
\m
\v 1 Awarni man aya iruḥ Yasuɛ ɣar ujemmaḍ n řebḥar n Ljalil, wenni umi qqaren ɛawed \add řebḥar n\add* Tibiriyas. \x ◘ \xo 6:1 \xt [Mt. 14:13-21; Mk. 6:30-44; Lk. 9:10-17]\x*  
\v 2 Iḍfar i-t-i-dd ijj n řɣaci d ameqqran, minzi ẓrin řeɛřamat i igga i imehřac.  
\v 3 Řexdenni igeɛɛed Yasuɛ ɣar wedrar uca iqqim dinni ak-d imeḥḍaren nnes.  
\v 4 Iqarreb-dd Řɛid n Tɣarṣt n Useɛdu n Wudayen. \x ◘ \xo 6:4 \xt Uf. 12:18; Lawi 23:5, 7; Řxř. 28:16; Aɛwd. 16:1. \x*   
\m
\v 5 Řexdenni issgeɛɛed Yasuɛ tiṭṭawin nnes uca, umi iẓra ijj n řɣaci d ameqqran yusa-dd ɣares, inna i Filippus: “Manis i ɣa nseɣ aɣrum, ḥima ad ccen ina?” \x ◘ \xo 6:5 \xt Mt. 14:14; Mk. 6:34; Lk. 9:13. \x*  
\v 6 Inna ammu ḥima ad t ijarreb, minzi Netta issen min ɣa yegg.  
\v 7 Yarra-dd xas Filippus: “Aɣrum s mitayen dinar war ten ittqeddi, \add ɛad\add* mařa kuř ijjen zzaysen ad iksi \add mɣir\add* drus \add waha\add*.”  
\v 8 Ijjen zeg imeḥḍaren nnes, netta d Andrawus, umas n Cimɛun Buṭrus, inna as:  
\v 9 “Aqa da ijj n uḥenjir ɣares xemsa n tecnifin n imendi d tnayen n iseřman, maca man aya war ittqeddi i marra ina!”   
\m
\v 10 Yasuɛ inna asen: “Sɣimem iwdan.” Tuɣa din aṭṭas n arbiɛ deg wemcan nni. S uyenni qqimen yeryazen, aqa aten di xemsa-ařaf idsen.  
\v 11 Yasuɛ iksi ticnifin, u awarni řami ibarek i tent, ibḍa i-tent x yinni \add din\add* iqqimen. \add Ibḍa Netta\add* amenni ɛawed iseřman, ɛlaḥsab anect ixsen \add ad ccen\add*. \x ◘ \xo 6:11 \xt 1 Ṣm. 9:13. \x*  
\v 12 Řami jjiwnen, inna i imeḥḍaren nnes: “Yrumem iřeqqwaz iceṭṭen, ḥima uřa d ict n řḥajjet war tᵉttḍeyyiɛ!”  
\v 13 Yrun ten uca ɛemmaren tenɛac n tsuǧatin s iřeqqwaz nni iceṭṭen ɣar yinni iccin zi xemsa n tecnifin n imendi.   
\m
\v 14 Řami ẓrin iwdan řeɛřamet i igga Yasuɛ, nnan: “Wa d tidett d Anabi i igguren ad dd-yas ɣar ddunect.” \x ◘ \xo 6:14 \xt Aɛwd. 18:15, 18; Aɛwd. 34:10; Lk. 7:16; 24:19; Yḥ. 4:19. \x*  
\v 15 Umi issen Yasuɛ, belli ad dd-asen nitni, ad t ṭṭfen ḥima ad t ggen d ajeǧid, xenni innejra ɣar wedrar, ḥaca Netta weḥḥdes.   
\b  
\m  
\s1 Yasuɛ iggur x waman n řebḥar  
\m
\v 16 Řami dd-tewḍa tmeddit, hwan-dd imeḥḍaren nnes ɣar řebḥar, \x ◘ \xo 6:16 \xt [Mt. 14:22-27; Mk. 6:45-52] — Mt. 14:23; Mk. 6:47. \x*  
\v 17 u \add awarni řami\add* nyin di tɣarrabut, qeḍɛen \add řebḥar\add* ɣar Kafarnaḥum. Tqarreb-dd taǧest u Yasuɛ tuɣa ɛad war ɣarsen dd-yusi.  
\v 18 Řebḥar innehweř xasen, minzi asemmiḍ tuɣa ittsuḍ aṭṭas.  
\v 19 Ařami tuɣa qeddfen řqedd n ɛřaḥař xemsa u-ɛicrin ař třatin ‘istadiyyen’, \add ɛřaḥař xemsa kilumitr\add*, ẓrin Yasuɛ iggur x řebḥar, ittqarrab-dd ɣar tɣarrabut nsen, uca ggʷeden. \f ◼ \fr 6:19 \ft \+fk istadiyyen\ft  
\fp  ijj n řmeřɛeb di řweqt n Iyunaniyyen tuɣa ɣares ict tuzzugart n 185 mitr, ixs ad yini ‘ijj n ustadiy’.\f*  
\v 20 \add Maca\add* Netta inna asen: “Aqa d NECC, war tteggʷedem ca.”  
\v 21 Nitni xsen ad t ssqebřen di tɣarrabut, uca xenni tiweḍ-dd tɣarrabut deɣya ɣar řbarr i ɣar iǧa ttraḥen.   
\m
\v 22 Tiwecca nnes iẓra řɣaci nni ibedd x ujemmaḍ n řebḥar, belli war din tuɣi uřa d ict n tɣarrabut nneɣnit mɣir icten, tenni mani dayes udfen imeḥḍaren nnes, u Yasuɛ war yudif ca di tɣarrabut ak-d imeḥḍaren nnes.  
\v 23 \add Maca\add* usint-i-dd iɣarruba nneɣni zi Tibiriyas zzat i wemcan mani ccin aɣrum nni ibarek Yasuɛ.  
\v 24 Řami iẓra řɣaci belli Yasuɛ war din iǧi \add ɛad\add* uřa d imeḥḍaren nnes, nyin uřa d nitni deg iɣarruba-ya uca usin-dd ɣar Kafarnaḥum, arezzun x Yasuɛ.   
\b  
\m  
\s1 Yasuɛ Netta d Aɣrum Iddaren  
\m
\v 25 Řami t ufin x ujemmaḍ n řebḥar, nnan as: “\add A\add* Amseřmad nneɣ, meřmi dd-tusid da?”  
\v 26 Yasuɛ yarra-dd xasen, inna: “S tidett, s tidett, Necc ad awem iniɣ: Kenniw tarezzum xafi, war iǧi umi teẓrim řeɛřamat, maca umi teccim aɣrum uca tejjiwnem.  
\v 27 War ttxedmem i macca ixessaren, maca i macca ittɣiman i Tudart ittduman, tenni d awem i ɣa iwc Mmis n bnadem, minzi AREBBI, Babas, issars ṭṭabeɛ nnes xas.” \x ◘ \xo 6:27 \xt Mt. 3:17; 17:5; Mk. 1:11; 9:7; Lk. 3:22; 9:35; Yḥ. 1:33; 3:16; 4:14; 5:37; 6:40, 54; 8:18; 2 Bṭ. 1:17; Asa. 7:2; 9:4.\x*  
\v 28 Nnan as: “Min ɣa negg, ḥima ad negg řexdayem n AREBBI?”  
\v 29 Yarra-dd Yasuɛ, inna asen: “Ta d řxedmet n AREBBI, aqa ad tamnem deg Wenni dd-issekk Netta.” \x ◘ \xo 6:29 \xt 1 Yḥ. 3:23. \x*  
\v 30 \add Xas uca\add* nnan as: “Man řeɛřamet i ɣa tegged xenni ḥima ad \add t\add* nẓar uca ad zzayek namen? Man \add řxedmet\add* i ɣa tegged? \x ◘ \xo 6:30 \xt Mt. 12:38; 16:1; Mk. 8:11; Lk. 11:29; 1 Kur. 1:22. \x*  
\v 31 Řejdud nneɣ ccin ‘manna’ di řexřa am mammec tura: ‘Netta iwca asen-dd aɣrum zeg ujenna, ḥima ad t ccen’.” \x ◘ \xo 6:31 \xt Uf. 16:4, 14; Řxř. 11:7; Naḥ. 9:15; Izhd. 78:24, 25; 1 Kur. 10:3. \x*   
\m
\v 32 Inna asen Yasuɛ: “S tidett, s tidett, Necc ad awem iniɣ: War iǧi d Musa i d awem iwcin aɣrum zeg ujenna, maca Baba ittic awem Aɣrum n tidett zeg ujenna.  
\v 33 Minzi Aɣrum n AREBBI d Netta wenni dd-ihwan zeg ujenna uca ittic Tudart i ddunect.”  
\v 34 Nnan as: “\add A\add* Siditneɣ, ewc aneɣ-dd řebda aɣrum-a.”  
\v 35 Yasuɛ inna asen: “NECC d Aɣrum Iddaren. Wenni ɣari dd ɣa yasen, war ittřiẓ ɛemmarṣ, u wenni dayi i ɣa yamnen, war ittfidi \add ɛad\add* ɛemmarṣ. \x ◘ \xo 6:35 \xt Ica. 55:1; Yḥ. 4:14; 7:37. \x*  
\v 36 Maca Necc nniɣ awem, \add waxxa\add* kenniw teẓrim ayi, war tuminem ca.  
\v 37 Kuř ijj i d ayi ɣa iwc Baba, ad ɣari dd-yas u wenni ɣari dd ɣa yasen, war t ssuffuɣeɣ ca ɣar barra.  
\v 38 Minzi Necc hwiɣ-dd zeg ujenna, war iǧi ca ḥima ad ggeɣ min xseɣ Necc, maca \add ḥima ad ggeɣ\add* min ixs wenni d ayi dd-issekken. \x ◘ \xo 6:38 \xt Mt. 26:39; Mk. 14:36; Lk. 22:42; Yḥ. 5:30. \x*  
\v 39 D man aya min ixs Wenni d ayi dd-issekken, aqa Necc war ssweddareɣ uřa d ijjen zeg yinni d ayi iwca, maca ad t-i-dd-ssnekkareɣ deg wass aneggaru. \x ◘ \xo 6:39 \xt Yḥ. 10:28; 17:12; 18:9. \x*  
\v 40 D man aya min ixs Baba wenni d ayi dd-issekken, aqa kuř ijj wenni i ɣa iẓaren Mmis uca ad dayes yamen, ad ɣares tiři Tudart ittduman, uca Necc ad t-i-dd-ssnekkareɣ deg wass aneggaru.” \x ◘ \xo 6:40 \xt Yḥ. 3:16; 4:14; 6:27, 54. \x*   
\m
\v 41 Udayen cetcan zzayes, minzi inna: “Necc d Aɣrum i dd-ihwan zeg ujenna.”  
\v 42 Nnan: “Ma d wanita war iǧi bu d Yasuɛ, mmis n Yusuf? Neccin nessen babas d yemmas! Mammec i ɣa yini Weryaz-a: ‘Necc hwiɣ-dd zeg ujenna?’” \x ◘ \xo 6:42 \xt Mt. 13:55; Mk. 6:3. \x*  
\v 43 Yasuɛ yarra-dd xasen, inna: “War ttcetcam ca jar awem.  
\v 44 War izemmar uřa d ijj ad ɣari dd-yas, mɣir mařa ijebd i-t-i-dd Baba wenni d ayi dd-issekken uca Necc ad t-i-dd-ssnekkareɣ deg wass aneggaru. \x ◘ \xo 6:44 \xt Izři 1:4; Yḥ. 6:65. \x*  
\v 45 Aqa tura deg \add idlisen n\add* inabiyyen: ‘Nitni marra ad ttwassřemden zi AREBBI!’ S uyenni kuř ijj wenni d as isřin zi Baba u iřmed i-t zzayes, ad ɣari dd-yas. \x ◘ \xo 6:45 \xt Ica. 54:13; Irm. 31:33; Ɛbr. 8:10; 10:16. \x*  
\v 46 Uřa d ijj war izemmar ad iẓar Baba, mɣir wenni iǧan zi AREBBI, d Netta i ittwařin Baba. \x ◘ \xo 6:46 \xt Mt. 11:27; Lk. 10:22; Yḥ. 1:18; 7:29; 8:19. \x*  
\v 47 S tidett, s tidett, Necc ad awem iniɣ: Wenni dayi ittamnen, ad ɣares tiři Tudart ittduman. \x ◘ \xo 6:47 \xt Yḥ. 3:16,36. \x*  
\v 48 NECC d Aɣrum Iddaren.  
\v 49 Řejdud nwem ccin ‘manna’ di řexřa uca mmuten, \x ◘ \xo 6:49 \xt Uf. 16:4; Řxř. 11:7; Izhd. 78:24. \x*  
\v 50 \add maca\add* man aya d Aɣrum i dd-ihwan zeg ujenna, ḥima bnadem ad zzayes yecc, war ittmetti ca:  
\v 51 NECC d Aɣrum Iddaren i dd-ihwan zeg ujenna. Mařa ijjen icca zeg Weɣrum-a, ad iddar i řebda. Aɣrum nni i ɣa wceɣ Necc, netta d Arrimet inu i ɣa wceɣ i Tudart n ddunect.” \x ◘ \xo 6:51 \xt Yḥ. 11:26; Ɛbr. 10:5, 10. \x*   
\m
\v 52 Udayen mmenɣen jar asen, nnan: “Mammec i ɣa yegg Wanita ad aneɣ iwc Arrimet nnes ḥima ad \add tt\add* necc?” \x ◘ \xo 6:52 \xt Yḥ. 3:9. \x*  
\v 53 Inna asen Yasuɛ: “S tidett, s tidett, Necc ad awem iniɣ: Mařa war tᵉttᵉttem Arrimet n Mmis n bnadem u war tessesem Idammen nnes, war ɣarwem bu Tudart deg ixef nwem.  
\v 54 Wenni i ɣa iccen Arrimet inu uca ad isuw Idammen inu, ad ɣares tiři Tudart ittduman u Necc ad t-i-dd-ssnekkareɣ deg wass aneggaru. \x ◘ \xo 6:54 \xt Yḥ. 3:16; 4:14; 6:27,40. \x*  
\v 55 Minzi Arrimet inu d macca d tidett uca Idammen inu d tissit d tidett.  
\v 56 Wenni i ɣa iccen Arrimet inu uca ad isu Idammen inu, ad dayi iqqim u Necc dayes.  
\v 57 Am mammec d ayi dd-issekk Baba iddaren uca Necc ddareɣ zi Baba, ammu ɛawed wenni zzayi i ɣa iccen, ad zzayi iddar.  
\v 58 Wa d Aɣrum i dd-ihwan zeg ujenna. War iǧi ca am mammec ccin řejdud nwem ‘manna’ uca mmuten, wenni i ɣa iccen Aɣrum-a, ad iddar i řebda.” \x ◘ \xo 6:58 \xt Yḥ. 3:13. \x*  
\v 59 Inna man aya di temzida, am tuɣa isseřmad di Kafarnaḥum.   
\b  
\m  
\s1 Aṭṭas n imeḥḍaren bdan tteggʷejjen x Yasuɛ  
\m
\v 60 Aṭṭas n imeḥḍaren nnes, umi sřin man aya, nnan: “Awař-a iqseḥ. Wi izemmaren ad as iseř?”  
\v 61 Maca Yasuɛ issen deg Ixef nnes, aqa imeḥḍaren nnes cetcan x man aya, uca inna asen: “Ma ad tenqarḍem di man aya?  
\v 62 I mammec mařa teẓrim Mmis n bnadem ittgeɛɛad ɣar mani iřa iǧa qbeř? \x ◘ \xo 6:62 \xt Mk. 16:19; Lk. 24:50; Yḥ. 3:13; Řex. 1:9; Afa. 4:8. \x*  
\v 63 Arruḥ d Netta isseddaren, arrimet war tneffeɛ i walu. Awařen i d awem nniɣ, aqa aten d Arruḥ d Tudart. \x ◘ \xo 6:63 \xt 2 Kur. 3:6. \x*  
\v 64 Maca aqa din ca jar awem inni war yuminen.” Minzi Yasuɛ issen zeg umezwaru man yen iǧan inni war yuminen u man wen t i ɣa iɣdaren. \x ◘ \xo 6:64 \xt Yḥ. 2:25; 13:11. \x*  
\v 65 Inna asen: “S uyenni nniɣ awem: War izemmar uřa d ijj ad ɣari dd-yas, mɣir mařa temmewc as zi Baba.” \x ◘ \xo 6:65 \xt Yḥ. 6:44. \x*  
\v 66 Zi řweqt nni dewřen aṭṭas zeg imeḥḍaren nnes ɣar ḍeffar, war qqimen ca gguren akides.   
\m
\v 67 Inna Yasuɛ i tenɛac: “Ma uřa d kenniw texsem ad tuyurem?”  
\v 68 Cimɛun Buṭrus yarra-dd xas, inna: “\add A\add* Sidi, wi ɣar i ɣa nraḥ? Cek ɣarek awařen n Tudart ittduman, \x ◘ \xo 6:68 \xt Řex. 5:20. \x*  
\v 69 u neccin numen u nessen aqa Cek d Lmasiḥ, Mmis n AREBBI Iddaren.” \x ◘ \xo 6:69 \xt Mt. 16:16; Mk. 8:29; Lk. 9:20; Yḥ. 11:27. \x*  
\v 70 Yasuɛ inna asen: “Ma war iǧi d Necc i kenniw dd-ixḍaren d tenɛac? Uca ijjen zzaywem d cciṭan.” \x ◘ \xo 6:70 \xt Lk. 6:13. \x*  
\v 71 Inna man aya x Yahuda, mmis n Cimɛun Isxariyuṭi, minzi wanita tuɣa ixs ad t isellem. Netta d ijjen zi tenɛac.   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 7
\s1 Aytmas n Yasuɛ war dayes uminen  
\m
\v 1 Awarni man aya tuɣa Yasuɛ iggur di Ljalil, war ixs ad yuyur di Yahudiyya, minzi Udayen tuɣa arezzun ad t nɣen.  
\v 2 Iqarreb-dd Řɛid n Iɛuccuten n Wudayen. \x ◘ \xo 7:2 \xt Lawi 23:34. \x*  
\v 3 Nnan as aytmas: “Ffeɣ ssanita, ruḥ ɣar \add temmurt n\add* Yahudiyya ḥima uřa d imeḥḍaren nnec ad ẓaren řexdayem nni tᵉttegged.  
\v 4 Uřa d ijj war ittegg ca n tmesřact s tnuffra, mařa yarezzu ad isseḍhar ixef nnes s bṭayṭay. Mařa teggid timesřayin-a, scen Ixef nnec i ddunect.”  
\v 5 Minzi uřa d aytmas war dayes uminen ca. \x ◘ \xo 7:5 \xt Mk. 3:21. \x*  
\v 6 Inna asen Yasuɛ: “Řweqt inu ɛad war dd-tiwiḍ, maca řweqt nwem aqa-tt řebda akidwem.  
\v 7 Ddunnit war tzemmar ad kenniw tcarh, maca nettat tcarh ayi, minzi Necc cehhdeɣ xas belli řexdayem nnes d tiɛeffanin. \x ◘ \xo 7:7 \xt Yḥ. 3:19; 14:17; 15:18. \x*  
\v 8 Ruḥem kenniw ɣar Řɛid-a. Necc war ttriḥeɣ ca ɣar Řɛid-a, minzi řweqt inu ɛad war tkemmeř.” \x ◘ \xo 7:8 \xt Yḥ. 8:20. \x*  
\v 9 Awarni řami inna ammu, iqqim di Ljalil.   
\b  
\m  
\s1 Yasuɛ iggur ɣar Řɛid n Iɛuccuten  
\m
\v 10 Maca umi geɛɛden aytmas ɣar Řɛid, iruḥ uřa d Netta ɣar Řɛid, war iǧi s bṭayṭay, maca igga axmi innufar.  
\v 11 Udayen arezzun xas di Řɛid, nnan: “Mani iǧa Wanita?” \x ◘ \xo 7:11 \xt Yḥ. 11:56. \x*  
\v 12 Aṭṭas zi řɣaci temtumen xas. Ca \add zzaysen\add* nnan: “Netta d aṣebḥan” Maca inneɣni nnan: “Lla, maɣar issxarriq x řɣaci!” \x ◘ \xo 7:12 \xt Mt. 21:46; Lk. 7:16; Yḥ. 6:14; 9:16; 10:19. \x*  
\v 13 Maca uřa d ijj war xas issiweř s bṭayṭay zi ssibbet n tiggʷudi zeg Wudayen. \x ◘ \xo 7:13 \xt Yḥ. 9:22; 12:42; 19:38. \x*   
\m
\v 14 Maca ařami iɛdu wezyen n Řɛid, igeɛɛed Yasuɛ ɣar Zzawect Tameqqrant, isseřmad \add din\add*.  
\v 15 Udayen dehcen, nnan: “Mammec igga Weryaz-a issen Idlisen am war iɣri ca?”  
\v 16 Yasuɛ yarra-dd, inna: “Taɣuri inu war teǧi ca inu, maca n Wenni d ayi dd-issekken. \x ◘ \xo 7:16 \xt Yḥ. 3:11; 8:28; 12:49; 14:10, 24. \x*  
\v 17 Mařa ijjen ixs ad igg min ixs Netta, ad issen ma aqa taɣuri-ya zi AREBBI niɣ aqa ssawařeɣ ɛlaḥsab řxaḍar inu.  
\v 18 Wenni issawařen zeg uxarreṣ n řxaḍar n yixef nnes, yarezzu aɛuǧi nnes, maca Wenni yarezzun aɛuǧi n wenni t-i-dd issekken, aqa Netta d tidett, war dayes bu řɣecc.  
\v 19 Ma war iǧi d Musa i d awem iwcin Ccariɛa? Maca uřa d ijj zzaywem war ittegg Ccariɛa? I mayemmi \add xenni\add* tarezzum ad ayi tenɣem?” \x ◘ \xo 7:19 \xt Uf. 20:1; 24:3; Mt. 12:14; Mk. 3:6; Yḥ. 5:18; 10:39; 11:53; Řex. 7:53. \x*   
\m
\v 20 Řɣaci yarra-dd, nitni nnan: “Dayek ijj n cciṭan, wi yarezzun ad Cek nɣen?” \x ◘ \xo 7:20 \xt Yḥ. 8:48, 52; 10:20. \x*  
\v 21 Yasuɛ yarra-dd, inna asen: “Ggiɣ ict n řxedmet uca kenniw tᵉttbehtem marra.  
\v 22 I uya Musa iwca awem-dd axtan, war iǧi minzi axtan zi Musa i yeǧa, maca \add minzi axtan iǧa\add* zi řejdud nwem, u \add xenni\add* txettnem i bnadem di ssebt. \x ◘ \xo 7:22 \xt Lawi 12:3; Amz. 17:10. \x*  
\v 23 Mařa iqbeř bnadem ad ittwaxten deg wass n ssebt, ḥima war tᵉttwareẓẓi Ccariɛa n Musa, mammec i xafi i ɣa tcetcam řami ssgenfiɣ bnadem ikmeř deg wass n ssebt?  
\v 24 War ḥekkmem x teqcurt \add n bnadem\add*, maca ḥekmem s yijj n řḥukm iseggden.” \x ◘ \xo 7:24 \xt Aɛwd. 1:16, 17; Awřn. 24:23; Yaɛ. 2:1. \x*   
\b  
\m  
\s1 Ma Yasuɛ Netta d Lmasiḥ?  
\m
\v 25 Nnan iryazen zi Urcalim: “Ma war iǧi d Wa i yarezzun ad t nɣen?  
\v 26 Maca xzar, issawař s bṭayṭay, war d as qqaren walu. Ad taɣ aqa ssnen imɣaren \add n řgens\add* nican belli s tidett Wanita d Lmasiḥ?  
\v 27 Maca nessen Wa, manis Netta, maca xmi dd ɣa yas Lmasiḥ, uřa d ijj war issin manis Netta.” \x ◘ \xo 7:27 \xt Mt. 13:55; Mk. 6:3; Lk. 4:22. \x*  
\v 28 Řami tuɣa isseřmad di Zzawect Tameqqrant, issgeɛɛed Yasuɛ tmijja nnes s jjehd, inna: “Kenniw tessnem ayi u tessnem manis Necc. Necc war dd-usiɣ s řxaḍar n Yixef inu, maca Wenni d ayi dd-issekken aqa-t d tidett, kenniw war t tessinem ca. \x ◘ \xo 7:28 \xt Yḥ. 5:43; 8:26, 42; Rum. 3:4. \x*  
\v 29 Maca Necc ssneɣ t, minzi Necc zzayes u Netta d wenni d ayi-dd issekken.” \x ◘ \xo 7:29 \xt Yḥ. 10:15. \x*   
\m
\v 30 Xenni arezzun ad t ṭṭfen, maca uřa d ijj war xas issars afus, minzi tasaɛɛet nnes war dd-tiweḍ ɛad. \x ◘ \xo 7:30 \xt Mk. 11:18; Lk. 19:47; 20:19; Yḥ. 7:19; 8:20, 37. \x*   
\m
\v 31 Aṭṭas zi řɣaci umnen zzayes, nnan: “Xmi dd ɣa yas Lmasiḥ, ma ad igg řeɛřamat ktar zi tina i igga Wa?” \x ◘ \xo 7:31 \xt Yḥ. 8:30. \x*   
\b  
\m
\v 32 Sřin Ifarisiyyen marra min xas itemten řɣaci. Uca nitni d imeqqranen n ikehhanen ssekken-dd iɛessasen ḥima ad t ṭṭfen.  
\v 33 Yasuɛ inna: “Necc ad kidwem qqimeɣ drus n řweqt ɛad, \add xenni\add* ad raḥeɣ ɣar Wenni d ayi dd-issekken. \x ◘ \xo 7:33 \xt Yḥ. 16:16. \x*  
\v 34 Ad xafi tarzum, war dayi tᵉttifem, u mani ɣa iřiɣ Necc, war tzemmarem ad dd-tadfem.” \x ◘ \xo 7:34 \xt Yḥ. 8:21; 13:33. \x*  
\v 35 Nnan Wudayen jar asen: “Mani ɣa iraḥ Netta ařami war nzemmar ad t naf. Ma xenni ixs ad iraḥ ɣar temmura n řegnus? Ma ixs ad isseřmed i lkuffar?  
\v 36 Min iɛna wawař-a i inna: ‘Ad xafi tarzum, war dayi tᵉttᵉṭṭifem!’, u ‘Mani ɣa iřiɣ Necc, war tzemmarem ad dd-tadfem’?”   
\b  
\m  
\s1 Yasuɛ d řɛunṣar n Waman Iddaren  
\m
\v 37 Deg wass ameqqran, ass aneggaru n Řɛid, \add ikkar\add* ibedd-dd Yasuɛ, iřaɣa, inna: “Mařa ifud ḥed, ejj i-t ad ɣari dd-yas, ad isu. \x ◘ \xo 7:37 \xt Lawi 23:36; Ica. 55:1; Yḥ. 6:35; Asa. 22:17. \x*  
\v 38 Wenni dayi i ɣa yamnen, am mammec nnant Tira \add Iqeddsen\add*: Ad zzayes azzřen iɣezran n Waman Iddaren!” \x ◘ \xo 7:38 \xt Ica. 12:3. \x*  
\v 39 Inna man aya x Arruḥ i ɣa qebřen inni dayes ittamnen. Minzi Arruḥ \add Iqeddsen\add* war d asen immewc \add ɛad\add*, minzi Yasuɛ war ittwassɛuǧi ɛad. \x ◘ \xo 7:39 \xt Ica. 44:3; Yuw. 3:1; Řex. 2:17. \x*   
\m
\v 40 Aṭṭas zi řɣaci, umi sřin awař-a, nnan: “D Wa d Anabi s tidett!” \x ◘ \xo 7:40 \xt Mt. 21:46; Lk. 7:16; Yḥ. 6:14. \x*  
\v 41 Inneɣni nnan: “Wa d Lmasiḥ!”, maca ca nneɣni \add zzaysen\add* nnan: “Ma ad dd-yas Lmasiḥ zi Ljalil? \x ◘ \xo 7:41 \xt Yḥ. 1:47; 4:42. \x*  
\v 42 Ma war qqarent Tira \add Iqeddsen\add*, aqa Lmasiḥ ad dd-yas zi zzariɛet n Dawud, zi Bayt-Laḥm, zi dcar n Dawud?” \x ◘ \xo 7:42 \xt Izhd. 132:11; Mixa 5:1; Mt. 2:6. \x*  
\v 43 Uca imsar umsebḍi n řɣaci di ssibbet nnes.  
\v 44 Ca zzaysen xsen ad t ṭṭfen, maca uřa d ijj war xas issars ifassen.   
\m
\v 45 Xenni dewřen-dd iɛessasen nni ɣar imeqqranen n ikehhanen d Ifarisiyyen. Ikehhanen nnan asen: “Mayemmi war t-i-dd-tiwyem?”  
\v 46 Arrin-dd xasen iɛessasen: “Ɛemmarṣ war issiweř uřa d ijj n bnadem am mammec \add issawař\add* Weryaz-a!”  
\v 47 Nnan asen Ifarisiyyen: “Ma uřa d kenniw ttwaxedɛem \add zzayes\add*?  
\v 48 Ma xenni din ca n ijjen zeg imeqqranen \add n řgens\add* niɣ zeg Ifarisiyyen yumen zzayes? \x ◘ \xo 7:48 \xt Ica. 33:18; Yḥ. 12:42; 1 Kur. 1:20; 2:8. \x*  
\v 49 Maca řɣaci-ya i war issinen ca Ccariɛa, aqa ittwanɛeř.”  
\v 50 Nikudimus, wenni tuɣa d ijjen zzaysen u wenni dd-yusin ɣar Yasuɛ s ǧiřet, inna asen: \x ◘ \xo 7:50 \xt Yḥ. 3:2; 19:39. \x*  
\v 51 “Ma ad teḥkem Ccariɛa nneɣ x ijj n bnadem, břa ma ad zzayes sřen, ad ssnen min igga?” \x ◘ \xo 7:51 \xt Uf. 23:1; Lawi 19:15; Aɛwd. 1:17; 17:8; 19:15. \x*  
\v 52 Arrin-dd, nnan as: “Ma uřa d cek \add ad taɣ\add* zi Ljalil? Arzu, xzar, uřa d ijj n unabi war dd-ittekk ca zi Ljalil.”  
\v 53 \add Xas uca\add* iruḥ kuř ijjen ɣar taddart nnes. Maca Yasuɛ iruḥ ɣar wedrar n Zzitun.   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 8
\s1 Tamɣart tᵉttwaṭṭef tᵉttegg zzina  
\m
\v 1 ...  
\v 2 Di ṣṣbeḥ yusa-dd ɛawed ɣar Zzawect Tameqqrant, usin-dd ɣares iwdan marra. \add Xenni\add* am iqqim, ibda isseřmad i-ten.  
\v 3 Imseřmaden n idlisen d Ifarisiyyen iwyen as-dd ict n temɣart, tᵉttwaṭṭef tᵉttegg zzina. Ssbedden tt di řwesṭ,  
\v 4 nnan as: “\add A\add* Amseɣɣar, tamɣart-a tᵉttwaṭṭef s bṭayṭay, tᵉttegg zzina.  
\v 5 Iweṣṣa Musa di Ccariɛa ad narjem \add timɣarin\add* am tanita. Min ɣa tinid Cek?” \x ◘ \xo 8:5 \xt Lawi 20:10; Aɛwd. 22:22. \x*  
\v 6 Nnan as aya ḥima ad t jarrben, ḥima ad ɣarsen tiři minzi xas i ɣa cetcan. Maca Yasuɛ yuḍar swadday, yura \add s uḍaḍ nnes\add* di temmurt.   
\m
\v 7 Řami qqimen ammu t ttesseqsan, ibedd, inna asen: “Wi zzaywem iǧan břa ddnub, ad xas inḍar aẓru amezwaru.” \x ◘ \xo 8:7 \xt Aɛwd. 17:7. \x*  
\v 8 Xenni yuḍar ɛawed swadday uca yura di temmurt. \x ◘ \xo 8:8 \xt Irm. 17:13\x*  
\v 9 Řami sřin man aya, ffɣen ijjen awarni wenneɣni, imeqqranen d amezwaru. Tamɣart nni ibedden di řwesṭ jjin tt weḥḥdes.  
\v 10 Řexdenni Yasuɛ ikkar, inna i temɣart: “Mani ǧan nitni? Ma war cem iḥakem uřa d ijjen?”  
\v 11 Nettat tenna: “Uřa d ijj, \add a\add* SIDI!” Yasuɛ inna as: “Uřa d Necc war cem ttḥakameɣ ca. Ruḥ, war ttɛawad ad tegged ddnub zi ssa tsawent!” \x ◘ \xo 8:11 \xt Yḥ. 5:14. \x*   
\b  
\m  
\s1 Yasuɛ d Tafawt n ddunect  
\m
\v 12 Issiweř Yasuɛ ɛawed akidsen, inna: “NECC d Tafawt n ddunect. Wenni d ayi ɣa iḍfaren, war iggur ɛemmarṣ di taǧest, maca ad yaf Tfawt n Tudart.” \x ◘ \xo 8:12 \xt Ica. 42:6, 16; Yḥ. 1:9; 9:5; 12:35, 36. \x*   
\m
\v 13 Nnan as Ifarisiyyen: “Cek tcehhded x Yixef nnec, cchadet nnec war teǧi ca d tidett.”  
\v 14 Yasuɛ yarra-dd, inna asen: “Ɛad mařa Necc cehhdeɣ x Yixef inu, cchadet inu aqa d tidett, minzi Necc ssneɣ manis dd-usiɣ u mani ɣa raḥeɣ, maca kenniw war tessinem ca manis dd-usiɣ uřa mani ɣa raḥeɣ. \x ◘ \xo 8:14 \xt Yḥ. 5:31. \x*  
\v 15 Kenniw tᵉttḥakamem ɛlaḥsab ddat, Necc war ttḥakameɣ uřa x ijjen.  
\v 16 U Necc, mařa ḥakmeɣ, ad yiři řeḥkam inu d tidett, minzi Necc war ǧiɣ bu weḥḥdi, maca Necc d Baba wenni d ayi dd-issekken.  
\v 17 Tura ɛawed di Ccariɛa nwem, belli cchadet n tnayen n iwdan d tidett. \x ◘ \xo 8:17 \xt Řxř. 35:30; Aɛwd. 17:6; 19:15; Mt. 18:16; 2 Kur. 13:1; Ɛbr. 10:28. \x*  
\v 18 NECC d wenni icehhden x Yixef inu, uca uřa d Baba wenni d ayi-dd issekken, iched xafi.” \x ◘ \xo 8:18 \xt Mt. 3:17; 17:5; Mk. 1:11; 9:7; Lk. 3:22; 9:35; Yḥ. 1:33; 5:37; 6:27. \x*  
\v 19 Nitni nnan as: “Mani iǧa Babac?” Yasuɛ yarra-dd, inna asen: “Kenniw war d ayi tessinem ca u war tessinem Baba. Meɛlik kenniw d ayi tessnem, ad tiři tessnem uřa d Baba.” \x ◘ \xo 8:19 \xt Yḥ. 14:9; 16:3. \x*   
\m
\v 20 Inna awařen-a di mani tuɣa řexzen n ṣṣedqet, am tuɣa isseřmad di Zzawect Tameqqrant. War t iṭṭif uřa d ijj, minzi tasaɛɛet nnes tuɣa ɛad war dd-tiwiḍ. \x ◘ \xo 8:20 \xt Yḥ. 7:30. \x*   
\m
\v 21 Yasuɛ inna asen ɛawed: “Necc ad raḥeɣ, kenniw ad xafi tarzum, ad temmtem di ddnub nwem. Mani ɣa raḥeɣ Necc, war tzemmarem kenniw ad dd-tasem.” \x ◘ \xo 8:21 \xt Yḥ. 7:34; 13:33. \x*  
\v 22 Udayen nnan: “Ma ad ineɣ Ixef nnes \add řexxu\add*, minzi Netta inna: ‘Mani ɣa raḥeɣ Necc, war tzemmarem kenniw ad dd-tasem’?”  
\v 23 Netta inna asen: “Kenniw zi swadday, Necc zi sennej, kenniw zi ddunect-a, maca Necc war ǧiɣ ca zi ddunect-a. \x ◘ \xo 8:23 \xt Yḥ. 3:31. \x*  
\v 24 Necc nniɣ awem, ad temmtem di ddnub nwem, maɣar mařa war tuminem ca aqa d Necc, ad temmtem di ddnub nwem.” \x ◘ \xo 8:24 \xt Yḥ. 8:21. \x*  
\v 25 Udayen nnan: “Min teɛnid Cek?” Yasuɛ inna asen: “Waxxa Necc bdiɣ ad kidwem ssiwřeɣ -  
\v 26 \add uca\add* Necc ɣari aṭṭas n tmesřayin i xef zemmareɣ ad xawem ssiwřeɣ uca ad xawem ḥekmeɣ - \add ittxeṣṣa ɛad ad tessnem,\add* aqa Wenni d ayi dd-issekken aqa-t d tidett, uca min zzayes sřiɣ, ad t iniɣ i ddunect.” \x ◘ \xo 8:26 \xt Yḥ. 7:28; 15:15; Rum. 3:4. \x*  
\v 27 Nitni war fhimen ca, belli tuɣa issawař akidsen x Babas.  
\v 28 Yasuɛ inna asen ɛawed: “Xmi ɣa tessgeɛɛdem Mmis n bnadem, ad tfehmem belli aqa d Necc, u belli war tteggeɣ uřa d ict n řḥajjet zeg Ixef inu, maca ssawařeɣ am mammec d ayi isseřmed Baba. \x ◘ \xo 8:28 \xt Řxř. 21:9; 2 Ij. 18:4; Yḥ. 3:11, 14; 7:16; 12:32, 49; 14:10. \x*  
\v 29 Wenni d ayi dd-issekken aqa-t akidi. Baba war d ayi ijji ca weḥḥdi, minzi tteggeɣ řebda min t yarḍan.” \x ◘ \xo 8:29 \xt Yḥ. 14:10; 16:32. \x*  
\v 30 Umi tuɣa issawař x tmesřayin-a, umnen dayes aṭṭas. \x ◘ \xo 8:30 \xt Yḥ. 7:31. \x*   
\b  
\m  
\s1 Ayt n Ibrahim  
\m
\v 31 Xenni inna Yasuɛ i Wudayen nni dayes yumnen: “Mařa teqqimem tᵉṭṭfem deg wawař inu, ad tiřim s tidett d imeḥḍaren inu,  
\v 32 uca ad tessnem tidett uca tidett ad kenniw tḥarr.” \x ◘ \xo 8:32 \xt Rum. 6:18; Gal. 5:1; 1 Bṭ. 2:16. \x*  
\v 33 Nnan as: “Neccin d zzariɛet n Ibrahim, ɛemmarṣ war neɛbid ḥed s tesmuɣi. Mammec tzemmared ad tinid: ‘Kenniw ad tᵉttwaḥarrem’?” \x ◘ \xo 8:33 \xt Mt. 3:9. \x*  
\v 34 Yasuɛ yarra-dd xasen: “S tidett, s tidett, Necc ad awem iniɣ, marra wenni itteggen ddnub netta d amsexxar n ddnub. \x ◘ \xo 8:34 \xt Rum. 6:20; 2 Bṭ. 2:1. \x*  
\v 35 Amsexxar war ittɣimi ca di taddart řebda, maca Mmis ad din iqqim i řebda.  
\v 36 Xmi kenniw i ɣa iḥarr Mmis, ad tiřim s tidett d iḥurriyyen. \x ◘ \xo 8:36 \xt Rum. 8:2. \x*   
\m
\v 37 Necc ssneɣ, aqa kenniw d tarwa n Ibrahim, maca kenniw tarezzum ad ayi tenɣem, minzi awař inu war tzemmarem ad t tfehmem.  
\v 38 Necc ssawařeɣ s min ẓriɣ zi Baba. Uřa d kenniw tᵉtteggem zi min teẓrim zi babatwem.” \x ◘ \xo 8:38 \xt Yḥ. 3:11; 7:16; 12:49; 14:10, 24. \x*  
\v 39 Arrin-dd, nnan as: “Babatneɣ d Ibrahim.” Inna asen Yasuɛ: “Maɛlik kenniw teǧim d tarwa n Ibrahim, ad yiři aqa tᵉtteggem řexdayem n Ibrahim. \x ◘ \xo 8:39 \xt Rum. 2:28; 9:7. \x*  
\v 40 Maca řexxu tarezzum ad ayi tenɣem, Necc d ijj n Bnadem i tuɣa akidwem issawařen s tidett i sřiɣ zi AREBBI. Man aya war t iggi ca Ibrahim. \x ◘ \xo 8:40 \xt Yḥ. 17:17. \x*  
\v 41 Kenniw tᵉtteggem řexdayem n babatwem.” Nitni nnan as: “Neccin war dd-nexřiq ca zi farq-ccɣeř, aqa ɣarneɣ Ijjen wenni d Babatneɣ, aqa-t d AREBBI.”   
\b  
\m  
\s1 Ayt n ibřis  
\m
\v 42 Inna asen Yasuɛ: “Maɛlik AREBBI d Babatwem, iři aqa texsem ayi, minzi Necc ffɣeɣ-dd zi AREBBI. Necc war dd-usiɣ ca zeg Ixef inu, maca Netta issekk ayi-dd. \x ◘ \xo 8:42 \xt Yḥ. 5:43; 7:29. \x*  
\v 43 Mayemmi war tefhimem i wawařen inu? Minzi kenniw war tzemmarem ad tesřem i wawař\add en\add* inu!  
\v 44 Aqa kenniw \add teffɣem\add* zi babatwem, ibřis, uca texsem ad teggem imeẓran n babatwem. Netta tuɣa ineqq iwdan zeg umezwaru u war ibedd di tidett, minzi war dayes bu tidett. Meřmi ma issawař s uxarriq, issawař s min dayes, minzi netta d bu-ixarriqen uřa d babas n uxarriq. \x ◘ \xo 8:44 \xt Amz. 3:1; 2 Kur. 11:3; 1 Yḥ. 3:8. \x*  
\v 45 Maca umi Necc qqareɣ awem tidett, kenniw war dayi tᵉttimnem ca.  
\v 46 Wi zzaywem ad ayi isseqneɛ x ddnub? Umi qqareɣ tidett, mayemmi war dayi tᵉttimnem ca?  
\v 47 Wenni iǧan zi AREBBI, ittesřa i wawařen n AREBBI. Minzi kenniw war teǧim ca zi AREBBI, s uyenni kenniw war tᵉttesřim ca.” \x ◘ \xo 8:47 \xt Yḥ. 6:37; 10:26, 27; 1 Yḥ. 4:6. \x*   
\b  
\m  
\s1 Yasuɛ tuɣa-t din qbeř Ibrahim  
\m
\v 48 Udayen arrin-dd, nnan as: “Ma war iǧi nican umi nenna, aqa Cek zi Samarya u dayek ijj n cciṭan?” \x ◘ \xo 8:48 \xt Yḥ. 7:20; 10:20. \x*  
\v 49 Yasuɛ yarra-dd, inna: “Necc war dayi uřa d ijj n cciṭan, maca Necc ttweqqareɣ Baba, uca kenniw tesseḥqaram ayi. \x ◘ \xo 8:49 \xt Yḥ. 7:18. \x*  
\v 50 Necc war arezzuɣ ca aɛuǧi inu. Aqa din Ijjen i xas yarezzun d wenni i ɣa iḥekmen.  
\v 51 S tidett, s tidett, Necc ad awem iniɣ: Mařa ca n yijjen iṭṭef deg wawař inu, ɛemmarṣ war ittwiři řmewt i řebda.” \x ◘ \xo 8:51 \xt Yḥ. 5:24; 11:25. \x*  
\v 52 Nnan as Wudayen: “Řexxu nessen belli dayek ijj n cciṭan. Aqa Ibrahim d inabiyyen mmuten. Cek teqqared: ‘Mařa ca n yijjen iṭṭef deg wawař inu, ɛemmarṣ ad iqqas řmewt i řebda!’  
\v 53 Ma Cek temɣared x jedditneɣ Ibrahim wenni immuten, uřa x inabiyyen nni immuten? Min tḥesbed Ixef nnec?” \x ◘ \xo 8:53 \xt Ɛbr. 11:13. \x*  
\v 54 Inna asen Yasuɛ: “Mařa Necc ssɛuǧiɣ Ixef inu, aɛuǧi inu war iǧi d walu. Baba, aqa issɛuǧa ayi, Wenni xef teqqarem: ‘Netta d AREBBI nneɣ!’  
\v 55 Kenniw war t tessinem, maca Necc aqa ssneɣ t. Mařa nniɣ: ‘War t ssineɣ!’, ad iřiɣ Necc d bu-ixarriqen am kenniw. Maca Necc ssneɣ t u ttᵉṭṭfeɣ deg wawař nnes.  
\v 56 Jedditwem Ibrahim tuɣa ittraja s řefraḥet ḥima ad iẓar ass inu, uca iẓra i-t, ifarḥ.” \x ◘ \xo 8:56 \xt Amz. 17:17; Lk. 10:24; Ɛbr. 11:13. \x*  
\v 57 Nnan as Wudayen: “Ɛad war ɣarek bu xemsin n iseggʷusa, mammec teggid teẓrid Ibrahim?”  
\v 58 Inna asen Yasuɛ: “S tidett, s tidett, Necc ad awem iniɣ, qbeř ma tuɣa Ibrahim, tuɣa NECC ǧiɣ.”  
\v 59 \add Xenni\add* ksin iẓra ḥima ad t arejmen. Maca Yasuɛ issnuffar Ixef nnes uca iffeɣ zi Zzawect Tameqqrant \add am\add* icuq di řwesṭ nsen, uca \add ammu i\add* iruḥ. \x ◘ \xo 8:59 \xt Lk. 4:29; Yḥ. 10:31,39; 11:8. \x*   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 9
\s1 Asgenfi n ijjen wenni d adarɣař zeg wami dd-ixřeq  
\m
\v 1 Umi xasen dd-ikka, iẓra ijj n weryaz tuɣa d adarɣař zeg wami dd-ixřeq.  
\v 2 Imeḥḍaren nnes sseqsan t, nnan: “\add A\add* Amseřmad nneɣ, wi ixḍan, ma d wa niɣ lwalidin nnes, ařami dd-ixřeq d adarɣař?”  
\v 3 Yasuɛ inna asen: “Uřa d netta war ixḍi uřa d lwalidin nnes, maca \add man aya aqa imsar\add*, ḥima ad dayes ḍharent řexdayem n AREBBI.  
\v 4 Icuwwar ad xedmeɣ řexdayem n Wenni d ayi dd-issekken maḥend ɛad d aziř. Ad dd-tas taǧest mani war izemmar uřa d ijj ad ixdem.  
\v 5 Mintra Necc aqa ayi di ddunect, Necc d Tafawt n ddunect.” \x ◘ \xo 9:5 \xt Ica. 42:6; Lk. 2:32; Yḥ. 1:9; 8:12; 12:35,46; Řex. 13:47. \x*  
\v 6 Awarni řami inna ammu, issusef di temmurt, igga abeǧaɛ zeg ikuffan nni uca iḥennec zzayes tiṭṭawin n udarɣař s ubeǧaɛ. \x ◘ \xo 9:6 \xt Mk. 8:23. \x*  
\v 7 \add Xas uca\add* inna as: “Ruḥ, tessirded di tuyeřmamt n useɣḍeṣ n Siluwam!” Iruḥ, issird, idweř ittwařa. \f ◼ \fr 9:7 \ft \+fk Siluwam\ft  - isem wanita ixs ad yini ‘ittwassekken’.\f*   
\m
\v 8 Jjiran d yinni tuɣa t iẓrin qbeř ittettar, nnan: “Ma war iǧi d wa d wenni tuɣa ittɣiman ittettar?” \x ◘ \xo 9:8 \xt Řex. 3:2. \x*  
\v 9 Ca zzaysen nnan: “Aqa d netta!” Nnan inneɣni: “Lla, maca ittawi-dd dayes!” Maca netta \add s yixef nnes\add* inna: “Aqa d necc!”  
\v 10 Nnan as: “Mammec \add temsar\add* ttwarezment tiṭṭawin nnec?”  
\v 11 Yarra-dd, inna asen: “Bnadem umi qqaren Yasuɛ, igga abeǧaɛ, iḥennec tiṭṭawin inu uca inna ayi: ‘Ruḥ ɣar tuyeřmamt n Siluwam, tessirded!’ Xenni ruḥeɣ, ssirdeɣ uca dewřeɣ ttwařiɣ.”  
\v 12 Nnan as: “Mani iǧa Netta?” Inna: “War ssineɣ.”   
\m
\v 13 Awyen-dd wenni tuɣa iǧa qbeř d adarɣař, ɣar Ifarisiyyen.  
\v 14 Tuɣa d ssebt řami igga Yasuɛ abeǧaɛ u yarzem as tiṭṭawin nnes. \x ◘ \xo 9:14 \xt Mt. 12:1; Mk. 2:23; Lk. 6:1; Yḥ. 5:9. \x*  
\v 15 Sseqsan t Ifarisiyyen ɛawed: “Mammec tdewřed tᵉttwařid?” Yarra-dd xasen: “Igga abeǧaɛ x tiṭṭawin inu, xenni ssirdeɣ uca dewřeɣ ttwařiɣ.”  
\v 16 Ca zeg Ifarisiyyen nnan: “Bnadem-a war iǧi ca zi AREBBI, minzi Netta war ittweqqar ca ssebt.” Ca nneɣni nnan: “Mammec izemmar ijj n bnadem d aɛeffan ad igg řeɛřamat am tina?” Uca imsar ubeṭṭu jar asen. \x ◘ \xo 9:16 \xt Yḥ. 3:2; 7:12; 9:33; 10:19. \x*  
\v 17 Nnan ɛawed i udarɣař: “Min xas teqqared cek, ařami yarzem tiṭṭawin nnec?” Netta inna asen: “Aqa-t d anabi!” \x ◘ \xo 9:17 \xt Lk. 7:16; 24:19; Yḥ. 4:19; 6:14. \x*   
\m
\v 18 Maca Udayen war zzayes uminen ca belli netta tuɣa d adarɣař uca idweř ittwařa, ařami d řaɣan x lwalidin n wenni idewřen ittwařa.  
\v 19 Sseqsan ten: “Ma wa d mmitwem min xef teqqarem aqa ittwaxřeq-dd d adarɣař? I mammec igga ittwařa řexxu?”  
\v 20 Arrin-dd lwalidin nnes, nnan: “Neccin nessen belli wa d mmitneɣ, aqa ittwaxřeq-dd d adarɣař,  
\v 21 maca mammec igga ittwařa řexxu, war nessin, u wi d as yarezmen tiṭṭawin nnes war t nessin ca \add ɛawed\add*. Seqsam t simant nnes, netta aqa d abřiɣ, ad issiweř x yixef nnes.”  
\v 22 Nnan lwalidin nnes ammu minzi ggʷeden zeg Wudayen, minzi Udayen mɛahaden belli wenni i ɣa icehden aqa Netta d Lmasiḥ, ad t mmenḍaren zi temzida. \x ◘ \xo 9:22 \xt Yḥ. 7:13; 12:42. \x*  
\v 23 S uyenni nnan lwalidin nnes: “Netta aqa-t d abřiɣ, seqsam t simant nnes.”   
\m
\v 24 \add Xas uca\add* řaɣan-dd wiss martayen x weryaz wenni tuɣa d adarɣař, nnan as: “Sɛuǧa AREBBI! Aqa nessen belli Aryaz-a d ijj n umednub.” \x ◘ \xo 9:24 \xt Yac. 7:19. \x*  
\v 25 Netta yarra-dd, inna asen: “Ma Netta d amednub war ssineɣ. Necc ssneɣ ict n tmesřact, aqa tuɣa ayi d adarɣař, řexxu ttwařiɣ!”  
\v 26 Nnan as ɛawed: “Min zzayek igga? Mammec d ac igga yarzem tiṭṭawin nnec?”  
\v 27 Inna asen: “Aqa nniɣ awem t, \add maca\add* kenniw war tesřim. Mayemmi texsem ad t tesřem i twařa nneɣni? Ma texsem uřa d kenniw ad tdewřem d imeḥḍaren nnes?”  
\v 28 Kkwaren t, nnan: “Cek d ameḥḍar nnes! Maca neccin aqa d imeḥḍaren n Musa.  
\v 29 Neccin nessen aqa AREBBI issiweř ak-d Musa, maca Aryaz-a wanita war nessin ca manis Netta.”  
\v 30 Yarra-dd weryaz, inna asen: “Aqa di man aya řeɛjeb, kenniw war tessinem ca manis Netta, waxxa Netta yarzem ayi tiṭṭawin inu.  
\v 31 Neccin nessen, aqa AREBBI war ittesři ca ɣar imednab, maca mařa ca n ijjen ittweqqar i-t uca ittegg min ixs Netta, aqa Netta ad ɣares iseř. \x ◘ \xo 9:31 \xt Izhd. 66:18; Awřn. 15:29; 28:9; Ica. 1:15; Mixa 3:4. \x*  
\v 32 Ɛemmarṣ war ittwasři qaɛ, aqa ca n ijjen yarzem tiṭṭawin n ijjen ixřeq-dd d adarɣař.  
\v 33 Meɛlik Wa war iǧi ca zi AREBBI, war izemmar ad igg man aya!”  
\v 34 Arrin-dd, nnan as: “Cek txeřqed-dd tkemmřed di ddnub, ma xenni texsed ad aneɣ tesseřmaded?” \add Xenni\add* nḍaren t ɣar barra.   
\m
\v 35 Isřa Yasuɛ belli nḍaren t ɣar barra, uca umi t yufa, inna as: “Ma tumned di Mmis n AREBBI?”  
\v 36 Yarra-dd, inna: “Min iɛna Netta, \add a\add* Sidi, ḥima ad dayes amneɣ?”  
\v 37 Inna as Yasuɛ: “Aqa cek teẓrid t uřa d wenni akik issawařen aqa-t d Netta.”  
\v 38 Netta inna: “Umneɣ, a Sidi!”. Uca iɛebd as.  
\v 39 Yasuɛ inna: “I řḥukm i dd-usiɣ ɣar ddunect-a, ḥima ad ẓaren inni war ittwiřin, u \add ḥima\add* inni ittwařan ad darɣřen.” \x ◘ \xo 9:39 \xt Yḥ. 3:17; 12:47. \x*   
\m
\v 40 Sřin ca n Ifarisiyyen i kides iǧan man aya, nnan as: “Ma aqa d neccin ɛawed d idarɣařen?”  
\v 41 Inna asen Yasuɛ: “Maɛlik teǧam d idarɣařen war ɣarwem ittiři bu ddnub, maca řexxu teqqarem: ‘Aqa nettwařa!’ S uyenni ad iqqim ddnub nwem ibedd.”   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 10
\s1 Yasuɛ d Ameksa d Aṣebḥan  
\m
\v 1 “S tidett, s tidett, Necc ad awem iniɣ: Wenni war ittidfen zi tewwart ɣar řkuri n wuǧi, maca ad igeɛɛed manis nneɣni, aqa-t d aceffar d axewwan.  
\v 2 Maca wenni i ɣa yadfen zi tewwart, netta d ameksaw n tḥimart.  
\v 3 Aɛessas n tewwart ad as yarzem i wanita uca ad tseř tḥimart i tmijja nnes. Netta ad iřaɣa i wuǧi nnes s ismawen nsen uca ad ten issuffeɣ ɣar barra.  
\v 4 Awarni řami issuffeɣ marra taḥimart nnes, ad yuyur zzates, uca ad t-i-dd-ḍfaren wuǧi nnes, minzi ssnen tmijja nnes.  
\v 5 Maca abarrani war t tḍeffar tḥimart ɛemmarṣ, maca ad zzayes tarweř, minzi war tessin tmijja n ubarrani.”   
\m
\v 6 Inna asen Yasuɛ amettiř-a, maca nitni war fhimen ca i tmesřayin min xef tuɣa akidsen issawař.   
\m
\v 7 Yasuɛ inna asen ɛawed: “S tidett, s tidett, Necc ad awem iniɣ: Necc d Tawwart n tḥimart.  
\v 8 Marra inni dd-yusin \add qbeř inu\add* aqa aten d iceffaren d ixewwanen. Maca taḥimart war d asen tesři ca.  
\v 9 NECC d Tawwart. Wenni zzayi i ɣa yadfen, ad iddar. Netta ad yadef, ad iffeɣ uca ad yaf mani ɣa yarwes. \x ◘ \xo 10:9 \xt Yḥ. 14:6. \x*  
\v 10 Aceffar war dd-ittis mɣir ḥima ad yacar, ad ineɣ u ad isshellek. Necc \add maca\add* usiɣ-dd ḥima ad ɣarsen tiři Tudart d ufeyyeḍ.   
\m
\v 11 NECC d Ameksaw Aṣebḥan. Ameksaw Aṣebḥan issrusa tudart nnes i tḥimart nnes. \x ◘ \xo 10:11 \xt Ica. 40:11; Ḥiz. 34:11, 12, 15, 22, 23; Mixa 1:14; Ɛbr. 13:20; 1 Bṭ. 5:4. \x*  
\v 12 Maca amcaray, wenni war iǧi ca d ameksaw, war iǧi ca d bab n wuǧi, x minni i ɣa iẓar uccen yusa-dd, ad yejj taḥimart uca ad yarweř. Xenni ad dd-yas wuccen, ad ixḍef taḥimart uca ad tt izzuzar. \x ◘ \xo 10:12 \xt Zak. 11:16. \x*  
\v 13 Amcaray yarweř, minzi netta d amcaray, war t icqi taḥimart.  
\v 14 NECC d Ameksaw Aṣebḥan. Ssneɣ uǧi inu uca uǧi inu ssnen ayi, \x ◘ \xo 10:14 \xt 2 Tim. 2:19. \x*  
\v 15 am mammec i d ayi issen Baba, ammu i ssneɣ Necc Baba. Necc ad wceɣ tudart inu i tḥimart. \x ◘ \xo 10:15 \xt Mt. 11:27; Lk. 10:22; Yḥ. 6:46; 7:29. \x*  
\v 16 Ɣari ɛad uǧi nneɣni, inni war iǧin ca zi řkuři-ya. Icuwwar ayi ad ten dd-ssmuneɣ ɛawed uca ad sřen i tmijja inu, uca ad dewřen marra d ict n tḥimart \add sadu ufus n\add* ijj n Umeksaw. \x ◘ \xo 10:16 \xt Ḥiz. 37:22. \x*  
\v 17 S man aya ittexs ayi Baba, minzi Necc wciɣ tudart inu ḥima ad tt-i-dd-ksiɣ ɛawed. \x ◘ \xo 10:17 \xt Ica. 53:12. \x*  
\v 18 Uřa d ijj war zzayi tt iksi, maca Necc wciɣ tt s řxaḍar inu. Ɣari ṣṣulṭa ḥima ad tt wceɣ u ɣari ṣṣulṭa ḥima ad tt-i-dd-ksiɣ ɛawed. Tawṣeyyet-a ṭṭfeɣ tt zi Baba.” \x ◘ \xo 10:18 \xt Yḥ. 2:19. \x*   
\m
\v 19 Xenni imsar ɛawed ubeṭṭu jar Wudayen s ssibbet n wawařen-a. \x ◘ \xo 10:19 \xt Yḥ. 7:12; 9:16. \x*  
\v 20 Aṭṭas zzaysen nnan: “Aqa dayes ijj n cciṭan, Netta d aṭemmes ameqqran. Mayemmi ɣares tᵉttesřam?” \x ◘ \xo 10:20 \xt Yḥ. 7:20; 8:48, 52. \x*  
\v 21 Inneɣni nnan: “Awařen-a war ǧin ca n ijj n umaryaḥ. Ma izemmar ijj n cciṭan ad yarzem tiṭṭawin n idarɣařen?” \x ◘ \xo 10:21 \xt Uf. 4:11; Izhd. 94:9; 146:8. \x*   
\b  
\m  
\s1 Řɛid n Udeccen n Zzawect Tameqqrant  
\m
\v 22 Yiweḍ-dd Řɛid n Udeccen \add n Zzawect Tameqqrant\add* di Urcalim. Tuɣa d řmecta.  
\v 23 Yasuɛ iggur di Zzawect Tameqqrant deg useqqif ak-d ukulwar d ipilaren n Suliman. \x ◘ \xo 10:23 \xt 1 Ij. 6:3; Řex. 3:11; 5:12. \x*  
\v 24 Nnḍen as-dd Wudayen, nnan as: “Ař meřmi d aneɣ i ɣa tejjed nuyeř \add ɛad\add*? Mařa Cek d Lmasiḥ, ini aneɣ t s bṭayṭay.”  
\v 25 Yarra-dd Yasuɛ, inna asen: “Nniɣ awem t uca kenniw war tuminem. Řexdayem i ggiɣ s Yisem n Baba, cehhdent xafi. \x ◘ \xo 10:25 \xt Yḥ. 5:36. \x*  
\v 26 Maca kenniw war tuminem, minzi kenniw war teǧim ca d uǧi inu, am mammec tuɣa d awem nniɣ.  
\v 27 Uǧi inu isřa ɣar tmijja inu u Necc ssneɣ asen uca nitni ad ayi-dd ḍfaren. \x ◘ \xo 10:27 \xt Yḥ. 8:47. \x*  
\v 28 Ad asen wceɣ Tudart ittduman uca war ttwahellken ɛemmarṣ qaɛ uca uřa d ijj war ten ixeṭṭef zeg ufus inu. \x ◘ \xo 10:28 \xt Yḥ. 6:39; 17:12; 18:9. \x*  
\v 29 Baba wenni d ayi ten iwcin, aqa-t d ameqqran x kuřci. Uřa d ijj war izemmar ad \add ten\add* ixḍef zeg ufus n Baba.  
\v 30 Necc d Baba d Ijjen.” \x ◘ \xo 10:30 \xt Ica. 54:5; Yḥ. 5:19; 14:9; 17:5. \x*   
\b  
\m  
\s1 Udayen arezzun ad arejmen Yasuɛ  
\m
\v 31 Xenni ksin Wudayen ɛawed iẓra ḥima ad t arejmen. \x ◘ \xo 10:31 \xt Yḥ. 8:59; 11:8. \x*  
\v 32 Yasuɛ inna asen: “Aqa ssecneɣ awem aṭṭas n řexdayem tiṣebḥanin zi Baba. I man řxedmet zzaysent \add i texsem\add* ad ayi tarejmem?”  
\v 33 Nnan as Wudayen: “War Cek narejjem x ict n řxedmet taṣebḥant, maca umi tekfared u tarrid Ixef nnec d AREBBI, waxxa Cek d bnadem i teǧid.” \x ◘ \xo 10:33 \xt Yḥ. 5:18. \x*  
\v 34 Inna asen Yasuɛ: “Ma war turi di Ccariɛa nwem: ‘Necc nniɣ, aqa kenniw d irebbiten’? \x ◘ \xo 10:34 \xt Izhd. 82:6. \x*  
\v 35 Mařa Netta isemma ten ‘irebbiten’, yinni umi dd-yusa wawař n AREBBI, uca war izemmar ad ttwarẓent Tira \add Iqeddsen\add*,  
\v 36 mammec teqqarem kenniw x wenni ittwaqeddsen zi Baba u \add x wenni\add* issekk i-t-i-dd ɣar ddunect: ‘Aqa Cek tekfared!’, minzi Necc nniɣ: ‘Aqa Necc d Mmis n AREBBI’? \x ◘ \xo 10:36 \xt Yḥ. 5:1; 6:27. \x*  
\v 37 Mařa Necc war xeddmeɣ ca řexdayem n Baba, \add xenni\add* war dayi ttimnem ca. \x ◘ \xo 10:37 \xt Yḥ. 15:24. \x*  
\v 38 Maca mařa xedmeɣ tent, amnem xenni di řexdayem, waxxa kenniw ɛad war dayi tuminem, ḥima ad tessnem aqa Baba dayi u Necc aqa ayi di Baba.” \x ◘ \xo 10:38 \xt Yḥ. 14:11; 17:21. \x*   
\m
\v 39 Arezzun ad t ṭṭfen ɛawed, \add maca\add* ixtutteř asen jar ifassen nsen. \x ◘ \xo 10:39 \xt Lk. 4:29; Yḥ. 8:59. \x*  
\v 40 Iruḥ ɣar ujemmaḍ \add n iɣzar\add* n L’Urdun, ɣar wemcan mani tuɣa issɣeṭṭaṣ Yuḥanna deg umezwaru, uca iqqim dinni. \x ◘ \xo 10:40 \xt Yḥ. 1:28; 3:23. \x*  
\v 41 Usin-dd ɣares waṭṭas \add n iwdan\add*, nnan: “Yuḥanna war iggi uřa d ict n řeɛřamet, maca marra min inna x Weryaz-a d tidett!”  
\v 42 Uca umnen dayes aṭṭas \add diha\add*.   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 11
\s1 Asnekkar n Aliɛazar zi řmewt  
\m
\v 1 Tuɣa din ijj n bnadem ihřec, \add qqaren as\add* Aliɛazar, zi dcar n Bayt-Ɛanya. Netta tuɣa d umas n Maryam d Marta.  
\v 2 Maryam tanita nettat d tenni i tuɣa idehnen Yasuɛ s řefwaḥet n mirru u temseḥ iḍaren nnes s ucuwwaf nnes, u umas Aliɛazar tuɣa ihřec. \x ◘ \xo 11:2 \xt Mt. 26:6; Mk. 14:3; Lk. 7:37; Yḥ. 12:3. \x*  
\v 3 Ssekkent-i-dd tnayen n suyᵉtmas \add ijjen\add* ɣar Yasuɛ, nnant: “\add A\add* Siditneɣ, xzar, wenni texsed, aqa ihřec.”   
\m
\v 4 Maca Yasuɛ inna: “Řehřac-a war iǧi ca i řmewt, maca i uɛuǧi n AREBBI, ḥima ad zzayes ittwassɛuǧ Mmis n AREBBI.” \x ◘ \xo 11:4 \xt Yḥ. 9:3; 11:40. \x*  
\v 5 Tuɣa Yasuɛ ittexs Marta d Maryam d Aliɛazar.   
\m
\v 6 Ařami isřa aqa \add Aliɛazar\add* ihřec, řexdenni iqqim ɛad tnayen n wussan deg wemcan mani t tuɣa.  
\v 7 Awarni man aya inna i imeḥḍaren nnes: “Ejj aneɣ ad nraḥ ɛawed ɣar \add temmurt n\add* Yahudiyya!”  
\v 8 Imeḥḍaren nnan as: “\add A\add* Amseřmad nneɣ, drus zeg wami tuɣa Udayen arezzun ad Cek arejmen, mammec Cek ad traḥed dinni ɛawed?” \x ◘ \xo 11:8 \xt Yḥ. 8:59; 10:31. \x*  
\v 9 Yarra-dd Yasuɛ: “Ma war din tenɛac n tsaɛɛetin deg uziř? Mařa ca n yijjen yuyur s uziř, war ittneqriḍ ca, minzi ittwařa tafawt n ddunect-a.  
\v 10 Maca mařa ca n yijjen ad yuyur s ǧiřet, ad inqareḍ, minzi war dayes bu tfawt.”  
\v 11 Awarni řami inna man aya, inna asen: “Aliɛazar, ameddukkeř nneɣ aqa iṭṭeṣ, maca ad raḥeɣ ḥima ad t-i-dd-ssnekkareɣ.” \x ◘ \xo 11:11 \xt Mt. 9:24; Mk. 5:39; Lk. 8:52. \x*  
\v 12 Nnan as imeḥḍaren: “\add A\add* Siditneɣ, mařa netta iṭṭeṣ, \add xenni\add* ad iggenfa!”  
\v 13 \add Maca\add* Yasuɛ uɣa issawař x řmewt nnes, maca ittɣiř asen belli Netta issawař x arraḥet n yiḍeṣ.  
\v 14 Xenni inna asen Yasuɛ s bṭayṭay: “Aqa Aliɛazar immut.  
\v 15 U Necc farḥeɣ awem umi Necc war din ǧiɣ, ḥima ad tamnem. Maca ittxeṣṣa kenniw ad traḥem dinni.”  
\v 16 Inna Tuma, wenni umi qqaren ‘Acniw’, i imeḥḍaren imɛacaren nnes: “Ejj aneɣ ad nraḥ uřa d neccin, ḥima ad nemmet akides.”   
\m
\v 17 Řami dd-yiweḍ Yasuɛ ɣar Bayt-Ɛanya, yufa aqa ɛdun arebɛa n wussan zeg wami tuɣa-t deg wenḍeř.  
\v 18 Bayt-Ɛanya tuɣa tudes Urcalim, ɛřaḥař xemmesṭac ‘istadiyyen’, \add ɛřaḥař třata kilumitr\add*. \f ◼ \fr 11:18 \ft \+fk istadiyyen\ft  
\fp  ijj n řmeřɛeb di řweqt n Iyunaniyyen tuɣa ɣares ict tuzzugart n 185 mitr, ixs ad yini ‘ijj n ustadiy’.\f*  
\v 19 Aṭṭas n Wudayen usin-dd ɣar Marta d Maryam ḥima ad tent ɛezzan x umatsent.  
\v 20 Řami tesřa Marta, aqa Yasuɛ yiweḍ-dd, teffeɣ ḥima ad t teřqa, maca Maryam teqqim di taddart.  
\v 21 Tenna Marta i Yasuɛ: “\add A\add* Sidi, meɛlik Cek tuɣa da, iři war ittmetti ca uma.  
\v 22 Maca řexxu ɛad ssneɣ ɛawed belli marra min ɣa tᵉttared zi AREBBI, Netta ad ac t iwc.”  
\v 23 Yasuɛ inna as: “Ad dd-ikkar umam.”  
\v 24 Tenna as Marta: “Ssneɣ belli ad dd-ikkar di tnukra deg wass aneggaru.” \x ◘ \xo 11:24 \xt Dan. 12:2; Lk. 14:14; Yḥ. 5:29. \x*  
\v 25 Yasuɛ inna as: “NECC d Tanukra d Tudart. Wenni zzayi i ɣa yamnen, ad iddar, waxxa immut. \x ◘ \xo 11:25 \xt Yḥ. 1:4; 3:16, 36; 5:24; 6:47; 14:6; 1 Yḥ. 5:10. \x*  
\v 26 Marra wenni iddaren uca yumen zzayi, war ittmetti i řebda. Ma tumned di man aya?” \x ◘ \xo 11:26 \xt Yḥ. 6:51. \x*  
\v 27 Tenna as: “Wah, \add a\add* Sidi inu, umneɣ aqa Cek d Lmasiḥ, Mmis n AREBBI wenni tuɣa i d ttasen ɣar ddunect.” \x ◘ \xo 11:27 \xt Mt. 16:16; Mk. 8:29; Lk. 9:20; Yḥ. 6:69. \x*   
\m
\v 28 Awarni řami tenna aya, truḥ třaɣa i učmas Maryam s řḥess, tenna as: “Amseřmad nneɣ yusa-dd, ittřaɣa-dd xam.”  
\v 29 Řami tesřa Maryam aya, tekkar s tazřa, truḥ ɣares.  
\v 30 Tuɣa Yasuɛ war dd-yusi ca ɛad ɣar dcar, maca tuɣa-t \add ɛad\add* deg wemcan mani t teřqa Marta.  
\v 31 Uřa d Udayen, inni iǧan akides di taddart, tuɣa ttɛezzan tt, ḍeffaren tt řami ẓrin aqa Maryam tekkar s tazřa, teffeɣ, minzi ittɣiř asen aqa truḥ ɣar wenḍeř ḥima ad tru dinni.  
\v 32 Řami dd-tusa Maryam ɣar mani tuɣa Yasuɛ, uca teẓra i-t, tewḍa ɣar iḍaren nnes, tenna as: “A Sidi, meɛlik tuɣa Cek danita, iři uma war ittmetti ca!”   
\m
\v 33 Řami tt iẓra Yasuɛ tᵉttru, uřa d Wudayen inni dd-yusin akides ttrun, innehweř Arruḥ nnes, inhezz di řeɛmar nnes.  
\v 34 Inna: “Mani t tessarsem?” Nnan as: “Araḥ-dd, \add a\add* Siditneɣ, ad texzared!”  
\v 35 \add Xenni\add* ffɣent as-dd i Yasuɛ imeṭṭawen. \x ◘ \xo 11:35 \xt Lk. 19:41. \x*  
\v 36 Udayen nnan: “Xzarem, mecḥař t ittexs.”  
\v 37 \add Maca\add* ca zzaysen nnan: “Ma war izemmar Wa, wenni yarezmen tiṭṭawin i udarɣař, ad igg ca maḥend uřa d wanita war ittmetti ca?”   
\m
\v 38 Umi dd-yusa ɣar waxxam n wenḍeř, innehweř Yasuɛ aṭṭas deg Ixef nnes. Axxam n wenḍeř aqa-t d ijj n ifri uca ict n teṣḍart tuɣa temmars x wadaf nnes.  
\v 39 Yasuɛ inna: “Ksim taṣḍart-a.” Tenna as Marta, učmas n wenni immuten: “\add A\add* Sidi, aqa yarṣuḍ, minzi teɛdu xas arebɛa n wussan.”  
\v 40 Inna as Yasuɛ: “Ma war d am nniɣ, mařa tumned, ad tẓared aɛuǧi n AREBBI?”  
\v 41 Kksin taṣḍart. Xenni issgeɛɛed Yasuɛ tiṭṭawin nnes ɣar sennej, inna: “\add A\add* Baba, ɛafak řami d ayi tesřid.  
\v 42 Necc ssneɣ aqa řebda tᵉttesřid ɣari, maca di ṭṭweɛ n řɣaci i d ayi dd-innḍen, nniɣ t, ḥima ad amnen belli Cek tessekked ayi-dd.” \x ◘ \xo 11:42 \xt Yḥ. 12:30. \x*  
\v 43 Řami inna aya, iřaɣa s jjehd: “Aliɛazar, ffeɣ-dd!”  
\v 44 Řexdenni iffeɣ-dd umettin, tuɣa ifassen d iḍaren nnes carfen s řecfen \add n řeqṭen\add* u tuɣa ijj umendiř \add n řeqṭen\add* ittwacarf x uɣembub nnes. Inna asen Yasuɛ: “Fesyem as-dd. Jjem t ad iraḥ.” \x ◘ \xo 11:44 \xt Yḥ. 20:7. \x*   
\b  
\m  
\s1 Imɣaren n Wudayen arezzun ad nɣen Yasuɛ  
\m
\v 45 Aṭṭas n Wudayen inni dd-yusin ɣar Maryam, uca ẓrin min igga Yasuɛ, umnen zzayes. \x ◘ \xo 11:45 \xt [Mt. 26:1-5; Mk. 14:1-2; Lk. 22:1-2]\x*  
\v 46 Maca ca zzaysen ruḥen ɣar Ifarisiyyen, nnan asen min igga Yasuɛ.  
\v 47 Uca ggin imeqqranen n ikehhanen d Ifarisiyyen ijj n umuni, nnan: “Min ɣa negg, minzi Aryaz-a ittegg aṭṭas n řeɛřamat. \x ◘ \xo 11:47 \xt Izhd. 2:2; Mt. 26:3; Mk. 14:1; Lk. 22:2; Řex. 4:27. \x*  
\v 48 Mařa nejja i-t amya, marra ad zzayes amnen. \add Xenni\add* ad dd-asen Irumaniyyen, ad zzayneɣ kksen amcan nneɣ \add iqeddsen\add* uřa d \add iwdan n\add* řgens nneɣ.”  
\v 49 Inna asen ijjen zzaysen, aqa-t d Qayafa, netta d arrays n ikehhanen deg useggʷas nni: “Kenniw war tessinem walu,  
\v 50 uca war tefhimem ca belli ineffeɛ i neccin x minni i ɣa immet ijj n bnadem di ṭṭweɛ n řgens, uca war ittmetti ca řgens nneɣ marra.” \x ◘ \xo 11:50 \xt Yḥ. 18:14. \x*  
\v 51 War ini ca man aya zeg ixef nnes, maca, umi tuɣa d arrays n ikehhanen deg useggʷas nni, tuɣa ittnebba belli Yasuɛ ad immet di ṭṭweɛ n řgens.  
\v 52 War iǧi ḥaca di ṭṭweɛ n řgens, maca uřa ḥima ad issmun iḥenjiren ittwazuzzaren n AREBBI ɣar ijjen. \x ◘ \xo 11:52 \xt Afa. 2:14, 15, 16. \x*  
\v 53 Zeg wass nni nwan ad t nɣen.   
\m
\v 54 Maca Yasuɛ war iqqim iggur jar Wudayen s bṭayṭay, maca iruḥ ssenni ɣar ict n temmurt tudes řexřa, ɣar ict n tendint qqaren as Ifrayim, uca iqqim dinni ak-d imeḥḍaren nnes.   
\m
\v 55 Tuɣa \add Řɛid n Tɣarṣt n\add* Useɛdu n Wudayen ɛřayen yiweḍ-dd. Aṭṭas zi dcurat usin-dd ɣar Urcalim ḥima ad ṭehharen ixef nsen qbeř Řɛid. \x ◘ \xo 11:55 \xt Amz. 35:2, Uf. 19:10-11, Lawi 22:1-4, Řxř. 9:10, 2 Im. 30:17-18, Yḥ. 18:28, Řex. 21:18, 24, 26\x*  
\v 56 Nitni tuɣa arezzun x Yasuɛ, nnan jar asen umi nitni bedden di Zzawect Tameqqrant: “Min tᵉttwařam? Ma zeɛma war dd-ittis ɣar Řɛid?” \x ◘ \xo 11:56 \xt Yḥ. 7:11. \x*  
\v 57 \add Maca\add* imeqqranen n ikehhanen d Ifarisiyyen weṣṣan belli, mařa ca n yijjen issen mani iǧa, ad t ini, ḥima ad t ṭṭfen.   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 12
\s1 Adhan s řeɛṭur iɣřan di Bayt-Ɛanya  
\m
\v 1 Setta n wussan qbeř \add Řɛid n Tɣarṣt n\add* Useɛdu, yusa-dd Yasuɛ ɣar Bayt-Ɛanya, mani tuɣa iǧa Aliɛazar, wenni dd-issnekkar Yasuɛ zi taddart n imettinen. \x ◘ \xo 12:1 \xt [Mt. 26:6-13; Mk. 14:3-9] — Mt. 26:6; Mk. 14:3; Lk. 7:37; Yḥ. 11:2. \x*  
\v 2 Ggin as din ijj n umensi. Marta tuɣa tsexxar, u Aliɛazar tuɣa d ijjen zeg inni akides iqqimen \add ɣar ṭṭabřa\add*.  
\v 3 Teksi-dd Maryam ijj n uɣarraf n zzect i wedhan zi řeɛṭur n ṣṣenbel teṣfa tiɣřa, tedhen iḍaren n Yasuɛ, xenni temseḥ iḍaren nnes s ucuwwaf nnes. Taddart teccur s řefwaḥet n \add zzect n\add* wedhan.  
\v 4 Ijjen zeg imeḥḍaren nnes wenni umi qqaren Yahuda Isxariyuṭi wenni t i ɣa iɣdaren, inna:  
\v 5 “Mayemmi war temmenz ca řefwaḥet-a n ṣṣenbel s teřt mya n dinar, ḥima ad temmewc i imezřaḍ?” \x ◘ \xo 12:5 \xt Mk. 14:5. \x*  
\v 6 Netta inna aya, war iǧi minzi cqan t imezřaḍ, maca minzi netta d aceffar, tuɣa ɣares ssenduq, uca yarbu min dayes immarsen. \x ◘ \xo 12:6 \xt Yḥ. 13:29. \x*  
\v 7 Yasuɛ inna: “Jjem tt, aqa txemmeř i-tt i wass n wenḍeř inu. \x ◘ \xo 12:7 \xt Mk. 14:8. \x*  
\v 8 Minzi imezřaḍ aqa aten řebda akidwem, maca Necc war kidwem ǧiɣ i řebda.” \x ◘ \xo 12:8 \xt Aɛwd. 15:11; Mt. 26:11; Mk. 14:7. \x*   
\m
\v 9 Aṭṭas n řɣaci zeg Wudayen sřin belli Yasuɛ aqa-t dinni. Usin-dd nitni, war iǧi ḥaca zi ssibbet n Yasuɛ, maca ɛawed ḥima ad ẓaren Aliɛazar, wenni dd-issnekkar zi taddart n imettinen. \x ◘ \xo 12:9 \xt Yḥ. 11:44. \x*  
\v 10 Mcawaren imeqqranen n ikehhanen, ḥima ad nɣen uřa d Aliɛazar,  
\v 11 minzi aṭṭas n Wudayen ffɣen-dd zi ssibbet nnes uca umnen di Yasuɛ.   
\b  
\m  
\s1 Adaf n Yasuɛ ɣar Urcalim  
\m
\v 12 Tiwecca nnes, umi sřin aṭṭas n řɣaci inni dd yusin ɣar Řɛid belli Yasuɛ yusa-dd ɣar Urcalim, \x ◘ \xo 12:12 \xt [Mt. 21:1-11; Mk. 11:1-11; Lk. 19:28-40] — Mt. 21:8; Mk. 11:8; Lk. 19:36. \x*  
\v 13 ksin ifetwan n tini uca ffɣen, ḥima ad t řqan, řaɣan:  
\b  
\m \qt “Uṣanna!\qt*  
\m \qt Sseɛd n Wenni dd-yusin\qt*  
\m \qt s Yisem n SIDI,\qt*  
\m \qt Ajeǧid n Israil!”\qt* \x ◘ \xo 12:13 \xt Izhd. 118:25, 26; Mt. 21:9; Mk. 11:9, 10\x*   
\b  
\m
\v 14 Yufa Yasuɛ ijj n wesnus uca inya xas, am mammec tura:   
\b  
\m
\v 15 \qt “War tteggʷed ca, \+add a\+add* yeǧis n Ṣihyun,\qt*  
\m \qt xzar, Ajeǧid nnem ad dd-yas,\qt*  
\m \qt iqqim x wesnus, aḥenjir n teɣyuč.”\qt* \x ◘ \xo 12:15 \xt Ica. 62:11; Zak. 9:9; Mt. 21:5. \x*   
\b  
\m
\v 16 Imeḥḍaren nnes war fhimen ca timesřayin-a di řweqt nni. Maca awarni řami ittwassuɛřa Yasuɛ, řexdenni ɛeqřen belli man aya tura xas uca belli nitni ggin zzayes man aya.  
\v 17 Řɣaci i tuɣa iǧan akides, tuɣa iched aqa Netta iřaɣa-dd x Aliɛazar zeg wenḍeř uca issnekkar i-t-i-dd zi taddart n imettinen.  
\v 18 S man aya iffeɣ řɣaci ameqqran maḥend ad t mmeřqan, minzi nitni sřin belli igga řeɛřamet-a.  
\v 19 Ifarisiyyen nnan jar asen: “Tᵉttwařam mliḥ belli kenniw tᵉttakkwaḍem ɣar walu, xzarem, aqa qaɛ ddunect teḍfar i-t-i-dd.” \x ◘ \xo 12:19 \xt Yḥ. 11:47. \x*   
\b  
\m  
\s1 Yasuɛ issawař x řmewt d tnukra nnes  
\m
\v 20 Tuɣa din ca n iwdan zi řegnus jar asen inni dd-igeɛɛden \add ɣar Urcalim\add* ḥima ad ɛebden di Řɛid. \x ◘ \xo 12:20 \xt Řex. 8:27. \x*  
\v 21 Ina ruḥen ɣar Filippus, wenni zi \add tendint n\add* Bayt-Ṣayda di Ljalil. Sseqsan t, nnan: “A Sidi, nexs ad nẓar Yasuɛ.” \x ◘ \xo 12:21 \xt Yḥ. 1:45. \x*  
\v 22 Yusa-dd Filippus, inna \add tt\add* i Andrawus, uca Andrawus d Filippus nnan \add tt\add* i Yasuɛ.  
\v 23 Yasuɛ yarra-dd, inna asen: “Aqa tiweḍ-dd tsaɛɛet i di i ɣa ittwassɛuǧ Mmis n bnadem. \x ◘ \xo 12:23 \xt Yḥ. 13:32; 17:1. \x*  
\v 24 S tidett, s tidett, Necc ad awem iniɣ: Mařa war dd-iwḍi řḥebb n yirden di temmurt, ad immet, xenni ad iqqim weḥḥdes, maca mařa immut, xenni ad dd-yawi řɣiǧet aṭṭas. \x ◘ \xo 12:24 \xt 1 Kur. 15:36. \x*  
\v 25 Wenni ittexsen tudart nnes, ad tt ixsar, \add maca\add* wenni i ɣa icarhen tudart nnes di ddunect-a, ad tt ixemmeř i Tudart ittduman. \x ◘ \xo 12:25 \xt Mt. 10:39; 16:25; Mk. 8:35; Lk. 9:24; 17:33. \x*  
\v 26 Mařa ca n yijjen isexxar ayi, ejj i-t ad ayi iḍfar. Mani ɣa iřiɣ Necc, dinni i ɣa yiři ɛawed umsexxar inu. Mařa ca n ijjen ixdem ayi, ad t icenneɛ Baba. \x ◘ \xo 12:26 \xt Yḥ. 14:3; 17:24. \x*  
\v 27 Řexxu uř inu innehweř, min ɣa iniɣ? \add A\add* Baba, senjem ayi zi tsaɛɛet-a? Maca x uyenni i dd-usiɣ ɣar tsaɛɛet-a. \x ◘ \xo 12:27 \xt Mt. 26:37,38,39; Mk. 14:34; Lk. 22:44. \x*  
\v 28 \add A\add* Baba, sɛuǧi Isem nnec.” Xenni tusa-dd ict n tmijja zeg ujenna, \add tenna\add*: “Sɛuǧeɣ t uca ad t sɛuǧeɣ ɛawed!”  
\v 29 Řɣaci i tuɣa ibedden din isřa i-tt, nitni nnan: “Aqa imsar wajjaj.” Inneɣni nnan: “Aqa issiweř-dd ijj n lmalak akides.”   
\m
\v 30 Yarra-dd Yasuɛ, inna asen: “Tmijja-ya war teǧi ca di ṭṭweɛ inu maca di ṭṭweɛ nwem. \x ◘ \xo 12:30 \xt Yḥ. 11:42. \x*  
\v 31 Řexxu ad yiři řḥukm x ddunect-a, řexxu ad immenḍar umeqqran n ddunect-a ɣar barra. \x ◘ \xo 12:31 \xt Yḥ. 14:30; 16:11; Kul. 2:15. \x*  
\v 32 U Necc, x minni i ɣa ttwassgeɛɛdeɣ zi temmurt, ad ɣari dd-jebdeɣ marra.” \x ◘ \xo 12:32 \xt Řxř. 21:9; 2 Ij. 18:4; Yḥ. 3:14; 8:28. \x*  
\v 33 Inna man aya ḥima ad isscen ɣar man řmewt i ɣa immet.   
\m
\v 34 Řɣaci yarra-dd xas: “Neccin nesřa zi Ccariɛa aqa Lmasiḥ ad iqqim i řebda. I mammec teqqared Cek belli ittxeṣṣa i Mmis n bnadem ad ittwassgeɛɛed? Min iɛna Mmis-a n bnadem?” \x ◘ \xo 12:34 \xt 2 Ṣm. 7:16; 1 Im. 22:10; Izhd. 45:7; 89:37; 110:4; Ica. 9:5; Irm. 23:6; Ḥiz. 37:26; Dan. 2:44; 7:14, 27; Mixa 4:7; Ɛbr. 1:8. \x*  
\v 35 Yasuɛ inna asen: “Tafawt ad tiři akidwem drus n řweqt ɛad. Uyurem, řami ɣarwem Tafawt, ḥima war kenniw tᵉttᵉṭṭef taǧest. Wenni igguren di taǧest, war issin mani iggur. \x ◘ \xo 12:35 \xt Irm. 13:16; Yḥ. 1:9; 8:12; 9:5; 12:46; Afa. 5:8; 1 Ts. 5:4\x*  
\v 36 Amnem di Tfawt maḥend Tafawt ɛad aqa-tt ɣarwem, ḥima kenniw ad tiřim tarwa n Tfawt.” Ammu i tuɣa issawař Yasuɛ. \add Řexdenni\add* yuyur uca innufar zzaysen.   
\b  
\m  
\s1 Břa l’iman n Wudayen  
\m
\v 37 Waxxa tuɣa Netta ittegg marra řeɛřamat-a zzatsen, nitni war zzayes uminen ca,  
\v 38 ḥima ad ittwakemmeř wawař n unabi Icaɛya i innan:  
\b  
\m \qt “\+tl A\+tl* Sidi, wi yumnen s řexbar nneɣ\qt*  
\m \qt u i umi ittwassargeb ufus n SIDI?”\qt* \x ◘ \xo 12:38 \xt Ica. 53:1; Rum. 10:16. \x*   
\b  
\m
\v 39 S uyenni war zemmaren ad amnen, minzi Icaɛya inna ɛawed:   
\b  
\m
\v 40 \qt “Nitni ssdarɣřen tiṭṭawin \+tl n yixef\+tl* nsen,\qt*  
\m \qt sseqseḥen uřawen nsen,\qt*  
\m \qt ḥima war ttᵉtwiřin s tiṭṭawin nsen,\qt*  
\m \qt war fehhmen s wuř nsen,\qt*  
\m \qt ad tuben uca Necc ad ten ssgenfiɣ.”\qt* \x ◘ \xo 12:40 \xt Ica. 6:9-10; Ḥiz. 12:2; Mt. 13:14; Mk. 4:12; Lk. 8:10; Řex. 28:26; Rum. 11:8 \x*   
\b  
\m
\v 41 Inna Icaɛya ammu, umi iẓra aɛuǧi nnes uca tuɣa issawař xas. \x ◘ \xo 12:41 \xt Ica. 6:1. \x*  
\v 42 Umnen zzayes ɛawed aṭṭas n imeqqranen \add n řgens\add*, maca s ssibbet n Ifarisiyyen war zzayes cehden ca \add s bṭayṭay\add*, ḥima war ten ssuffuɣen zi temzida. \x ◘ \xo 12:42 \xt Yḥ. 7:13; 9:22. \x*  
\v 43 Minzi nitni tuɣa xsen aɛuǧi zeg iwdan x uɛuǧi zi AREBBI. \x ◘ \xo 12:43 \xt Yḥ. 5:44. \x*   
\m
\v 44 Maca Yasuɛ iřaɣa, inna: “Wenni dayi ittamnen, war dayi ittimen ca, maca deg Wenni d ayi dd-issekken.  
\v 45 Wenni d ayi iẓrin, iẓra wenni d ayi dd-issekken. \x ◘ \xo 12:45 \xt Yḥ. 10:30; 14:9. \x*  
\v 46 Necc d Tafawt i dd-yusin ɣar ddunect, ḥima kuř ijjen wenni dayi ittamnen, war ittɣimi ca di taǧest. \x ◘ \xo 12:46 \xt Ica. 42:6; 49:6; Yḥ. 1:9; 8:12; 9:5; 12:46; Řex. 13:47. \x*  
\v 47 Mařa ca n yijjen isřa i wawařen inu, \add maca\add* war daysen ittᵉṭṭef, Necc war xas ḥekkmeɣ ca. Necc war dd-usiɣ ca, ḥima ad ḥekmeɣ x ddunect, maca ḥima ad wceɣ Tudart i ddunect. \x ◘ \xo 12:47 \xt Yḥ. 3:17; 9:39. \x*  
\v 48 Wenni d ayi isseḥqaren uca war iqbiř awařen inu, ɣares wenni xas i ɣa iḥekmen: awař i nniɣ, ad xas iḥkem deg wass aneggaru. \x ◘ \xo 12:48 \xt Mk. 16:16; Yḥ. 3:18; 8:24. \x*  
\v 49 Minzi Necc war ssiwřeɣ ca zi ɣari, maca Baba Wenni d ayi-dd-issekken iwca ayi ict n tewṣeyyet x min ɣa iniɣ d min xef ɣa ssiwřeɣ,\x ◘ \xo 12:49 \xt Aɛwd. 18:18; Yḥ. 3:11; 5:20; 7:16; 8:28; 14:10, 24; 16:13. \x*  
\v 50 u Necc ssneɣ tiweṣṣa nnes, aqa atent d Tudart ittduman. S uya, min ssawařeɣ, ssawařeɣ t am mammec d ayi inna Baba.”   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 13
\s1 Asird n iḍaren n imeḥḍaren  
\m
\v 1 Qbeř i Řɛid n \add Tɣarṣt n\add* Useɛdu, umi issen Yasuɛ aqa tasaɛɛet nnes tiweḍ-dd belli ad iffeɣ zi ddunect-a ɣar Babas, tuɣa ittexs inni iǧan nnes, inni iǧan di ddunect, uca Netta ittexs i-ten ař aneggaru. \x ◘ \xo 13:1 \xt Mt. 26:2; Mk. 14:1; Lk. 22:1. \x*   
\m
\v 2 Ɣar umensi, umi iɛarn cciṭan uř n Yahuda, mmis n Cimɛun Isxariyuṭi, maḥend ad t isellem, \x ◘ \xo 13:2 \xt Lk. 22:3; Yḥ. 13:2. \x*  
\v 3 ikkar-dd Yasuɛ x umensi, minzi tuɣa issen belli Babas iwca as kuřci deg ifassen nnes u belli iffeɣ-dd zi ɣar AREBBI u ɣar AREBBI i ɣa iraḥ, \x ◘ \xo 13:3 \xt Mt. 11:27; Yḥ. 3:35; 16;28. \x*  
\v 4 uca ikkes arruḍ nnes, iksi ijj n umendiř uca ibyes i-t i Yixef nnes.  
\v 5 Ifarreɣ aman di tbanyut uca ibda issirid iḍaren n imeḥḍaren, imesseḥ asen s umendiř i zi tuɣa ibyes.   
\m
\v 6 Řami dd-yusa ɣar Cimɛun Buṭrus, inna as Cimɛun: “\add A\add* Sidi, ma ad tessirded iḍaren inu?” \x ◘ \xo 13:6 \xt Mt. 3:14. \x*  
\v 7 Yarra-dd Yasuɛ, inna as: “Cek war tefhimed ca řexxu min tteggeɣ, maca ad tfehmed man aya awarni manawenni.”  
\v 8 Inna as Cimɛun Buṭrus: “Qaɛ ɛemmarṣ ad tessirded iḍaren inu.” Yarra-dd xas Yasuɛ: “Mařa war d ac ssirdeɣ, war ɣarek tᵉttiři bu tasɣart akidi.”  
\v 9 Inna as Cimɛun Buṭrus: “\add A\add* Sidi, \add xenni\add* war tessirid iḍaren inu waha, maca uřa d ifassen inu d uzeǧif inu.”  
\v 10 Yasuɛ inna as: “Wenni ittwasirden qaɛ \add di tbanyut\add*, war iḥdij mɣir ad ttwasirden iḍaren nnes waha, minzi ɛad netta d amezdag. Uřa d kenniw tizdigem, maca war iǧi marra.” \x ◘ \xo 13:10 \xt Yḥ. 15:3. \x*  
\v 11 Yasuɛ tuɣa issen wi t ɣa iɣdaren, s uyenni inna: “Kenniw war teǧim ca marra d imezdag.” \x ◘ \xo 13:11 \xt Yḥ. 6:64. \x*   
\m
\v 12 Awarni řami issird iḍaren nsen, yarḍ arruḍ nnes \add ɛawed\add*, xenni iqqim, inna asen: “Ma tfehmem min daywem ggiɣ?  
\v 13 Kenniw tᵉttřaɣam ayi ‘Amseřmad nneɣ!’ d ‘Siditneɣ!’, uca tidett i tennam, minzi wa d Necc. \x ◘ \xo 13:13 \xt Mt. 23:8, 10; 1 Kur. 8:6; 12:3; Fil. 2:11. \x*  
\v 14 Mařa Necc d Sidi nwem d Amseřmad nwem, uca ssirdeɣ iḍaren nwem, mahu ittxeṣṣa uřa i kenniw ad tessirdem iḍaren ijjen i wenneɣni! \x ◘ \xo 13:14 \xt Gal. 6:1, 2. \x*  
\v 15 Minzi Necc zeɛma wciɣ awem amedya-ya, ḥima, am mammec ggiɣ Necc akidwem, ad teggem kenniw ɛawed \add ak-d wayawya\add*. \x ◘ \xo 13:15 \xt 1 Bṭ. 2:21; 1 Yḥ. 2:6. \x*  
\v 16 S tidett, s tidett, Necc ad awem iniɣ: War din iǧi umsexxar wenni yuɛřan x sides, uřa d areqqas yuɛřan x wenni i-t-i-dd-issekken. \x ◘ \xo 13:16 \xt Mt. 10:24; Lk. 6:40; Yḥ. 15:20. \x*  
\v 17 Mařa tessnem timesřayin-a, ad tiřim tᵉttwabarkem mařa teggim zzaysent.   
\b  
\m  
\s1 Yasuɛ issen wenni t i ɣa isellmen  
\m
\v 18 War t qqareɣ ca xawem marra, maɣar ssneɣ inni i xḍareɣ, maca ḥima ad ittwakemmeř min yuran deg Wedlis \add i iqqaren\add*: ‘Wenni i ɣa iccen zeg weɣrum akidi, aqa issgeɛɛed xafi anirz nnes.’ \x ◘ \xo 13:18 \xt [Mt. 26:20-25; Mk. 14:17-21; Lk. 22:21-23] — Izhd. 41:10; Mt. 26:23; 1 Yḥ. 2:19. \x*  
\v 19 Řexxu ad awem t iniɣ qbeř ma ad imsar, ḥima, x minni i ɣa imsar, ad tamnem belli aqa d Necc. \x ◘ \xo 13:19 \xt Yḥ. 14:29; 16:4. \x*  
\v 20 S tidett, s tidett, Necc ad awem iniɣ: Wenni i ɣa iqebřen wenni dd ɣa ssekkeɣ, ad ayi iqbeř, u wenni d ayi ɣa iqebřen, ad iqbeř uřa d Wenni d ayi dd-issekken.” \x ◘ \xo 13:20 \xt Mt. 10:40; Lk. 10:16. \x*  
\v 21 Řami inna Yasuɛ man aya, innehweř Arruḥ nnes aṭṭas, uca iched, inna: “S tidett, s tidett, Necc ad awem iniɣ: Ijjen zzaywem ad dayi iɣder!” \x ◘ \xo 13:21 \xt Mt. 26:21; Mk. 14:18; Lk. 22:21; Řex. 1:17; 1 Yḥ. 2:19. \x*  
\v 22 Imeḥḍaren xzaren ɣar wayawya, minzi war ssinen di min xef tuɣa issawař.  
\v 23 Tuɣa din ijjen zeg imeḥḍaren nnes i tuɣa ittexs Yasuɛ, tuɣa isenned ɣar weḥsin n Yasuɛ. \x ◘ \xo 13:23 \xt Yḥ. 20:2; 21:7, 20. \x*  
\v 24 Isscen Cimɛun Buṭrus ɣares, ḥima netta ad t isseqsa min iɛna wenni min xef tuɣa issawař \add ammu\add*.  
\v 25 Ameḥḍar nni yarra ixef nnes ittmeyyeř ɣar idmaren n Yasuɛ, inna as: “\add A\add* Sidi, min iɛna?”  
\v 26 Yarra-dd Yasuɛ, inna: “D wenni umi ɣa ssisneɣ \add ařeqqim n\add* weɣrum, ad as \add t\add* wceɣ.” Řexdenni issisen \add ařeqqim n\add* weɣrum, iwca as \add t-i\add*-dd i Yahuda, mmis n Cimɛun Isxariyuṭi.   
\m
\v 27 Awarni \add iṭṭef uřeqqim n\add* weɣrum, yudef i-t cciṭan. Inna as Yasuɛ: “Min \add texsed\add* ad t tegged, egg i-t deɣya.”  
\v 28 Uřa d ijj zeg inni tuɣa iqqimen \add ɣar umensi\add* war issin mayemmi Netta i d as inna man aya.  
\v 29 Maɣar ittɣiř asen i ca \add zzaysen\add*, umi Yahuda aqa-t x ssenduq, aqa Yasuɛ yumur i-t ḥima ad iseɣ ca min ḥdajen nitni i Řɛid, niɣ ḥima ad iwc ca i imezřaḍ. \x ◘ \xo 13:29 \xt Yḥ. 12:6. \x*  
\v 30 Wanita, awarni řami iṭṭef \add ařeqqim n\add* weɣrum, iffeɣ deɣya. Tuɣa d ǧiřet umi iffeɣ.   
\b  
\m  
\s1 Asɛuǧi n Yasuɛ - X tayri jar wawmaten  
\m
\v 31 Inna Yasuɛ: “Aqa řexxu ittwassɛuǧ Mmis n bnadem uca ittwassɛuǧ AREBBI dayes.  
\v 32 Mařa AREBBI aqa ittwassɛuǧ dayes, řexdenni AREBBI ad issɛuǧ Ixef nnes dayes, \add wah,\add* ad t issɛuǧ deɣya. \x ◘ \xo 13:32 \xt Yḥ. 12:23; 17:1. \x*  
\v 33 \add A\add* iḥenjiren inu imeẓyanen, Necc aqa ayi akidwem drus n řweqt ɛad. Kenniw ad xafi tarzum, uca am mammec nniɣ i Wudayen: ‘Mani ɣa raḥeɣ Necc, war tzemmarem ad dd-tasem!’, ammu i d awem ɣa iniɣ ɛawed řexxu. \x ◘ \xo 13:33 \xt Yḥ. 7:34; 8:21. \x*   
\m
\v 34 Tawṣeyyet n jdid i d awem ɣa wceɣ ḥima ad texsem ijjen wenneɣni. Am mammec Necc ttexseɣ kenniw, ittxeṣṣa uřa d kenniw ad texsem ayawya. \x ◘ \xo 13:34 \xt Lawi 19:18; Mt. 22:39; Yḥ. 15:12; Afa. 5:2; 1 Ts. 4:9; 1 Bṭ. 4:8; 1 Yḥ. 2:23, 3:23; 4:21.\x*  
\v 35 S man aya ad ssnen marra, aqa kenniw d imeḥḍaren inu, mařa din ɣarwem tayri jar awem.” \x ◘ \xo 13:35 \xt 1 Yḥ. 2:5; 4:20. \x*   
\b  
\m  
\s1 Yasuɛ izwar issiwiř x wenkar n Buṭrus  
\m
\v 36 Cimɛun Buṭrus inna as: “\add A\add* Siditneɣ, mani ɣa traḥed?” Yarra-dd Yasuɛ, inna as: “Mani ɣa raḥeɣ Necc, war tzemmared řexxu ad ayi teḍfared, maca ɣar uneggaru ad tased.” \x ◘ \xo 13:36 \xt [Mt. 26:31-35; Mk. 14:27-31; Lk. 22:31-34] — Yḥ. 21:18; 2 Bṭ. 1:14. \x*  
\v 37 Cimɛun Buṭrus inna as: “\add A\add* Sidi, mayemmi war zemmareɣ ad aseɣ awarni ac řexxu? Necc ad wceɣ tudart inu i Cek.” \x ◘ \xo 13:37 \xt Mt. 26:33; Mk. 14:29; Lk. 22:33. \x*  
\v 38 Inna as Yasuɛ: “Ma texsed ad tessarsed tudart nnec di ṭṭweɛ inu? S tidett, s tidett, Necc ad ac iniɣ: War isququɛ uyaẓiḍ, qbeř ma ad ayi tenkared třata n twařawin.” \x ◘ \xo 13:38 \xt Mt. 26:34; Mk. 14:30; Lk. 22:34. \x*   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 14
\s1 Yasuɛ Netta d Abrid d Tidett d Tudart  
\m
\v 1 “War ttejjim ad innehweř uř nwem. Kenniw tumnem di AREBBI, amnem ɛawed dayi.  
\v 2 Di taddart n Baba dayes aṭṭas n tzeddiɣin. Meɛlik war iǧi amenni, iři nniɣ awem t, minzi Necc ad raḥeɣ, ḥima ad awem sswejdeɣ amcan.  
\v 3 Awarni řami ruḥeɣ uca sswejdeɣ awem amcan, xenni ad ɛeqbeɣ, ad kenniw dd-awyeɣ ɣari, ḥima, mani ǧiɣ Necc, ad din tiřim uřa d kenniw. \x ◘ \xo 14:3 \xt Yḥ. 12:26; 17:24. \x*  
\v 4 Aqa tessnem mani ɣa raḥeɣ uca tessnem abrid.”   
\m
\v 5 Inna as Tuma: “\add A\add* Siditneɣ, war nessin mani ɣa traḥed i mammec nzemmar ad nessen abrid?”  
\v 6 Yasuɛ inna as: “NECC d Abrid d Tidett d Tudart, war dd-ittis uřa d ijj ɣar Baba mɣir zzayi. \x ◘ \xo 14:6 \xt Yḥ. 1:4, 17; 10:9; 11:25; Ɛbr. 9:8. \x*  
\v 7 Mařa tuɣa tessnem ayi, ad tiři aqa tessnem uřa d Baba. Zi řexxu aqa tessnem t, teẓrim t.”   
\m
\v 8 Filippus inna as: “\add A\add* Siditneɣ, scen aneɣ Babac, uca ikfa.”  
\v 9 Yasuɛ inna as: “Anect uya n řweqt qaɛ Necc akidwem, ma war d ayi tessined \add ɛad\add*, \add a\add* Filippus? Wenni d ayi iẓrin, iẓra Baba. Mammec teqqared: ‘Scen aneɣ Babac’? \x ◘ \xo 14:9 \xt Yḥ. 10:30. \x*  
\v 10 Ma war tumined ca aqa Necc aqa ayi di Baba d Baba aqa-t dayi? Awařen i qqareɣ, war ten qqareɣ ca zi ɣari, maca Baba wenni dayi izeddɣen, Netta ittegg řexdayem-a. \x ◘ \xo 14:10 \xt Yḥ. 5:17; 7:16; 8:28; 10:38; 12:49; 16:13; 17:21. \x*  
\v 11 Amnem ayi, aqa Necc aqa ayi di Baba u Baba aqa-t dayi, u mařa lla, amnem ayi x ssibbet n řexdayem simant nsent.  
\v 12 S tidett, s tidett, Necc ad awem iniɣ: Wenni dayi yumnen, aqa řexdayem i tteggeɣ, ad zzaysent igg uřa d netta, uca ad igg tinni iǧan d timeqqranin x man aya, minzi Necc ad raḥeɣ ɣar Baba. \x ◘ \xo 14:12 \xt Mt. 21:21; Lk. 17:6; Řex. 5:12; 19:11. \x*  
\v 13 Uca marra min ɣa tᵉttarem s Yisem inu, ad t ggeɣ i kenniw, ḥima ad ittwassɛuǧ Baba di Mmis. \x ◘ \xo 14:13 \xt Irm. 29:12; Mt. 7:7; 21:22; Mk. 11:24; Lk. 11:9; Yḥ. 15:7; 16:24; Yaɛ. 1:5; 1 Yḥ. 3:22. \x*  
\v 14 Mařa d ayi ɣa tᵉttarem s Yisem inu, ad t ggeɣ.   
\b  
\m  
\s1 Lwaɛd n Arruḥ Iqeddsen  
\m
\v 15 Mařa texsem ayi, ṭṭfem di tweṣṣa inu, \x ◘ \xo 14:15 \xt Yḥ. 14:21, 23; 15:10; 1 Yḥ. 5:3. \x*  
\v 16 uca Necc ad ẓẓaǧeɣ i Baba u Netta ad awem iwc ijj n Umseṣřaḥ \bd nneɣni\bd*, ḥima ad kiwem iqqim i řebda:  
\v 17 Arruḥ n tidett tenni war tzemmar ddunect ad t teqbeř, minzi war t tᵉttwiři, war t tessin. Maca kenniw tessnem t, minzi Netta ittɣima akidwem u Netta aqa-t daywem.”   
\m
\v 18 “War kenniw ttejjiɣ ca d iyujiřen, maɣar awarni drus n řweqt Necc ad ɣarwem dd-aseɣ \add ɛawed\add*. \x ◘ \xo 14:18 \xt Mt. 28:20. \x*  
\v 19 Ddunect war d ayi tẓarr, maca kenniw ad ayi twařam. Minzi Necc ddareɣ, ad teddarem uřa d kenniw.  
\v 20 Deg wass nni ad tessnem, aqa Necc aqa ayi di Baba, kenniw dayi u Necc daywem.   
\m
\v 21 Wenni ɣar iǧa tiweṣṣa inu uca ad daysent iṭṭef, d wenni d ayi ittexsen, u wenni d ayi ittexsen, uřa d Baba ad t ixs u Necc ad t xseɣ \add ɛawed\add* uca ad as ssecneɣ Ixef inu.”  
\v 22 Inna as Yahuda, war iǧi d Isxariyuṭi: “\add A\add* Sidi, mammec d aneɣ i ɣa tessecned Ixef nnec, war iǧi ca i ddunect?”  
\v 23 Yasuɛ yarra-dd, inna as: “Mařa ca n yijjen ixs ayi, xenni ad iṭṭef deg wawař inu uca Baba ad t ixs, uca ɣares i dd ɣa nas u ɣares i ɣa negg tazeddiɣt nneɣ.  
\v 24 Wenni war d ayi ittexsen, war ittᵉṭṭif ca deg wawař inu, uca awař-a i tesřim, war iǧi ca zi ɣari, maca zi Baba, wenni d ayi dd-issekken. \x ◘ \xo 14:24 \xt Yḥ. 7:16; 8:28; 12:49; 14:10; 16:13. \x*   
\m
\v 25 Ssiwřeɣ akidwem man aya umi Necc \add ɛad\add* akidwem.  
\v 26 Maca Umseṣřaḥ, Arruḥ Iqeddsen, Wenni i dd ɣa issekk Baba s Yisem inu, ad awem isseřmed kuřci, ad awem issfekkar marra min d awem nniɣ. \x ◘ \xo 14:26 \xt Lk. 24:49; Yḥ. 15:26; 16:7, 13; Řex. 2:4. \x*   
\m
\v 27 Řehna ad awem t jjeɣ, Necc ad awem wceɣ řehna inu. Necc ad awem \add t\add* wceɣ, war iǧi ca am mammec \add t\add* tᵉttic ddunect. War tejjim ad innehweř uř nwem, war tteggʷedem ca. \x ◘ \xo 14:27 \xt Fil. 4:7. \x*  
\v 28 Aqa tesřim Necc nniɣ awem: ‘Necc ad uyureɣ uca ad ɣarwem dd-aseɣ ɛawed’. Mařa texsem ayi, ad tfarḥem, minzi aqa ad raḥeɣ ɣar Baba, minzi Baba imɣar xafi! \x ◘ \xo 14:28 \xt Yḥ. 14:3. \x*  
\v 29 Uca řexxu, xzar, Necc nniɣ awem tt qbeř ma ad yiři, ḥima kenniw, x minni i ɣa yiři uya, ad tamnem. \x ◘ \xo 14:29 \xt Yḥ. 13:19; 16:4. \x*  
\v 30 Awarni man aya war kiwem ssiwiřeɣ \add ɛad\add* aṭṭas ktar, maɣar ad dd-yas umeqqran n ddunect-a, war ɣares ittiři walu dayi, \x ◘ \xo 14:30 \xt Yḥ. 12:31; 16:11; Afa. 2:2. \x*  
\v 31 maca ittxeṣṣa ad tessen ddunect aqa Necc ttexseɣ Baba uca tteggeɣ min d ayi iweṣṣa Baba. Kkarem, ad nuyur ssanita.” \x ◘ \xo 14:31 \xt Yḥ. 10:18; Ɛbr. 10:5. \x*   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 15
\s1 Tazayart d tiṣedwin nnes  
\m
\v 1 “NECC d Tazayart n tidett, Baba d bab n weḥwic n tzayart.  
\v 2 Kuř taseṭṭa dayi i war itticen řɣiǧet, ad tt ikkes, uca kuř \add taseṭṭa\add* i dd-ittawyen řɣiǧet, ad tt issizdeg, ḥima ad tarni di řɣiǧet. \x ◘ \xo 15:2 \xt Mt. 15:13. \x*  
\v 3 Kenniw aqa tᵉttwassizedgem zi ssibbet n wawař i d awem nniɣ. \x ◘ \xo 15:3 \xt Yḥ. 13:10. \x*  
\v 4 Qqimem dayi, \add am mammec\add* Necc aqa ayi daywem. Am tseṭṭa i war izemmaren ad dd-tawyi řɣiǧet zeg ixef nnes mařa war teqqim di tzayart, amya uřa d kenniw, mɣir mařa teqqimem dayi.  
\v 5 NECC d Tazayart, kenniw d tiseḍwin. Wenni dayi i ɣa iqqimen u Necc dayes, netta ad dd-yawi řɣiǧet aṭṭas, minzi břa zzayi war tzemmarem ad teggem walu.  
\v 6 Mařa ca n yijjen war dayi iqqim, ad immenḍar ɣar barra am tseṭṭa tuẓeɣ, xenni ad tt yarwen, ad tt nḍaren di tmessi, ad yareɣ. \x ◘ \xo 15:6 \xt Ḥiz. 15:2-8; Mt. 3:10; 7:19; Kul. 1:23. \x*  
\v 7 Maca mařa teqqimem dayi uca awařen inu ad daywem qqimen, ttarem min texsem uca ad ɣarwem yiři. \x ◘ \xo 15:7 \xt Irm. 29:12; Mt. 7:7; 21:22; Mk. 11:24; Lk. 11:9; Yḥ. 14:13; 16:24; Yaɛ. 1:5; 1 Yḥ. 3:22; 5:14. \x*  
\v 8 Zi man aya ad ittwassɛuǧ Baba, xmi i dd ɣa tawyem aṭṭas n řɣiǧet uca ad tiřim d imeḥḍaren inu.   
\m
\v 9 Am mammec Baba tuɣa ittexs ayi, ammu uřa d Necc tuɣa ttexseɣ kenniw. Qqimem di tayri inu.  
\v 10 Mařa tᵉṭṭfem di tweṣṣa inu, ad teqqimem di tayri inu, am mammec Necc tuɣa ttᵉṭṭfeɣ di tweṣṣa n Baba uca ttɣimeɣ di tayri nnes. \x ◘ \xo 15:10 \xt Yḥ. 14:15, 21, 23; 1 Yḥ. 5:3. \x*   
\m
\v 11 Nniɣ awem man aya, ḥima ad daywem tiři řefraḥet inu uca ḥima ad tᵉttwakemmeř řefraḥet nwem.  
\v 12 Tawṣeyyet inu d tanita: aqa ad texsem ijjen wenneɣni am mammec Necc tuɣa xseɣ kenniw. \x ◘ \xo 15:12 \xt Lawi 19:18; Mt. 22:39; Yḥ. 13:34; Afa. 5:2; 1 Ts. 4:9; 1 Bṭ. 4:8; 1 Yḥ. 3:23; 4:21. \x*  
\v 13 Uřa d ijj war ɣares bu tayri tameqqrant x tanita: belli ca n yijjen ad iwc tudart nnes i imeddukkař nnes. \x ◘ \xo 15:13 \xt Rum. 5:7; Afa. 5:2; 1 Yḥ. 3:16. \x*  
\v 14 Kenniw d imeddukkař inu, mařa teggim marra min kenniw weṣṣiɣ. \x ◘ \xo 15:14 \xt Mt. 12:50; 2 Kur. 5:16; Gal. 5:6; 6:15; Kul. 3:11. \x*  
\v 15 War ttɛiwideɣ ad awem semmiɣ ‘imsexxaren’, minzi amsexxar war issin min ittegg sidis. Maca Necc tuɣa ttřaɣiɣ awem d ‘imeddukkař inu!’, minzi Necc ssecneɣ kenniw marra min sřiɣ zi Baba. \x ◘ \xo 15:15 \xt Yḥ. 8:26. \x*  
\v 16 War iǧi d kenniw i d ayi ixḍaren, maca d Necc i kenniw ixḍaren uca Necc ggiɣ kenniw ḥima ad traḥem, ad dd-tawyem řɣiǧet u ḥima ad teqqim řɣiǧet nwem, ḥima marra min ɣa tᵉttarem zi Baba s Yisem inu, ad awem \add t\add* iwc Netta. \x ◘ \xo 15:16 \xt Mt. 28:19; Mk. 16:15; Yḥ. 13:18; Afa. 1:4; Kul. 1:6. \x*  
\v 17 D man aya i zi kenniw umureɣ, ḥima ad texsem ijjen wenneɣni.”   
\b  
\m  
\s1 Ddunect tcarreh Yasuɛ  
\m
\v 18 “Mařa ddunect ad kenniw tcarh, snem aqa tcarh ayi qbeř kenniw. \x ◘ \xo 15:18 \xt 1 Yḥ. 3:13. \x*  
\v 19 Mařa aqa kenniw zi ddunect, iři aqa ddunect tuɣa tᵉttexs inni zzayes. Maca minzi kenniw war teǧim ca zi ddunect, maca Necc ixḍareɣ kenniw zi ddunect, s uyenni tcarreh ddunect kenniw. \x ◘ \xo 15:19 \xt Yḥ. 17:14; Gal. 1:10. \x*  
\v 20 Ɛeqřem awař i d awem nniɣ: ‘Amsexxar war yuɛři x sidis!’ Mařa darracen ayi, ad kenniw darrcen ɛawed. Mařa ṭṭfen deg wawař inu, ad ṭṭfen ɛawed deg wawař nwem. \x ◘ \xo 15:20 \xt Mt. 10:24; 24:9; Lk. 6:40; Yḥ. 13:16; 16:2. \x*  
\v 21 Maca ad zzaywem ggen man aya marra di ssibbet n Yisem inu, minzi nitni war ssinen ca Wenni d ayi dd-issekken. \x ◘ \xo 15:21 \xt Mt. 10:22; Yḥ. 16:3. \x*  
\v 22 Mařa war dd-usiɣ u war kisen ssiwřeɣ, ad yiři war ɣarsen bu ddnub. Maca řexxu war ɣarsen bu smaḥet x ddnub nsen. \x ◘ \xo 15:22 \xt Rum. 4:15; 5:20. \x*  
\v 23 Wenni d ayi icarrhen, ad icarh uřa d Baba.  
\v 24 Mařa war ggiɣ zzat i tiṭṭawin nsen řexdayem i war tent yeggi uřa d ijj bnadem nneɣni, ad yiři war ɣarsen bu ddnub. Maca řexxu ẓrin \add tent\add*, carhen ayi Necc uřa d Baba. \x ◘ \xo 15:24 \xt Yḥ. 10:37. \x*  
\v 25 S uya ad ittwakemmeř wawař i yuran di Ccariɛa nsen: ‘Carhen ayi x walu’. \x ◘ \xo 15:25 \xt Izhd. 35:19; 69:5. \x*   
\m
\v 26 Xmi dd ɣa yas Umseṣřaḥ, wenni ɣarwem dd ɣa ssekkeɣ zi Baba, Arruḥ n tidett i dd-yusin zi ɣar Baba, xenni wanita ad ayi iched. \x ◘ \xo 15:26 \xt Lk. 24:49; Yḥ. 14:26; 16:7; Řex. 5:32. \x*  
\v 27 Uca ad tcehdem uřa d kenniw, minzi tuɣa kenniw akidi zeg umezwaru.” \x ◘ \xo 15:27 \xt Řex. 1:8, 21; 5:32. \x*   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 16
\s1 Arruḥ Iqeddsen d Amefdi nneɣni  
\m
\v 1 “Aqa ssiwřeɣ akidwem aya, ḥima war ttenqarḍem.  
\v 2 Ad kenniw ssuffɣen zi temzidawin nsen. Iwa, tasaɛɛet ad dd-tas umi kuř ijjen wenni kenniw i ɣa inɣen, ad as ittɣiř aqa iwca ict n tewhibt i AREBBI. \x ◘ \xo 16:2 \xt Yḥ. 9:22, 34; 12:42. \x*  
\v 3 Ad zzaywem ggen man aya, minzi nitni war ssinen Baba uřa d Necc. \x ◘ \xo 16:3 \xt Yḥ. 15:21; 1 Kur. 2:8. \x*  
\v 4 Maca aqa nniɣ awem man aya, ḥima, xmi i dd ɣa tas tsaɛɛet, xenni ad tɛeqřem x man aya. Necc war daywem nniɣ ca man aya qbeř, minzi Necc tuɣa ayi \add ɛad\add* akidwem. \x ◘ \xo 16:4 \xt Yḥ. 13:19; 14:29. \x*  
\v 5 Maca řexxu ad raḥeɣ ɣar Wenni d ayi dd-issekken, \add maca\add* uřa d ijj zzaywem war d ayi isseqsi: ‘Mani ɣa traḥed?’  
\v 6 Maɣar minzi nniɣ awem man aya, aqa acḍan iccur uřawen nwem.  
\v 7 Maca Necc ad awem iniɣ tidett: Ḥsen awem ad raḥeɣ, maɣar mařa war ruḥeɣ ca, war ɣarwem dd-ittis Umseṣřaḥ. Mařa ruḥeɣ, ad awem t-i-dd-ssekkeɣ. \x ◘ \xo 16:7 \xt Lk. 24:49; Yḥ. 14:26; 15:26. \x*  
\v 8 Řami dd-yusa wanita, ad isseqneɛ ddunect x ddnub, x tsegda u x řḥukm.  
\v 9 X ddnub minzi nitni war zzayi uminen,  
\v 10 x tsegda, minzi Necc ad raḥeɣ ɣar Baba uca war d ayi tẓarrem ɛad,  
\v 11 uca x řḥukm, minzi ameqqran n ddunect-a aqa ittwaḥaseb. \x ◘ \xo 16:11 \xt Yḥ. 12:31; 14:30; Afa. 2:2; Kul. 2:15. \x*   
\m
\v 12 Ɣari aṭṭas min daywem i ɣa iniɣ, maca řexxu war tzemmarem ad t teksim.  
\v 13 Maca řami dd-yusa Arruḥ n tidett, ad kenniw indeh di marra tidett, minzi Netta war issiwiř ca zeg Ixef nnes, maca marra min ɣa isřa, ad zzayes issiweř, uca ad awem isscen timesřayin i dd ɣa yasen. \x ◘ \xo 16:13 \xt Yḥ. 12:49; 14:26\x*  
\v 14 Netta ad ayi issɛuǧ, minzi ad iksi zi min ɣari uca ad kenniw issargeb zzayes.  
\v 15 Marra min iǧan ɣar Baba, aqa-t inu. S uyenni nniɣ, belli Netta ad iksi zi min ɣari uca ad kenniw tt issargeb.” \x ◘ \xo 16:15 \xt Yḥ. 17:10. \x*   
\b  
\m  
\s1 Řweqt n wecḍan ad tedweř d řefraḥet  
\m
\v 16 “War ittɣimi ca uca war d ayi tẓarrem \add ɛad\add*, u xenni \add ɛawed\add* war ittɣimi ca uca ad ayi tẓarem, minzi Necc ad raḥeɣ ɣar Baba.” \x ◘ \xo 16:16 \xt Yḥ. 7:33. \x*   
\m
\v 17 Imeḥḍaren nnes nnan jar asen: “Manawya min d aneɣ inna: ‘War ittɣimi ca uca war d ayi tẓarrem \add ɛad\add* u xenni ɛawed war ittɣimi ca uca ad ayi tẓarem!’ u: ‘Necc ad raḥeɣ ɣar Baba’?”  
\v 18 Uca nitni nnan: “Manawya min iqqar: ‘War ittɣimi ca’? War nessin ca min xef issawař.”  
\v 19 Issen Yasuɛ min xsen ad t sseqsan, inna asen: “Ma temmseqsam minzi nniɣ: ‘War ittɣimi ca uca war d ayi tẓarrem \add ɛad\add* u xenni ɛawed war ittɣimi ca uca ad ayi tẓarem’?”   
\m
\v 20 “S tidett, s tidett, Necc ad awem iniɣ: Kenniw ad trum, ad tɛebbsem, maca ddunect ad tfarḥ. Kenniw ad tceḍnem, maca acḍan nwem ad idweř d řefraḥet.  
\v 21 Tamɣart, xmi ɣa taruw, ad dayes yiři řeḥriq, minzi tasaɛɛet nnes aqa tiweḍ-dd. Maca xmi dd ɣa taruw mmis, war tfekkar ca ɛad di řmeḥnet nnes s řefraḥet, minzi tarni-dd ijj n bnadem ɣar ddunect. \x ◘ \xo 16:21 \xt Ica. 26:17. \x*  
\v 22 Uřa d kenniw aqa daywem acḍan řexxu, maca ad kenniw ẓareɣ ɛawed, uca ad farḥen wuřawen nwem uca uřa d ijj war zzaywem ittekkes řefraḥet nwem.   
\m
\v 23 Deg wass nni war d ayi tᵉttarem ca. S tidett, s tidett, Necc ad awem iniɣ: Marra min ɣa tᵉttarem zi Baba s Yisem inu, ad awem t iwc. \x ◘ \xo 16:23 \xt Irm. 29:12; Mt. 7:7; 21:22; Mk. 11:24; Lk. 11:9; Yḥ. 14:13; 15:7; Yaɛ. 1:5; 1 Yḥ. 3:22; 5:14. \x*  
\v 24 Ař i řexxu war tᵉttarem ca s Yisem inu. Ttarem, ad teksim, ḥima ad tiři řefraḥet nwem tekmeř.   
\m
\v 25 Ssiwřeɣ awem x man aya s imedya, maca ad dd-taweḍ tsaɛɛet i di war ɣarwem i ɣa ssiwiřeɣ ɛad s imettiřen, maca ad awem barrḥeɣ x Baba s bṭayṭay.  
\v 26 Deg wass nni ad tᵉttarem s Yisem inu. Necc war d awem qqareɣ ca belli ad ttareɣ \add ca\add* zi Baba di ṭṭweɛ nwem,  
\v 27 minzi Baba simant nnes ittexs kenniw, minzi kenniw tuɣa tᵉttexsem ayi uca aqa tumnem aqa Necc zi ɣar AREBBI i dd-ffɣeɣ. \x ◘ \xo 16:27 \xt Yḥ. 17:8. \x*  
\v 28 Ffɣeɣ-dd zi Baba, usiɣ-dd ɣar ddunect. Ad jjeɣ ɛawed ddunect uca ad raḥeɣ ɣar Baba.” \x ◘ \xo 16:28 \xt Yḥ. 13:3. \x*   
\m
\v 29 Nnan as imeḥḍaren nnes: “Aqa řexxu tessawařed s bṭayṭay, war tessiwiřed ca s uřa d ijj n umedya.  
\v 30 Řexxu nessen aqa tessned kuřci, war teḥdijed ad Cek isseqsa ḥed. Zi manawenni numen aqa Cek teffɣed-dd zi AREBBI.” \x ◘ \xo 16:30 \xt Yḥ. 21:17. \x*  
\v 31 Yasuɛ yarra-dd xasen: “Ma řexxu tumnem?  
\v 32 Ad dd-taweḍ tsaɛɛet, aqa tiweḍ-dd, i di i ɣa tᵉttwazuzzarem, kuř ijj ad iṭṭef ɣar wemcan nnes, ad ayi tejjem weḥḥdi, \add maca\add* Necc war ǧiɣ bu weḥḥdi, minzi Baba aqa-t akidi. \x ◘ \xo 16:32 \xt Zak. 13:7; Mt. 26:31; Mk. 14:27; Yḥ. 8:29; 14:10. \x*  
\v 33 Aqa ssiwřeɣ akidwem s man aya, ḥima ad ɣarwem yiři řehna dayi. Di ddunect ad ɣarwem tiři řmeḥnet, maca ggem uř, Necc aqa ɣellbeɣ x ddunect.” \x ◘ \xo 16:33 \xt 2 Ij. 6:16; 2 Im. 32:7; Ica. 9:5; Yḥ. 14:27; 16:33; Rum. 5:1; Afa. 2:13; Kul. 1:20; 1 Yḥ. 4:4 \x*   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 17
\s1 Taẓaǧit n Yasuɛ am Ukehhan Ameqqran  
\m
\v 1 Tuɣa Yasuɛ issawař s man aya uca issgeɛɛed tiṭṭawin nnes ɣar ujenna, inna: “\add A\add* Baba, aqa tasaɛɛet tiweḍ-dd. Suɛřa Mmic, ḥima uřa d Mmic ad Cek issuɛřa, \x ◘ \xo 17:1 \xt Yḥ. 12:23; 13:32. \x*  
\v 2 ařami d as tewcid ṣṣulṭa x marra ddat, ḥima xenni Netta ad iwc Tudart ittduman i kuř ijjen i d as tewcid. \x ◘ \xo 17:2 \xt Izhd. 8:7; Mt. 11:27; 28:18; Lk. 10:22; Yḥ. 3:35; 5:27; 1 Kur. 15:25; Fil. 2:10; Ɛbr. 2:8. \x*  
\v 3 D tanita d Tudart ittduman, aqa nitni ad Cek ssnen, maɣar Cek weḥḥdek d AREBBI d tidett, d Yasuɛ Lmasiḥ wenni dd-tessekked. \x ◘ \xo 17:3 \xt Ica. 53:11; Irm. 9:22\x*  
\v 4 Necc ssuɛřiɣ Cek x temmurt. Necc kemmřeɣ řxedmet i d ayi tewcid ḥima ad tt ggeɣ. \x ◘ \xo 17:4 \xt Yḥ. 4:34; 13:32; 14:13; 19:30. \x*  
\v 5 Řexxu, sɛuǧi ayi, \add a\add* Baba, ɣar Ixef nnec s uɛuǧi i tuɣa ɣari qbeř ma ad tiři ddunect. \x ◘ \xo 17:5 \xt Yḥ. 1:1, 2; 10:30; 14:9. \x*   
\m
\v 6 Secneɣ Isem nnec i iwdan inni d ayi tewcid zi ddunect. Nitni tuɣa aten nnec, tewcid ten i Necc, aqa ṭṭfen deg Wawař nnec.  
\v 7 Řexxu ssneɣ belli marra min d ayi tewcid, aqa-t zzayek dd-yusa.  
\v 8 Minzi Necc wciɣ asen awařen i d ayi tewcid uca nitni qebřen zzaysen, ssnen s tidett belli Necc ffɣeɣ-dd zzayek, umnen aqa Cek tessekked ayi-dd. \x ◘ \xo 17:8 \xt Yḥ. 16:27. \x*  
\v 9 Necc ttareɣ di ṭṭweɛ nsen, war ttᵉttareɣ di ṭṭweɛ n ddunect, maca di ṭṭweɛ n yinni d ayi tewcid, minzi aqa aten nnec.  
\v 10 Marra min iǧan inu aqa-t nnec u min iǧan nnec aqa-t inu, u Necc ttwassɛuǧeɣ daysen. \x ◘ \xo 17:10 \xt Yḥ. 16:15. \x*   
\m
\v 11 Zi řexxu Necc war ǧiɣ ɛad di ddunect, maca nitni aqa aten di ddunect, uca Necc ad ɣarek dd-aseɣ. \add A\add* Baba iqeddsen, ḥḍa ten deg Yisem nnec, \add Isem\add* nni d ayi tewcid, ḥima nitni ad iřin d ijjen am Neccin.  
\v 12 Řami d ayi tuɣa akidsen, ḥḍiɣ ten deg Yisem nnec. Necc ɛesseɣ x yinni d ayi tewcid. Uřa d ijj zzaysen war ittwahellek, mɣir mmis n tehliket, ḥima ad ittwakemmeř \add min yuran\add* di Tira \add Iqeddsen\add*. \x ◘ \xo 17:12 \xt Ica. 8:18; Yḥ. 6:39; 10:28; 18:9; Ɛbr. 2:13. \x*   
\m
\v 13 Maca řexxu ad ɣarek dd-aseɣ u ssawařeɣ x man aya di ddunect, ḥima ad tiři řefraḥet inu tekmeř daysen.  
\v 14 Wciɣ asen awař nnec uca ddunect tuɣa tcarreh i-ten, minzi war ǧin ca zi ddunect, am Necc war ǧiɣ ca zi ddunect. \x ◘ \xo 17:14 \xt Yḥ. 15:19. \x*  
\v 15 Necc war ttareɣ ḥima ad ten teksid zi ddunect, maca ḥima ad ten teḥḍid zeg umɛeffan.  
\v 16 Nitni war ǧin ca zi ddunect am Necc war ǧiɣ ca zi ddunect.  
\v 17 \add A\add* Baba, sqeddes i-ten di tidett, awař nnec d tidett. \x ◘ \xo 17:17 \xt Izhd. 119:142; Yḥ. 8:4. \x*  
\v 18 Am mammec i d ayi dd-tessekked ɣar ddunect, \add ammu i\add* ten ssekkeɣ ɛawed ɣar ddunect. \x ◘ \xo 17:18 \xt Yḥ. 20:21. \x*  
\v 19 Ssqeddaseɣ Ixef inu di ṭṭweɛ nsen, ḥima ad ttwaqeddsen uřa d nitni di tidett. \x ◘ \xo 17:19 \xt 1 Kur. 1:2,30; 1 Ts. 4:7. \x*   
\m
\v 20 War ttareɣ di ṭṭweɛ n yina waha, maca ɛawed di ṭṭweɛ n yinni dayi yumnen s wawař nsen.  
\v 21 ḥima ad iřin marra d ijjen, \add a\add* Baba, am Cek dayi u Necc dayek, ḥima uřa d nitni ad iřin d ijjen dayneɣ, ḥima ad tamen ddunect belli aqa d Cek i d ayi dd-issekken. \x ◘ \xo 17:21 \xt Yḥ. 10:38; 14:11; Gal. 3:28. \x*  
\v 22 Necc wciɣ asen aɛuǧi i d ayi tewcid, ḥima ad iřin d ijjen am mammec Neccin neǧa d Ijjen.  
\v 23 Necc daysen, Cek dayi, ḥima ad iřin ttwakemmřen ɣar ijjen, ḥima ad tessen ddunect aqa Cek tessekked ayi-dd u texsed ten am mammec i d ayi texsed.   
\m
\v 24 \add A\add* Baba, xseɣ i yinni d ayi tewcid ad iřin akidi mani ma ǧiɣ Necc, uca ad ẓaren aɛuǧi inu i d ayi tewcid, minzi Cek texsed ayi qbeř ma ad tᵉttwagg ddunect. \x ◘ \xo 17:24 \xt Yḥ. 12:26; 14:3. \x*  
\v 25 \add A\add* Baba inu iseggden, aqa ddunect war Cek tessin, maca Necc aqa ssneɣ Cek u ina ssnen aqa Cek tessekked ayi-dd. \x ◘ \xo 17:25 \xt Yḥ. 15:21; 16:3, 27; 17:8. \x*  
\v 26 Necc ssecneɣ asen Isem nnec u ad t ssecneɣ, ḥima tayri i zi tuɣa d ayi tᵉttexsed ad tiři daysen u Necc daysen.”   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 18
\s1 Uḍuf n Yasuɛ  
\m
\v 1 Awarni řami inna Yasuɛ aya, iffeɣ ak-d imeḥḍaren nnes, ẓwan x yeɣzar n Qidrun. Tuɣa din ijj n weḥwic, yudef ɣares ak-d imeḥḍaren nnes. \x ◘ \xo 18:1 \xt [Mt. 26:47-56; Mk. 14:43-50; Lk. 22:47-53] — 2 Ṣm. 15:23; Mt. 26:36; Mk. 14:32; Lk. 22:39. \x*  
\v 2 Maca uřa d Yahuda, aɣeddar, issen amcan nni ɛawed, minzi Yasuɛ tuɣa issmuna dayes aṭṭas ak-d imeḥḍaren nnes.  
\v 3 Yiwi-dd Yahuda akides ict n terbiɛt n řɛeskar uřa d iɛessasen zeg wudem n imeqqranen n ikehhanen d Ifarisiyyen, uca yusa-dd diha s iṣefḍawen d řeqnadeř d řesnaḥ. \x ◘ \xo 18:3 \xt Mt. 26:47; Mk. 14:43; Lk. 22:47. \x*   
\m
\v 4 Yasuɛ, wenni issen marra min d as ɣa imsaren, iffeɣ-dd \add ɣarsen\add*, inna asen: “Min xef tarezzum?”  
\v 5 Arrin-dd xas: “Yasuɛ Nnaṣiri!” Yasuɛ inna asen: “D NECC!” Tuɣa Yahuda, aɣeddar, ibedd ɛawed akidsen.  
\v 6 Řami d asen inna Yasuɛ: “D Necc!”, dewřen nitni ɣar ḍeffar uca wḍan ɣar temmurt.   
\m
\v 7 Isseqsa ten Yasuɛ ɛawed: “Min xef tarezzum?” Nnan: “Yasuɛ Nnaṣiri!”  
\v 8 Yasuɛ yarra-dd: “Aqa nniɣ awem, aqa d Necc. Mařa tarezzum xafi, jjem ina ad raḥen!”,  
\v 9 ḥima ad ittwakemmeř wawař i tuɣa inna: “Inni d ayi tewcid, war zzaysen weddareɣ uřa d ijj.” \x ◘ \xo 18:9 \xt Yḥ. 6:39; 10:28; 17:12. \x*   
\m
\v 10 Cimɛun Buṭrus wenni tuɣa ɣares ssif, ijbed i-t-i-dd, iwta zzayes amsexxar n arrays n ikehhanen, iqess as amezzuɣ nnes afusi. Tuɣa amsexxar \add nni\add* qqaren as Malxis. \x ◘ \xo 18:10 \xt Mt. 26:51; Mk. 14:47; Lk. 22:50. \x*  
\v 11 \add Xas uca\add* inna Yasuɛ i Buṭrus: “Arr ssif ɣar weɣřaf nnes, řkas nni d ayi iwca Baba, ma war t sesseɣ?” \x ◘ \xo 18:11 \xt Mt. 20:22; 26:39. \x*   
\b  
\m  
\s1 Yasuɛ zzat i Ḥannan, azeǧif n ikehhanen  
\m
\v 12 Tarbiɛt n řɛeskar d imeqqranen x wařef \add n iɛeskariyyen\add* uřa d iɛessasen n Wudayen ṭṭfen Yasuɛ, carfen t. \x ◘ \xo 18:12 \xt [Mt. 26:57, 58; Mk. 14:53, 54; Lk. 22:54]\x*  
\v 13 Nedhen t amezwaru ɣar Ḥannan, minzi netta d aḍeggʷař n Qayafa, wenni tuɣa d arrays n ikehhanen deg useggʷas nni. \x ◘ \xo 18:13 \xt Mt. 26:57; Mk. 14:53; Lk. 3:2; 22:54. \x*  
\v 14 Qayafa d netta tuɣa iweṣṣa i Wudayen, aqa ḥsen ad immet ijj n Bnadem di ṭṭweɛ n řgens. \x ◘ \xo 18:14 \xt Yḥ. 11:50. \x*   
\b  
\m  
\s1 Ankar n Buṭrus  
\m
\v 15 Cimɛun Buṭrus iḍfar Yasuɛ ak-d ijjen zeg imeḥḍaren inneɣni. Ameḥḍar nni tuɣa ittwassnen ɣar arrays n ikehhanen uca yudef ak-d Yasuɛ ɣar řemraḥ n taddart \add n arrays n ikehhanen\add*. \x ◘ \xo 18:15 \xt [Mt. 26:69-70; Mk. 14:66-68; Lk. 22:55-57] — Mt. 26:58; Mk. 14:54; Lk. 22:54. \x*  
\v 16 Cimɛun ibedd-dd barra ɣar tewwart. Iffeɣ-dd umeḥḍar i tuɣa ittwassnen ɣar arrays n ikehhanen, issiweř ak-d tɛessast tenni iḥeṭṭan tawwart uca issidef-dd Cimɛun ɣar daxeř.  
\v 17 Tabřiɣt tenni iḥeṭṭan tawwart, tenna i Cimɛun: “Ma war teǧid uřa d cek zeg imeḥḍaren n bnadem-a?” Inna: “Lla!”  
\v 18 Tuɣa imsexxaren d iɛessasen bedden \add din\add*, ssarɣen timessi s řefḥem, minzi tuɣa tesmeḍ, uca tuɣa ttweqqaḥen. Uřa d Cimɛun ibedd akidsen, ittweqqaḥ. \x ◘ \xo 18:18 \xt Mt. 26:69; Mk. 14:67; Lk. 22:55. \x*   
\b  
\m  
\s1 Iseqsiten n arrays n ikehhanen i Yasuɛ  
\m
\v 19 Isseqsa arrays n ikehhanen Yasuɛ x imeḥḍaren nnes u x tɣuri nnes. \x ◘ \xo 18:19 \xt [Mt. 26:59-66; Mk. 14:55-64; Lk. 22:66-71]\x*  
\v 20 Yarra-dd xas Yasuɛ: “Necc tuɣa ssawařeɣ i řgens s bṭayṭay, ssɣareɣ řebda di temzida u di Zzawect Tameqqrant mani ttmunan Wudayen řebda. Di tnuffra war ssiwřeɣ uřa d ict n řḥajjet. \x ◘ \xo 18:20 \xt Yḥ. 7:26. \x*  
\v 21 Mayemmi d ayi tesseqsid? Seqsa inni isřan min d asen nniɣ. Xzar, nitni ssnen min nniɣ!”  
\v 22 Řami inna ammu, xenni ijjen zeg iɛessasen i tuɣa din ibedden, iwta Yasuɛ x umeggiz nnes, inna as: “Ma ammu i dd ɣa tarred x arrays n ikehhanen?” \x ◘ \xo 18:22 \xt Irm. 20:2; Řex. 23:2. \x*  
\v 23 Yarra-dd xas Yasuɛ, inna: “Mařa ssiwřeɣ min war iḥřin, ched x min war iḥřin, maca mařa ssiwřeɣ mliḥ, mayemmi d ayi teccated \add xenni\add*?”  
\v 24 \add Xas uca\add* Ḥannan issekk i-t ittwacarf ɣar Qayafa, arrays n ikehhanen. \x ◘ \xo 18:24 \xt Mt. 26:57; Mk. 14:53; Lk. 22:54. \x*   
\b  
\m  
\s1 Cimɛun Buṭrus inkar ɛawed aqa netta issen Yasuɛ  
\m
\v 25 Tuɣa Cimɛun Buṭrus ibedd dinni ittweqqaḥ. Nnan as: “Ma war teǧid uřa d cek zeg imeḥḍaren nnes?” Netta inkar, inna: “War ǧiɣ ca d necc!” \x ◘ \xo 18:25 \xt [Mt. 26:71-75; Mk. 14:69-72; Lk. 22:58-62] — Mt. 26:71; Mk. 14:69; Lk. 22:58. \x*  
\v 26 Ijjen zeg imsexxaren n arrays n ikehhanen i tuɣa itteɛnan i wenni umi iqess Cimɛun amezzuɣ, inna: “Ma war cek ẓriɣ akides deg weḥwic?”  
\v 27 Řexdenni inkar Cimɛun ɛawed uca deɣya issquqeɛ uyaẓiḍ. \x ◘ \xo 18:27 \xt Yḥ. 13:38. \x*   
\b  
\m  
\s1 Yasuɛ zzat i Pilaṭus  
\m
\v 28 Xenni iwyen-dd Yasuɛ zi Qayafa ɣar taddart n ccreɛ, \add umi qqaren ‘Prituriyum’\add*. Tuɣa d zic di ṣṣbeḥ. Nitni war udifen ca ɣar taddart n ccreɛ, ḥima war ttwessixen qbeř ma i ɣa ccen \add Tɣarṣt n\add* Useɛdu. \x ◘ \xo 18:28 \xt [Mt. 27:1-2, 11-31; Mk. 15:1-20; Lk. 23:1-25] — Mt. 27:1; Mk. 15:1; Lk. 22:66; 23:1. \x*  
\v 29 \add S uyenni\add* iffeɣ-dd ɣarsen Pilaṭus, inna asen: “Man acetci i ɣarwem x Weryaz-a?”  
\v 30 Arrin-dd, nnan as: “Mařa Wanita war tuɣi d mmis n řmuɛṣiyyet, ad tiři war d ac t-i-dd-nettiwi.”  
\v 31 Inna asen Pilaṭus: “\add Xenni\add* awyem t-i-dd kenniw, tḥekmem xas ɛlaḥsab Ccariɛa nwem.” Xenni nnan as Wudayen: “War ɣarneɣ bu ttesriḥ maḥend ad neneɣ uřa d ijj!”,  
\v 32 ḥima ad ittwakemmeř wawař n Yasuɛ i tuɣa iqqar, am tuɣa isscanen i man řmewt i ɣa immet. \x ◘ \xo 18:32 \xt Mt. 20:19; Yḥ. 12:32. \x*   
\m
\v 33 Xenni yudef-dd Pilaṭus ɛawed ɣar taddart n Ccraɛ, \add umi qqaren Prituriyum\add*, iřaɣa-dd x Yasuɛ, inna as: “Ma Cek d Ajeǧid n Wudayen?” \x ◘ \xo 18:33 \xt Mt. 27:11; Mk. 15:2; Lk. 23:3. \x*  
\v 34 Yarra-dd xas Yasuɛ: “Ma teqqared aya zi ɣarek niɣ tuɣa inneɣni qqaren ac t xafi?”  
\v 35 Inna as Pilaṭus: “Ma necc d Uday? Aqa řgens nnec d imeqqranen n ikehhanen iwyen-dd Cek ɣari. Min tuɣa teggid?”  
\v 36 Yarra-dd xas Yasuɛ: “Tageldit inu war teǧi ca zi ddunect-a. Mařa teǧa Tgeldit inu zi ddunect-a, ad yiři aqa imsexxaren inu ad mmenɣen, ḥima war ttwasellameɣ i Wudayen, maca řexxu Tageldit inu war teǧi ca ssanita.” \x ◘ \xo 18:36 \xt Yḥ. 6:15; 1 Tim. 6:13. \x*  
\v 37 Inna as Pilaṭus: “Xenni aqa Cek d Ajeǧid nican!” Yarra-dd Yasuɛ: “Cek teqqared, aqa Necc d Ajeǧid. I man aya i dd-xeřqeɣ u i uya i dd-usiɣ ɣar ddunect, ḥima ad cehdeɣ i tidett. Marra wenni iǧan zi tidett, ad iseř i tmijja inu.”   
\m
\v 38 Inna as Pilaṭus: “Umi qqaren d tidett?” Řami inna ammu, iffeɣ-dd ɛawed ɣar Wudayen, inna asen: “War dayes ufiɣ uřa d ijj n uxeṭṭu. \x ◘ \xo 18:38 \xt Mt. 27:24; Lk. 23:4. \x*  
\v 39 Maca aqa tennumem ad awem sarrḥeɣ ijj n bnadem di \add Řɛid n Tɣarṣt n\add* Useɛdu. Ma texsem xenni ad awem sarrḥeɣ Bnadem-a, Ajeǧid n Wudayen?” \x ◘ \xo 18:39 \xt Mt. 27:15; Mk. 15:6; Lk. 23:17. \x*  
\v 40 Sɣuyyen ɛawed marra, nnan: “War iǧi ca Wanita, ḥaca Bar-Abbas!” Tuɣa Bar-Abbas d aqṭaṭɛiy. \x ◘ \xo 18:40 \xt Mt. 27:16; Mk. 15:7; Lk. 23:19; Řex. 3:1. \x*   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 19
\s1 Řḥukm x Yasuɛ  
\m
\v 1 Xenni \add ijja\add* Pilaṭus ad hettken Yasuɛ s urekkuḍ. \x ◘ \xo 19:1 \xt Mt. 27:26; Mk. 15:15. \x*  
\v 2 Awarni řami muden iɛeskariyyen ijj n ttaj s isennanen, ssarsen as tt x uzeǧif nnes uca yarḍen as ijj n useřham d arjuwani,  
\v 3 nnan: “Sřam xak, \add a\add* Ajeǧid n Wudayen!”, uca wtin t x igemmizen nnes.   
\m
\v 4 Iffeɣ-dd ɛawed Pilaṭus, inna asen: “Ad awem t-i-dd-ssuffɣeɣ, ḥima ad tessnem belli necc war dayes ufiɣ ssibbet i ucetci, uřa d ict.”  
\v 5 \add Xenni\add* iffeɣ-dd Yasuɛ s ttaj n isennanen d ujeǧab ajurwani. Inna asen Pilaṭus: “Xzarem, Bnadem!”   
\m
\v 6 Řami t ẓrin imeqqranen n ikehhanen d iɛessasen, sɣuyen, nnan: “Ṣellb i-t, ṣellb i-t” Inna asen Pilaṭus: “Awyem t-i-dd kenniw, ṣellbem t, minzi necc war dayes ufiɣ uřa d ijj n řɛib.”  
\v 7 Arrin-dd xas Wudayen: “Ɣarneɣ Ccariɛa, u ɛlaḥsab Ccariɛa nneɣ ittxeṣṣa ad immet, minzi Netta ittarra Ixef nnes d Mmis n AREBBI.” \x ◘ \xo 19:7 \xt Lawi 24:16; Yḥ. 5:18; 10:3. \x*   
\m
\v 8 Řami isřa Pilaṭus awař-a, yarni di tiggʷudi.  
\v 9 Yudef ɛawed ɣar taddart n ccreɛ, inna i Yasuɛ: “Manis Cek?” Maca Yasuɛ war xas dd-yarri ca.  
\v 10 Inna as Pilaṭus: “Ma war \add texsed ad\add* kidi tessiwiřed? Ma war tessined ca aqa ɣari ṣṣulṭa ḥima ad ac ssarrḥeɣ u ɣari ṣṣulṭa ḥima ad Cek ṣellbeɣ?”  
\v 11 Yarra-dd xas Yasuɛ: “War ɣarek tᵉttiři bu ṣṣulṭa xafi, mařa war d ac dd-temmewc zi sennej. S uya, wenni d ayi isellmen i cek, aqa xas ddenb imɣar zeg wenni \add i iǧan\add* xak.”  
\v 12 Zi řexdenni tuɣa Pilaṭus yarezzu ad as isarreḥ, maca Udayen sɣuyen, nnan: “Mařa tsarrḥed i Weryaz-a, war teǧid ca d ameddukkeř n qayṣar. Kuř ijjen wenni ittarran ixef nnes d ajeǧid, ittɛekkas qayṣar.” \x ◘ \xo 19:12 \xt Řex. 17:7. \x*   
\m
\v 13 Řami isřa Pilaṭus i wawař-a, issuffeɣ Yasuɛ, iqqim x řkursi n ccreɛ deg wemcan umi qqaren ‘Azzay n luṣa’, maca qqaren as s Tɛibranit ‘Gpipta’. \f ◼ \fr 19:13 \ft \+fk Tiɛibranit\ft  - ad taɣ ‘Tiɛibranit’ ijj n isem nni issmunen deg ixef nnes am iřes n Tɛibranit, am ires n Tramit.\f*  
\v 14 Tuɣa d \add ass n\add* Usewjed i \add Tɣarṣt n\add* Useɛdu. Tuɣa ɛřaḥař d tsaɛɛet wiss setta \add ɣar tuffut\add*, řami inna i Wudayen: “Xzarem, Ajeǧid nwem!”  
\v 15 Maca nitni sɣuyen: “Ksi t, ksi t, ṣellb i-t!” Inna asen Pilaṭus: “Ma ad ṣellbeɣ \add xenni\add* Ajeǧid nwem?” Arrin-dd xas imeqqranen n ikehhanen: “War ɣarneɣ bu ujeǧid mɣir qayṣar!” \x ◘ \xo 19:15 \xt Amz. 49:10. \x*  
\v 16 Xenni isellem asen t ḥima ad t ṣellben. Uca nitni ksin Yasuɛ, iwyen t ssenni. \x ◘ \xo 19:16 \xt Mt. 27:26; Mk. 15:22; Lk. 23:24, 25. \x*   
\b  
\m  
\s1 Yasuɛ yarebbu ṣṣalib  
\m
\v 17 Yarbu ṣṣalib nnes ɣar wemcan umi qqaren ‘Taceqquft’, maca s Tɛibranit qqaren as ‘Juljuta’. \f ◼ \fr 19:17 \ft \+fk Tiɛibranit\ft  - ad taɣ ‘Tiɛibranit’ ijj n isem nni issmunen deg ixef nnes am iřes n Tɛibranit, am ires n Tramit.\f*  \x ◘ \xo 19:17 \xt [Mt. 27:32-44; Mk. 15:21-32; Lk. 23:26-39] — Mt. 27:31, 33; Mk. 15:22; Lk. 23:26, 33. \x*  
\v 18 Ṣellben t dinni, uca ṣellben akides tnayen nneɣni, ijjen ɣar ijj n uɣezdis u wenneɣni ɣar uɣezdis nneɣni, u Yasuɛ di řwesṭ.  
\v 19 Yura Pilaṭus ɛawed deg ict teřwiḥt, issars i-tt x ṣṣalib. Ammu i ittwari \add dayes\add*: ‘Wanita d Yasuɛ Nnaṣiri, Ajeǧid n Wudayen’. \x ◘ \xo 19:19 \xt Mt. 27:37; Mk. 15:26; Lk. 23:38. \x*  
\v 20 Tira-ya ɣrin tent aṭṭas n Wudayen, minzi amcan mani tuɣa ṣellben Yasuɛ yudes-dd i tendint. \add Tira-ya\add* ttwarint s Tɛibranit d Tlatinit d Tyunanit.  
\v 21 Nnan imeqqranen n ikehhanen i Pilaṭus: “War ttari ca: ‘Ajeǧid n Wudayen’, maca aqa inna: ‘Necc d Ajeǧid n Wudayen!’”  
\v 22 Yarra-dd Pilaṭus: “Min uriɣ, aqa uriɣ t.”   
\m
\v 23 Řami ṣellben iɛeskariyyen Yasuɛ, ksin arruḍ nnes, bḍan t x arebɛa n tseqqar, i kuř aɛeskari ict n tesɣart. Maca tcamir nnes tuɣa břa taxeyyaḍt, tᵉttwaxeyyeḍ qaɛ zi sennej. \x ◘ \xo 19:23 \xt Mt. 27:35; Mk. 15:24; Lk. 23:34. \x*  
\v 24 Nnan i wayawya: “War t nettcarrig ca, ad xas negg akeccuḍ, ad nẓar wi t ɣa yawyen!” Ammu i ittwakemmeř awař n Tira \add Iqeddsen\add* i iqqaren: “Bḍan arruḍ inu jar asen u x tcamir inu ggin akeccuḍ.” Man aya i iggin iɛeskariyyen. \x ◘ \xo 19:24 \xt Izhd. 22:19. \x*   
\m
\v 25 Ɣar ṣṣalib n Yasuɛ tbedd yemmas, d učmas n yemmas, d Maryam \add tamɣart\add* n Kliyupas, d Maryam n Majdala. \x ◘ \xo 19:25 \xt Mt. 27:55; Mk. 15:40; Lk. 23:49. \x*  
\v 26 Řami iẓra Yasuɛ yemmas d umeḥḍar wenni tuɣa ittexs, ibedd din, inna i yemmas: “\add A\add* tamɣart, xzar, mmim!”  
\v 27 Řexdenni inna i umeḥḍar nni: “Aqa-c yemmac!” Zi tsaɛɛet nni iksi tt umeḥḍar \add ɣar taddart nnes\add*.   
\b  
\m  
\s1 Řmewt n Yasuɛ x ṣṣalib  
\m
\v 28 Awarni man aya issen Yasuɛ aqa kuřci ittwakemmeř, řexdenni inna, ḥima ad yiři \add min yuran\add* di Tira \add Iqeddsen\add*: “Necc ffudeɣ!” \x ◘ \xo 19:28 \xt [Mt. 27:45-56; Mk. 15:33-41; Lk. 23:44-49] — Izhd. 22:15; 69:21. \x*  
\v 29 Ittwamars din ijj n uɣarraf iccur s řxeǧ. Ssɣeḍṣen ict n spunxa \add n hisub\add* s řxeǧ uca ggin tt x \add ijj n uɣanim n\add* tɛelǧet, ssiwḍen as tt ɣar uqemmum nnes.  
\v 30 Řami iqqas Yasuɛ řxeǧ, inna: “Aqa ittwakemmeř!” Uca issaḍar azeǧif nnes, isellem Arruḥ nnes.   
\m
\v 31 Umi tuɣa \add ass n\add* Usewjed \add n Tɣarṣt n Useɛdu\add*, nnan Wudayen: “War iɛeddeř ad qqiment arrimat \add nsen\add* x ṣṣalib di ssebt, minzi ssebt yudes-dd!”, minzi ass nni n ssebt tuɣa d ass ameqqran. S uya ttaren Wudayen zi Pilaṭus, ḥima ad arẓen iḍaren n yinni ittwaṣellben, ad ten ssiggʷejen ssenni.  
\v 32 \add Xenni\add* usin-dd iɛeskariyyen, arẓin iḍaren n umezwaru u n wenneɣni i tuɣa ittwaṣelleb akides.  
\v 33 Maca řami dd-usin ɣar Yasuɛ, war arẓin ca iḍaren nnes umi ẓrin aqa immut.  
\v 34 Maca ijjen zeg iɛeskariyyen issnuqqeb i-t s ict n lansa deg uɣezdis nnes uca ffɣen-dd idammen d waman deɣya.  
\v 35 Wenni iẓrin man aya, tuɣa iched u cchadet nnes d tidett uca netta issen, aqa inna tidett, ḥima ad tamnem uřa d kenniw.  
\v 36 Timesřayin-a msarent, ḥima ad ttwakemmřent Tira \add Iqeddsen\add* i iqqaren: “War zzayes ittareẓẓi yiɣes.” \x ◘ \xo 19:36 \xt Uf. 12:46; Řxř. 9:12; Izhd. 34:22. \x*  
\v 37 Uca ijj n wawař nneɣni zi Tira \add Iqeddsen\add* iqqar: “Nitni ad ẓaren Wenni t issnuqqben.” \x ◘ \xo 19:37 \xt Zak. 12:10. \x*   
\b  
\m  
\s1 Anḍeř n Yasuɛ  
\m
\v 38 Awarni man aya imsar aqa Yusuf zi Ramta, wenni tuɣa d ijj n umeḥḍar n Yasuɛ maca s tnuffra zi tiggʷudi zeg Wudayen, ittar as i Pilaṭus ttesriḥ ḥima ad iksi arrimet n Yasuɛ, uca Pilaṭus isarreḥ as. Xenni yusa-dd, iksi arrimet n Yasuɛ. \x ◘ \xo 19:38 \xt [Mt. 27:57-61; Mk. 15:42-47; Lk. 23:50-56] — Mt. 27:57; Mk. 15:42; Lk. 23:50; Yḥ. 12:42. \x*  
\v 39 Yusa-dd ɛawed Nikudimus wenni tuɣa dd-yusin qbeř ɣar Yasuɛ s ǧiřet, yiwi-dd akides axeǧeḍ n řefwaḥet n mirru d wecfir ɛřaḥař mya litru. \f ◼ \fr 19:39 \ft \+fk qbeř\ft  - xzar Yḥ. 3:1.\f*  \x ◘ \xo 19:39 \xt Yḥ. 3:1; 7:50. \x*  
\v 40 Ksin nitni arrimet n Yasuɛ, řeḥḥfen tt di řecfun n řeqṭen \add azdad\add* ak-d řeɛṭur, am mammec nnumen tteggen tt Wudayen i wenḍeř.  
\v 41 Tuɣa din ijj n weḥwic deg wemcan mani ṣellben Yasuɛ, uca deg weḥwic ijj n wenḍeř n jdid, ɛemmarṣ war dayes ssarsen uřa d ijj.  
\v 42 Ssarsen Yasuɛ din, minzi tuɣa yiweḍ-dd ssebt u minzi anḍeř \add nni\add* tuɣa yudes.   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 20
\s1 Anḍeř n Yasuɛ ixwa  
\m
\v 1 Deg \add wass\add* amezwaru n ssimana tusa-dd Maryam n Majdala di ṣṣbeḥ zic ɣar wenḍeř, tuɣa ɛad d taǧest. Teẓra taṣḍart aqa temmeksi x wenḍeř. \x ◘ \xo 20:1 \xt [Mt. 28:1-10; Mk. 16:1-8; Lk. 24:1-12] — Mt. 28:1; Mk. 16:1; Lk. 24:1. \x*  
\v 2 Tuzzeř-dd, tusa-dd ɣar Cimɛun Buṭrus u ɣar umeḥḍar nneɣni wenni umi tuɣa ittexs Yasuɛ, tenna asen: “Ksin Siditneɣ zeg wenḍeř, war ssineɣ mani t ggin.” \x ◘ \xo 20:2 \xt Yḥ. 13:23; 21:7, 20. \x*   
\m
\v 3 Iffeɣ-dd Cimɛun d umeḥḍar nneɣni uca usin-dd ɣar wenḍeř. \x ◘ \xo 20:3 \xt Lk. 24:12. \x*  
\v 4 Nitni uzzřen s tnayen idsen, \add maca\add* ameḥḍar \add nneɣni\add* izwar i Cimɛun uca yiweḍ d amezwaru ɣar wenḍeř.  
\v 5 Ixzar, iẓra řecfun n řeqṭen \add azdad\add* mmarsen \add din\add*, maca war yudif ca. \x ◘ \xo 20:5 \xt Yḥ. 19:40. \x*  
\v 6 Iḍfar i-t Cimɛun, yudef ɣar wenḍeř, iẓra \add ɛawed\add* řecfun n řeqṭen \add azdad\add* mmarsen \add din\add*.  
\v 7 Amendiř nni tuɣa x uzeǧif nnes, war immars ca ak-d řecfun n řeqṭen \add azdad\add*, maca tuɣa iḍfeṣ, ittwagg deg wemcan weḥḥdes. \x ◘ \xo 20:7 \xt Yḥ. 11:44. \x*  
\v 8 Řexdenni yudef-dd uřa d ameḥḍar nneɣni nni dd-yusin d amezwaru ɣar wenḍeř, iẓra uca yumen.  
\v 9 Minzi nitni tuɣa ɛad war ssinen Tira \add Iqeddsen\add*, belli ittxeṣṣa as ad ikkar jar imettinen. \x ◘ \xo 20:9 \xt Izhd. 16:10; Řex. 2:25,31; 13:35. \x*   
\m
\v 10 Xenni dewřen imeḥḍaren nni ɣar taddart nsen.   
\b  
\m  
\s1 Aḍhar n Yasuɛ i Maryam zi Majdala  
\m
\v 11 Maryam teqqim tbedd ɣar wenḍeř barra, tᵉttru. Řami tuɣa tᵉttru, tesweḍ deg wenḍeř, \x ◘ \xo 20:11 \xt [Mk. 16:9-11] — Mt. 28:1; Mk. 16:5; Lk. 24:4. \x*  
\v 12 teẓra tnayen n lmalakat s warruḍ d acemřař, qqiment mani tuɣa temmars arrimet n Yasuɛ, ijjen ɣar tsummtin nnes n uzeǧif, ijjen ɣar iḍaren nnes.  
\v 13 Nnan as: “\add A\add* tamɣart, mayemmi tᵉttrud?” Tenna asen: “Maɣar kksen Sidi inu, war ssineɣ mani t ssarsen.”  
\v 14 Umi tenna aya, tenneqřeb ɣar ḍeffar, teẓra Yasuɛ ibedd, maca war tessin ca aqa-t d Yasuɛ. \x ◘ \xo 20:14 \xt Mt. 28:9; Mk. 16:9. \x*  
\v 15 Yasuɛ inna as: “\add A\add* tamɣart, mayemmi tᵉttrud? Min xef tarezzud?” Tᵉttɣiř as Netta d bab n teḥwict, tenna as: “\add A\add* sidi mařa cek i-t iksin, ini ayi mani t tessarsed, \add xenni\add* ad t ksiɣ.”  
\v 16 Yasuɛ inna as: “\add A\add* Maryam!” Nettat tenneqřeb, tenna as s Tɛibranit: “\add A\add* Rabbuli!”, ixs ad yini: ‘\add A\add* Amseɣɣar inu’.  
\v 17 Yasuɛ inna as: “War d ayi tᵉttḥidi ca, aqa Necc ɛad war geɛɛdeɣ ca ɣar Baba, maca ruḥ ɣar aytma, ini asen: ‘Necc aqa ad geɛɛdeɣ ɣar Baba d Babatwem, ɣar AREBBI inu d AREBBI nwem.’” \x ◘ \xo 20:17 \xt Izhd. 22:23; Mt. 28:10; Yḥ. 16:2; Ɛbr. 2:11. \x*  
\v 18 Teɛqeb-dd Maryam n Majdala txebbar imeḥḍaren belli nettat teẓra Siditneɣ u belli Netta inna as man aya. \x ◘ \xo 20:18 \xt Mt. 28:8; Mk. 16:10; Lk. 24:9. \x*   
\b  
\m  
\s1 Aḍhar n Yasuɛ i imeḥḍaren nnes  
\m
\v 19 Ɣar tmeddit n wass nni, netta d \add ass\add* amezwaru n ssimana, umi tuɣa tiwwura mani tuɣa \add qqimen\add* imeḥḍaren qqnent s tiggʷudi zeg Wudayen, yudef-dd Yasuɛ, ibedd di řwesṭ nsen, inna asen: “Sřam xawem.” \x ◘ \xo 20:19 \xt [Mt. 28:16-20; Mk. 16:14-18; Lk. 24:36-49] — Mk. 16:14; Lk. 24:36; 1 Kur. 15:5. \x*  
\v 20 Awarni řami inna aya, immeř asen ifassen nnes d uɣezdis nnes. Farḥen imeḥḍaren řami ẓrin Siditneɣ. \x ◘ \xo 20:20 \xt Yḥ. 16:22. \x*  
\v 21 Inna asen ɛawed Yasuɛ: “Sřam xawem, am mammec d ayi dd-issekk Baba, ad kenniw dd-ssekkeɣ uřa d Necc.” \x ◘ \xo 20:21 \xt Ica. 61:1; Mt. 28:18; Mk. 16:15; Lk. 4:18; Yḥ. 17:18. \x*  
\v 22 Awarni řami inna man aya, isuḍ daysen, inna asen: “Qebřem Arruḥ Iqeddsen.”  
\v 23 Wenni umi ɣa teɣfarem ddnub nnes, ad as ttwaɣfaren \add ddnub nnes\add*. Wenni umi d as i ɣa tᵉṭṭfem di ddnub nnes, ad as ttwaṭṭfen \add ddnub nnes\add*.” \x ◘ \xo 20:23 \xt Mt. 16:19; 18:18. \x*   
\b  
\m  
\s1 Yasuɛ isscen ixef nnes i Tuma  
\m
\v 24 Maca Tuma, ijjen zi tenɛac, wenni umi qqaren ‘Acniw’, war tuɣi ca akidsen řami dd-yusa Yasuɛ.  
\v 25 Nnan as imeḥḍaren: “Aqa neẓra Siditneɣ!” Maca netta inna asen: “Mařa war ẓriɣ řimařt n imesmiren deg ifassen nnes, ad ssarseɣ aḍaḍ inu deg wemcan n imesmiren uca ad ssarseɣ afus inu deg uɣezdis nnes, war ttimneɣ.”   
\m
\v 26 Awarni tmenya n wussan tuɣa imeḥḍaren \add nnes\add* ɛawed ɣar daxeř u Tuma tuɣa akidsen. Yudef-dd Yasuɛ, waxxa tiwwura tuɣa qqnent, uca ibedd-dd di řwesṭ nsen, inna: “Sřam xawem!”  
\v 27 Inna i Tuma: “Awi-dd aḍaḍ nnec uca xzar deg ifassen inu, sars afus nnec \add danita\add* u sidef i-t deg uɣezdis inu. War ttiři d akafriw, maca d řmumen.” \x ◘ \xo 20:27 \xt 1 Yḥ. 1:1. \x*  
\v 28 Yarra-dd Tuma, inna as: “A Sidi inu d AREBBI inu!”  
\v 29 Inna as Yasuɛ: “Umi teẓrid ayi řexxu, aqa tumned, \add a\add* Tuma! Sseɛd n yinni yumnen, waxxa nitni war \add d ayi\add* ẓrin.” \x ◘ \xo 20:29 \xt 1 Bṭ. 1:8. \x*   
\m
\v 30 Yasuɛ igga aṭṭas n řeɛřamat nneɣni qibač i imeḥḍaren nnes, tinni war yurint ca deg wedlis-a, \x ◘ \xo 20:30 \xt Yḥ. 21:25. \x*  
\v 31 maca tina urant ḥima ad tamnem belli Yasuɛ Netta d Lmasiḥ, Mmis n AREBBI, uca xmi ɣa tamnem, ad ɣarwem tiři Tudart s Yisem nnes.   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 21
\s1 Aḍhar n Yasuɛ ɣar řebḥar n Tibiriyas  
\m
\v 1 Awarni uya tuɣa Yasuɛ immeř ixef nnes ɛawed i imeḥḍaren nnes ɣar řebḥar n Tibiriyas, iḍhar-dd ammu.  
\v 2 Tuɣa \add din\add* jmiɛ Cimɛun Buṭrus d Tuma, wenni umi qqaren ‘Acniw’, d Natanayil, wenni tuɣa zi Qana di temmurt n Ljalil, d tarwa n Zabdi uřa d tnayen nneɣni zeg imeḥḍaren \add nnes\add*. \x ◘ \xo 21:2 \xt Mt. 4:21; Mk. 1:19; Yḥ. 1:46. \x*   
\m
\v 3 Inna asen Cimɛun Buṭrus: “Necc ad raḥeɣ ad gmareɣ \add iseřman\add*.” Nnan as: “Ad kik nraḥ uřa d neccin.” Ffɣen-dd uca nyin deɣya di tɣarrabut. Di ǧiřet nni war ṭṭifen walu.  
\v 4 Ɣar tuffut, ibedd-dd Yasuɛ x tma n řebḥar, maca imeḥḍaren war ssinen ca aqa d Yasuɛ.  
\v 5 Inna asen Yasuɛ: “\add A\add* iḥenjiren, ma ad taɣ ɣarwem ca n macca?” Arrin-dd xas “Lla!”  
\v 6 Inna asen: “Nḍarem tracca nwem ak-d uɣezdis afusi n tɣarrabut, ad tafem.” Xenni nḍaren \add tracca\add* uca war zemmaren ad tt-i-dd-jebden zi ssibbet n ubarru n iseřman i dayes ittwaṭṭfen. \x ◘ \xo 21:6 \xt Lk. 5:4, 6, 7. \x*   
\m
\v 7 Inna umeḥḍar wenni tuɣa ittexs Yasuɛ i Buṭrus: “Aqa Netta d Siditneɣ.” Řami isřa Cimɛun aqa Netta d Sidi, iṭṭef tcamir nnes minzi tuɣa d aɛaryan, inḍar ixef nnes di řebḥar ařami ɣa dd-iqarreb ɣar Yasuɛ. \x ◘ \xo 21:7 \xt Yḥ. 13:23; 20:2. \x*  
\v 8 Maca imeḥḍaren inneɣni usin-dd s tɣarrabut minzi war iggʷijen ca x řbarr mɣir mitayen n iɣaǧen, uca jebden-dd tracca ak-d iseřman. \f ◼ \fr 21:8 \ft \+fk mitayen n iɣaǧen\ft  - ixs ad yini ɛřaḥař 100 mitru.\f*   
\m
\v 9 Řami dd-ffɣen ɣar řbarr, ẓrin diha aqa ittwassewjed ijj n ufennic n řefḥem mixef mmarsen iseřman d weɣrum.  
\v 10 Inna asen Yasuɛ: “Awyem-dd zeg iseřman i tegmarem řexxu.” \x ◘ \xo 21:10 \xt Lk. 24:41. \x*  
\v 11 Cimɛun Buṭrus yuyur, ijbed tracca teccur s iseřman imeqqranen ɣar řbarr, aqa-tt dayes mya u-třata u-xemsin. Waxxa dayes s wanect uya \add aṭṭas\add*, war tcarreg ca tracca.  
\v 12 Inna asen Yasuɛ: “Araḥem-dd da, ad tariyyqem!” Uřa d ijj zeg imeḥḍaren war izɛim ad t isseqsa ‘Min teɛnid Cek?’, minzi ssnen aqa-t d Siditneɣ.  
\v 13 Řexdenni yusa-dd Yasuɛ, iksi aɣrum d iseřman, iwca asen.  
\v 14 Wanita d twařa wiss třata i dd-iḍhar Yasuɛ i imeḥḍaren nnes awarni řami dd-ittwassnekkar zi taddart n imettinen.   
\b  
\m  
\s1 Aseqsi n Yasuɛ i Buṭrus  
\m
\v 15 Awarni řami ariyyqen, inna Yasuɛ i Cimɛun Buṭrus: “\add A\add* Cimɛun, mmis n Yuna, ma tᵉttexsed ayi ktar zeg yina?” Inna as: “Wah, a Sidi, Cek tessned aqa necc ttexseɣ Cek.” Inna as: \bd “Arwes izmaren inu!”\bd*  
\v 16 Inna as ɛawed i twařa wiss tnayen: “\add A\add* Cimɛun, mmis n Yuna, ma tᵉttexsed ayi?” Inna as: “Wah \add a\add* Sidi, Cek tessned aqa necc ttexseɣ Cek.” Inna as: \bd “Arwes icarriyyen inu!”\bd*  
\v 17 Inna as i twařa wiss třata: “\add A\add* Cimɛun, mmis n Yuna, ma tᵉttexsed ayi?” Icḍen Buṭrus minzi inna as t twařa wiss třata: ‘Ma tᵉttexsed ayi?’, uca inna as: “\add A\add* Sidi, Cek tessned kuřci, tessned aqa necc ttexseɣ Cek.” Inna as Yasuɛ: \bd “Arwes tixsiwin inu!\bd* \x ◘ \xo 21:17 \xt Yḥ. 16:30. \x*  
\v 18 S tidett, s tidett, Necc ad ac iniɣ: Řami cek tuɣa d ameẓyan, tbeysed i yixef nnec, truḥed mani texsed, maca x minni i ɣa tewsared, ad tesswiẓẓḍed ifassen nnec uca wenneɣni ad cek ibyes uca ad cek yawi ɣar mani war tᵉttexsed.” \x ◘ \xo 21:18 \xt Yḥ. 13:36; Řex. 12:3; 2 Bṭ. 1:14. \x*  
\v 19 Inna ammu ḥima ad isscen i man řmewt i zi ɣa issɛuǧ AREBBI. Awarni řami \add d as\add* inna ammu, inna as: “Ḍfar ayi-dd!” \x ◘ \xo 21:19 \xt 2 Bṭ. 1:14. \x*   
\m
\v 20 Inneqřeb Cimɛun Buṭrus, iẓra ameḥḍar nni tuɣa ittexs Yasuɛ, iḍfar i-t, netta d wenni tuɣa yarra ixef nnes ad imeyyeř ɣar idmaren n Yasuɛ ɣar umensi i innan: “\add A\add* Sidi inu, wi Cek i ɣa iɣdaren?” \x ◘ \xo 21:20 \xt Yḥ. 13:23; 20:2; 21:7. \x*  
\v 21 Řami iẓra Buṭrus wa, inna i Yasuɛ: “\add A\add* Sidi, i wa, min d as ɣa imsaren?”  
\v 22 Inna as Yasuɛ: “Mařa xseɣ ad iqqim ař dd ɣa ɛeqbeɣ, min d ac iruḥen? Cek ḍfar ayi-dd!”  
\v 23 Uca iffeɣ-dd wawař-a jar wawmaten belli ameḥḍar nni war ittmetti ca, maca Yasuɛ war d as inni ca belli netta war ittmetti ca, maca: “Mařa xseɣ ad iqqim ař dd ɣa ɛeqbeɣ, min d ac iruḥen?”   
\b  
\m  
\s1 Taneggarut  
\m
\v 24 D wa d ameḥḍar i icehhden s man aya uca netta yura man aya, u neccin nessen aqa cchadet nnes d tidett. \x ◘ \xo 21:24 \xt Yḥ. 19:35. \x*  
\v 25 Aqa din ɛad aṭṭas n tmesřayin nneɣni i igga Yasuɛ. Mařa ttwarint ict awarni tenneɣnit, ittɣiř ayi, ad tiři ddunect simant nnes war dayes ca ttasiɛ ḥima ad teksi idlisen i ɣa ittwarin. Amin!  
\b  
\m Aneggar n L’Injil Iqeddsen am mammec t ibarreḥ Yuḥanna.  
\b  
\m Aneggar n tira n idlisen n arebɛa n \add idlisen\add* n L’Injil.  
\b  
\m Aɛuǧi i Babas, i Mmis u i Arruḥ Iqeddsen, řexxu, řebda u i řebda n řebdat. \x ◘ \xo 21:25 \xt Yḥ. 20:30. \x*   